\id EXO (EXO.BTU) Exode en Langue Baga Sitem
\h K…ôwur
\toc3 KWUR
\toc2 K…ôwur
\toc1 Tawureta Musa, Buk 2: K…ôwur ka aka Yisrayel Misira
\mt2 Tawureta Musa, Buk 2:
\mt1 K…ôwur ka aka Yisrayel Misira Ňäayi Y…õŇč…ôn
\imt1 Moloku ma k…ôs…Ēk…ôs buk ba Musa ba m…õr…ôŇč: K…ôwur
\ip D…ôbuk b…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ba tawureta Musa b…Ē taruku ta aka Yisrayel poncop, mb…õ aŇčwe: ¬ęD…ôk…ôcop da Doru.¬Ľ Sora s…ôlp…ôs s…ôk…Ē s…ôment…ôr t…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanayi at…Ēf Ňča Misira t…õm ta AŇčnabi Isifu m…Ē.
\ip Nt…õ Isifu k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča Ňčafi m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôb…Ēt k…ôncop k…ôpic…õ aka Yisrayel k…Ē aka Misira dac…Ē. D…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da ti, k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčay…Ēn…õ acar a aka Misira. K…Ē ab…õ a Misira Ňčanc…ômb…ôr aka Yisrayel y…õb…ôc yocuca, ti disr…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčal…Ēn…õ aka Misira s…ôdare s…ôŇčan.
\ip Mba MARIKI nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēp…ôl…ôrn…õ afum …Ēn m…Ē, osom AŇčnabi Musa nde at…Ēf Ňča Misira nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčas…Ēt…Ē k…ôyi y…õŇč…ôn m…Ē. K…Ē Kanu k…ôment…ôr…õ mes m…õw…õy-w…õy w…ôco d…ôwaca wa Musa haŇč k…Ē firawona …õmb…õl…ôs aka Yisrayel. Nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčancop k…ôk…Ēt m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp k…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma nk…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka Misira nk…õ k…ônafaŇč k…ôyams…ôr Ňča k…ôcep…ôr m…Ē. Firawona k…Ē as…Ēdar …Ēn Ňčas…õp k…ôdif…ôt Ňča d…ôndo, mba k…Ē Kanu k…ôment…ôr s…Ē d…ôndo tes t…õw…õy-w…õy, k'eŇčgbiti d…Ēp…Ē k…ôba dac…Ē nd…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčanacali. Arkun, aran, awut k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčaŇč f…ôp Ňčanacali d…ôk…ôba d…Ēp…Ē dowosu k…ôroŇč. Nt…õ aka Misira Ňčanac…ôm…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ôŇčgb…ôp…ôr Ňča domun da d…ôk…ôba.
\ip K…ôba mokuru, k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčancop k…ôk…Ēt d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ē ka at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč nŇč…õ Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč temer k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē. Ňäas…Ēr…Ēyi d…Ēp…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč AŇčnabi Musa mosom m…Ēn w…ôco nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi k…ôroŇč f…Ēr ya afum kiriŇč. Mba t…õnawon f…õ, k…Ē afum ŇčaŇčgb…õk…ôl sariy…õ sa Kanu, k…Ē Ňčasal…õn…õ t…õr…ôŇčka. Ti t…Ē Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õn…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôk…Ēt d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ disr…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanagb…õk…ôl Kanu m…Ē f…ôp Ňčalip k…ôfis-fis a Ňčacb…õr…õ at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč.
\ip K…ôk…Ēt kaŇčk…Ē disr…õ, k…Ē Kanu k…ôyi Ňča kiriŇč k…ôsol…õ Ňča. N…Ēr…Ē da debeki d…Ēn d…õnayi Ňča kiriŇč pibi k…Ē daŇč. Nt…õ Ňčanay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčantor…õ aŇčgbancan. N…Ēr…Ē da debeki da Kanu d…õnayi aka Yisrayel kiriŇč haŇč k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ nde Ňčanac…ômb…ôr…ôs m…Ē. Towur…õn…õ ta tat…Ēk…Ē t…õnayi meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ disr…õ f…ôp.
\ip Teta defi da AŇčnabi Musa t…Ē buk bamb…õ boloku t…õlp…ôs. Ta p…ômb…Ēl…õ k…Ē s…Ē k…ôfi-…õ, k'…õl…õk aka Yisrayel k'…Ēs…ĒŇč AŇčnabi Yosuwe nw…õ …õnab…õrs…õn…õ Ňča at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē.
\ip K…ôyi ka Kanu afum …Ēn dac…Ē, p…ôt…ôks…õ Ňča dolompu, p…ôbum…õ Ňča s…Ēk…ôt, tat…Ēk…Ē f…ôp towur…õn…õ t…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ afum a Kanu t…õm tosu tant…õ ayi m…Ē. Kanu k…ôfaŇč k…ôc…ômb…ôr su d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēt…Ēt k…ôk…Ē ka ariyana nde …ĒŇčk…Ēb…õrs…õn…õ su m…Ē. Kanu k…ômar su mar…ônt mam…Ēk…Ē disr…õ. AMINA!
\iot Teyer ta buk bamb…õ
\io1 1, As…Ēk…ôs t…Ēk…Ē anac…ômb…ôr aka Yisrayel dacar at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē.
\io1 2-4, As…Ēk…ôs tecep…ôr…õn…õ ta Musa haŇč t…õm nt…õ …õnade p…ôbaŇč aYisrayel aka Misira d…ôwaca m…Ē.
\io1 5-15.21, Aloku t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônay…Ē mes m…õw…õy-w…õy k…Ē arom nŇč…õ k…ônas…ĒŇč aMisira nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôbaŇč…ôr as…Ēdar a firawona afum …Ēn m…Ē.
\io1 15.22-19, Aloku t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanay…õf…õ Misira k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčand…õ toro ta Sinayi m…Ē.
\io1 20-31, Aloku t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč AŇčnabi Musa Sariy…õ ns…õ s…ônas…Ēk…ôs mosom nt…õ p…ômar aka Yisrayel Ňčade Ňčayi k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar Ňčade Ňčaclel…ôs nk…Ēn Kanu m…Ē.
\io1 32, Aloku t…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel ŇčanayeŇčk…ôr Kanu s…ôbomp nt…õ Ňčanac…ĒŇč…ôs Aruna k…ôs…õl…õ k…õma t…õr…ôŇčka pa tura m…Ē.
\io1 33-40, Al…Ēm t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnan…ôŇčk n…Ēr…Ē da debeki da Kanu m…Ē. K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ day, K…Ē Musa …õnt…ôks…õ aka Yisrayel Sariy…õ sa Kanu k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar palomp…ôs d…ôkiyi da Kanu, kaŇčk…ôra ka Sede, k…Ē yogbuŇčs…ôr…õn…õ y…Ēl…Ēma teta k…ôb…ôc…õ Kanu d…ôndo aŇčgbancan yosoku, k…Ē yamos taciŇča ya aloŇčn…õ.
\mt1 K…ôwur ka aka Yisrayel Misira
\c 1
\ms2 Kanu k…ôwur…õn…õ aka Yisrayel Misira
\mr 1-15
\s1 Aka Yisrayel k…ôyi k…ôŇčan dacar Misira
\p 
\v 1 Mewe ma awut a Yakuba\f + \fr 1:1 \ft C…ôHeb…ôre = ¬ęAwut a Yisrayel,¬Ľ Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč Yakuba tewe ta ¬ęYisrayel.¬Ľ M…ôm…Ēm…ôn D…ôk…ôcop 32.29.\f* m…Ē mm…õ, aŇč…õ Ňčanader Misira k…Ē nk…Ēn Yakuba m…Ē. F…ôp faŇčan Ňčanak…õr…õn…õ aka w…Ēl…Ē waŇčan disr…õ f…ôp:
\v 2 Ruben, Simey…ĒŇč, Lewy, k…Ē Yuda,
\v 3 Isakar, Sabulon, k…Ē BeŇčyamin,
\v 4 Dan, Naftali, Kadu k…Ē As…õr.
\v 5 Yuruya ya Yakuba f…ôp Ňčanayi afum w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (70). T…õnat…ôŇčn…õ Isifu nk…Ēn p…ôyi t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē Misira.
\v 6 K…Ē Isifu ende p…ôfi k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča, k…Ē danapa dad…Ēk…Ē f…ôp.
\v 7 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčande Ňčas…Ēt…Ē dokomb…ôra, k…Ē Ňčala, k…Ē k…ônay k…ôŇčan k…ôs…Ēt…Ē s…Ēk…ôt k…ôcep…ôr…ôr. K'at…Ēf Ňča Misira Ňč…õlar…õ Ňča.
\p 
\v 8 Nt…õ t…õm t…Ēl…Ēma tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ …õnat…Ēc…ôr…õ Isifu m…Ē, ende p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ Misira.
\v 9 K…Ē w…ôb…õ nw…õ ende p…ôloku afum …Ēn: ¬ęN…ôn…ôŇčk, afum aka Yisrayel Ňčala, k…Ē Ňčay…Ē s…Ēk…ôt Ňčatas su.
\v 10 M…õn…õ pat…õn k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt, nt…õ andeyams…ôr Ňča dokomb…ôra daŇčan m…Ē. K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, k…Ē k…ôwan k…ôy…õf…õ-…õ, Ňčantam k…ômar ater…õn…õ asu k…ôsut…õn…õ, k…Ē telip-…õ, Ňčamulp…ôr su Ňčawur at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ.¬Ľ
\v 11 Awa, k…Ē aka Misira Ňčanc…ômb…ôr akiriŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanak…Ēs…ĒŇč…ôs aka Yisrayel y…õb…ôc ya dacar m…Ē. Ti disr…õ, k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanc…ômb…ôr s…ôdare sa Pit…Ēm k…Ē Rams…õs, p…ôy…Ēn…õ di d…ôk…ôm…õŇčk da firawona\f + \fr 1:11 \fq Firawona\ft = Baf…Ē tewe ta fum t…Ē, mba tewe ta nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēmp…ôr d…õb…õ da Misira m…Ē.\f*.
\v 12 Mba p…Ēk…Ēt pa firawona p…õnak…Ēt f…õ few, bawo tat…Ēk…Ē anct…Ēr…ôs aka Yisrayel m…Ē, ti t…Ē Ňčanckom, Ňčacla, Ňčacw…Ēk…ôl…ôs d…ôk…ônd…õ daŇčan, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ pater aka Yisrayel p…ôp…ĒŇč.
\v 13 K…Ē aka Misira Ňčanc…ômb…ôr aka Yisrayel y…õb…ôc ya dacar yeyeŇčki.
\v 14 K'aka Misira Ňčandokt…ôs…õ aka Yisrayel doru y…õb…ôc yeyeŇčki: Y…õb…ôc ya dos, ya birik, ya dal…õ f…ôp. Y…õb…ôc ya dacar yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē Ňčanac…ômb…ôr aka Yisrayel.
\s1 Firawona …Ēnt…Ēr…ôs aka Yisrayel
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Misira ende p…ôloku aran abaŇč awut aHeb…ôre, pacwe w…ôkin ¬ęSifra,¬Ľ k…Ē w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč ¬ęPuwa.¬Ľ
\v 16 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Misira oloku Ňča: ¬ęK…Ē n…ônde k…ôcbaŇč aran aHeb…ôre awut-…õ, n…ôcm…Ēm…ôn Ňča kiriŇč. Nw…õ …ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ w…ôrkun m…Ē, n…ôdif k…Ē, nw…õ …ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ w…ôran m…Ē, n…ôsak w…ôkak…Ē p…ôyi doru.¬Ľ
\v 17 Mba k…Ē aran abaŇč awut aŇč…õ Ňčanes…õ Kanu, Ňčay…Ē f…õ nt…õ w…ôb…õ ka Misira …õnaloku Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčance awut arkun k…Ē Ňčayi doru.
\v 18 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Misira ewe aran abaŇč awut aŇč…õ, k'eyif Ňča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ tant…õ-…õ? Ta ake t…Ē n…ôncen…õ awut aŇčan arkun Ňčacyin…õ doru-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 19 K…Ē abaŇč awut aŇč…õ Ňčaloku firawona: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ ti m…Ē, aran aHeb…ôre Ňčayi f…õ p…ôm…Ē aran aka Misira. Aran aHeb…ôre ŇčayeŇčk m…õnc d…ôŇčkom, ŇčaŇčlip k…ôkom a s…ôna abaŇč awut s…ôcb…ôp di.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 20 K…Ē Kanu k…ôy…Ēn…õ abaŇč awut aŇč…õ p…ôt…Ēt, k'aka Yisrayel Ňčala, k…Ē Ňčas…Ēt…Ē s…Ē s…Ēk…ôt k…Ē Ňčancep…ôr…ôr.
\v 21 AbaŇč awut aŇč…õ Ňčananes…õ Kanu, it…Ē Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ Ňča dokomb…ôra.
\v 22 K…Ē firawona ende p…ôsom afum …Ēn f…ôp: ¬ęN…ôsump…ôr awut arkun aHeb…ôre f…ôp, aŇč…õ ande packom m…Ē, n…ôcgbal Ňča nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Nil, mba n…ôcsak gb…ôc…ôr…ôm awut aran Ňčayi doru.¬Ľ
\c 2
\s1 K…ôkom ka Musa k…Ē dowut d…Ēn
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma w…ôka kusuŇčka ka Lewy …õn…õnc…õ w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ ŇčanapaŇčn…õ kusuŇčka kin k…Ē nk…Ēn m…Ē.
\v 2 K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ …õmb…õk…ôs, k'oŇčkom wan w…ôrkun. K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ …õn…ôŇčk d…Ēt…Ēt da wan, k'…ĒŇčgb…Ēpn…õn…õ wan k…Ēn yof maas.
\v 3 Nt…õ …õn…ôŇčk a …Ēf…Ēs…Ētam k…ôgb…Ēpn…õn…õ wan m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôran nw…õ …õl…õk k…ôfala nk…õ andun…õ c…ôŇčk…Ēlma m…Ē, k'osop ki paka mp…õ powur…õn…õ k…Ērtal k…Ē b…ôn ya c…ôme m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ki k…ôf…Ēy m…Ē. K'…õmb…õr wan k…ôfala nk…õ disr…õ, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôc…ômb…ôr ki d…ôc…ôŇčk…Ēlma nde aparpara Ňča k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Nil.
\v 4 K…Ē w…ôkir…õ ka wan nw…õ aŇčgbal m…Ē, …õnc…ôm…õ p…ôwak k…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôctam k…ôc…ôr…õ t…Ēk…Ē tendeder wan m…Ē.
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē wan w…ôran w…ôka firawona ende p…ôtor nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē k…ôk…Ēbik…õ-bik…õ, amar…ôs …Ēn aran Ňčayi k…ôk…Ēt…ôs agb…õp Ňča k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Nil. K…Ē wan ka firawona w…ôran nw…õ …õn…ôŇčk k…ôfala c…ôŇčk…Ēlma dac…Ē, k'osom w…ômar…ôs k…Ēn w…ôran k…ôk…Ēl…õk ki.
\v 6 Wan ka firawona w…ôran endegbipi k…ôfala nk…õ, k'…õn…ôŇčk wan: Wan w…ôrkun …õnayi, p…ôcbok. K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…Ē n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr, k'oloku: ¬ęWan w…ôHeb…ôre w…ôl…Ēma …Ēf…Ē w…ôkaw…õ!¬Ľ
\v 7 K…Ē w…ôkir…õ ka wan nw…õ oloku wan ka firawona w…ôran: ¬ęM…ôfaŇč a ik…Ē iwen'am w…ôkomb…ôra w…ôHeb…ôre w…ôl…Ēma, p…ôdems…ôr'am wan w…ôkaw…õ?¬Ľ
\v 8 K…Ē wan ka firawona w…ôran oluks…õ w…ôyec…ôra nt…õ: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē!¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôyec…ôra nw…õ …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôwe iya w…ôka wan w…ôkak…Ē anafir m…Ē.
\v 9 K…Ē wan ka firawona w…ôran oloku w…ôran nw…õ: ¬ęM…ôken…õn…õ wan w…ôkaw…õ m…ôk…Ē m…ôcm…õs…ôr'em k…Ē belbel. Indes…ĒŇč …ôm k…ôway.¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ …õl…õk wan, k'…õm…õs…ôr k…Ē.
\p 
\v 10 Nt…õ awur…õ wan m…õs…õ m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôran nw…õ …õl…õk k…Ē, k'eŇčken…õ wan ka firawona w…ôran, p…ôy…Ēn…õ k…Ē wan. K'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē tewe ta Musa bawo ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęd…ôromun incafi k…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 P…ômar Musa p…ôy…õks…õ p…ôk…Ē MadiyaŇč
\p 
\v 11 Nt…õ Musa …õmb…õk k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôt…õmp m…Ē, d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma k'ende p…ôk…Ē k…ôk…Ēm…Ēm…ôn aw…õnc aŇča, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôn…ôŇčk y…õb…ôc yaŇčan yeyeŇčki ny…õ anac…ômb…ôr Ňča m…Ē. Nt…õ …Ēnc…ĒŇčn…õ kiriŇč m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôn…ôŇčk w…ôka Misira p…ôcsut w…õnc w…ôHeb…ôre w…ôkin.
\v 12 K…Ē Musa …Ēm…Ēm…ôn-m…Ēm…ôn, nt…õ …Ēnt…Ēn…ôŇčk fum m…Ē, k'osut w…ôka Misira nw…õ k'endif, k'…õl…õk k…Ē k'…õm…ôt d…õs…ônc.
\v 13 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē Musa owur s…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôn…ôŇčk aHeb…ôre m…õr…ôŇč Ňčacsut…õn…õ. K'eyif w…ôk…Ē …õnad…ôk…ôt m…Ē: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē m…ôŇčsut…õ w…ôkos …ôm-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 14 K…Ē fum nw…õ oloku k…Ē: ¬ęAn'…õc…ômb…ôr …ôm d…õb…õ k…Ē w…ôboc kiti su k…ôroŇč-…õ? K…ôdif im k…Ē m…ônder p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ôndifsa w…ôka Misira m…Ē ba?¬Ľ K…Ē Musa enes…õ, k'olokun…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc: ¬ęT…Ēl…Ēma anc…ôr…õ tes tant…õ iy…Ēsa m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 15 K…Ē firawona ene t…Ēk…Ē t…õnacep…ôr m…Ē, k'…õnt…õn oŇč k…ôdif Musa. Mba k…Ē Musa …õy…õks…õ k'…Ēmb…Ēl…õ firawona, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē at…Ēf Ňča MadiyaŇč. Nt…õ …õmb…õr…õ MadiyaŇč m…Ē k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ k…ôl…ômp k…ôs…ôk.
\p 
\v 16 Awa, w…ôloŇčn…õn…õ ka aka MadiyaŇč …õnay…Ē awut aran cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. K…Ē awut aran aŇč…õ Ňčander k…ôdek…õt domun, k…Ē Ňčalas…ôs d…ôk…ômun da y…Ēc…Ēl ya kas k…ôŇčan.
\v 17 K…Ē ak…õk al…Ēma Ňčander Ňčab…õl…ôs Ňča. K…Ē Musa …õy…õf…õ k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôbaŇč Ňča, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan domun k…Ē yomun.
\v 18 Nt…õ Ňčalukus nda kas k…ôŇčan Rehuw…õl m…Ē, k…Ē kas k…ôŇčan eyif Ňča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ônuŇčk…õn…õn…õ m…Ēk…Ē k…ôb…õr…õ-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 19 K'ayec…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčaloku kas k…ôŇčan: ¬ęW…ôka Misira w…ôl…Ēma …õyac su nn…Ē ak…õk Ňčayi m…Ē. ∆źŇčk…õt…õna su domun yati, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč y…Ēc…Ēl yosu.¬Ľ
\v 20 K…Ē Rehuw…õl eyif ayec…ôra: ¬ęDeke eyi-…õ? Ta ake t…Ē n…ôsak…õ fum w…ôkak…Ē-…õ? N…ôwe k…Ē p…ôder p…ôdi yeri.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē Musa ende p…ôwos…õ k…ôyi ka ndena Rehuw…õl, nw…õ …õnas…ĒŇč wan k…Ēn w…ôran Sefora k…ôn…õnc…õ m…Ē.
\v 22 K…Ē w…ôran kak…Ē ende p…ôkom wan, k'awe k…Ē K…õrs…Ēm, ¬ęW…ôcik…ôra,¬Ľ bawo k'oloku ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē: ¬ęW…ôcik…ôra iy…Ēn…õ k…ôr…õsna at…Ēf Ňčocuru.¬Ľ
\s1 Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk Musa k…ôwur…õ ka aka Yisrayel dacar
\p 
\v 23 Nt…õ p…ôwon m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Misira ende p…ôfi, aka Yisrayel Ňčacgbis, Ňčackul…õ-kul…õn…õ teta dacar deyeŇčki d…Ēk…Ē Ňčanayi m…Ē. K…Ē k…ômar nk…õ Ňčancbok m…Ē, k…ômp…õ haŇč nde nk…Ēn Kanu eyi m…Ē.
\v 24 K…Ē Kanu k…ône kigbis k…ôŇčan. K…Ē Kanu k…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ danapa nd…õ ŇčanacaŇč…ôs k…Ē Abraham, Siyaka k…Ē Yakuba m…Ē.
\v 25 K…Ē Kanu k…ôm…Ēm…ôn aka Yisrayel, k…Ē k…ôl…õk te taŇčan waca disr…õ.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē Musa ende p…ôyi…Ēn…õ w…ôk…õk y…Ēc…Ēl ya Yetero, papa ka w…ôran k…Ēn, nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôka MadiyaŇč m…Ē. D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma, k'ende p…ôkek…ôr…õ y…Ēc…Ēl k'encep…ôr d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, k'…õmb…ôp Hor…õb t…Ēr…Ē ta Kanu.
\v 2 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI mowur…ôr k…Ē d…ôn…õnc d…õmar disr…õ, nde d…õr…ônt…ôm. K…Ē Musa …Ēm…Ēm…ôn, k'…õn…ôŇčk ar…ônt…ôm f…ôp Ňč…õcmar, mba Ňč…õnct…õy…õ f…õ.
\v 3 K…Ē Musa …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ: ¬ęIluks…ôrn…õ ma, im…Ēm…ôn tes nt…õ intat…Ēn…ôŇčk m…Ē, ta ake t…Ē ar…ônt…ôm Ňč…Ēnt…Ēt…õy…õn…õ-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 4 K…Ē MARIKI …õn…ôŇčk a k…ôluks…ôrn…õ k…Ē Musa …õnd…õ k…ôk…Ēgb…õk…ôr…õ tes nt…õ. K…Ē Kanu k…ôwe k…Ē d…ôndo d…õr…ônt…ôm, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęMusa! Musa!¬Ľ K'owos…õn…õ k…Ē: ¬ęIn'…õw…õ!¬Ľ
\v 5 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku k…Ē: ¬ęTa m…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ nn…Ē, m…ôwur…õ c…Ēfta d…ôw…õc…ôk, bawo k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē m…ônc…ôm…õ m…Ē, ant…Ēf Ňčosoku Ňč…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 6 K…Ē k…ôndeŇč…ôr: ¬ęIn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ Kanu ka papa kam, Kanu ka Abraham, Kanu ka Siyaka, Kanu ka Yakuba.¬Ľ
\p K…Ē Musa oŇčkumpn…õ k…ôro, bawo …õnanes…õ k…ôm…Ēm…ôn Kanu.
\v 7 K…Ē MARIKI oloku: ¬ęIn…ôŇčk belbel nt…õ ant…Ēr…ôs afum em aŇč…õ Ňčayi Misira m…Ē. Ine nt…õ Ňčayi k…ôbok…ôr k…ôt…Ēr…ôs ka ab…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanc…ômb…ôr Ňča dacar f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē, inc…ôr…õ pucuy paŇčan.
\v 8 It'intor…õn…õ k…ôdebaŇč…ôr Ňča aka Misira, ip…õn…õ Ňča s…Ē at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ, ikek…ôr…õ Ňča at…Ēf Ňčobotu, at…Ēf Ňčowok…ôlu disr…õ, nde at…Ēf ŇčoboŇču dal…õ k‚Äôawop, at…Ēf nŇč…õ aka KanaŇč, aHit, aka Am…Ēr, aPerisi, aHiwy k…Ē aYebus Ňčand…õ m…Ē.
\v 9 K…ôbok ka aka Yisrayel k…ônder oŇč haŇč nn…Ē iyi m…Ē, k'in…ôŇčk k…ôt…Ēr…ôs k…ôlar…ôm nk…õ aka Misira Ňčayi k…ôt…Ēr…ôs afum em m…Ē.
\v 10 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč m…ôk…Ē, isom …ôm ndena firawona. M…ôwur…õn…õ afum em aka Yisrayel Misira.¬Ľ
\s1 Kanu k…ômbonc…ôr tewe t…Ēn Musa
\p 
\v 11 K…Ē Musa eyif Kanu: ¬ęAn'iy…Ēn…õ-…õ, nt…õ indek…Ē nda firawona, ik…Ēwur…õn…õ aka Yisrayel Misira m…Ē?¬Ľ
\v 12 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku k…Ē: ¬ęIn'osol'am! T…õgb…õk…ôr…õ nt…õ tendes…ĒŇč'am k…ôc…ôr…õ a in'osom …ôm: Nt…õ m…ôndewur…õn…õ aka Yisrayel Misira m…Ē, f…ôp fonu n…ôde n…ôcsal…õn'em nn…Ē t…Ēr…Ē nt…õ.¬Ľ
\v 13 K…Ē Musa oloku k…Ē: ¬ęK'iŇčk…Ē nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē, ik…Ē icloku Ňča: Kanu ka atem anu k…ôsom im nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē. Mba k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ēyif im nt…õ aŇčwe ki m…Ē, c…ôke c'iŇčk…Ēloku Ňča-…õ?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 14 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku Musa: ¬ęNw…õ iy…Ēn…õ m…Ē, iy…Ēn…õ!¬Ľ K…Ē k…ôndeŇč…ôr: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēloku aka Yisrayel: Nw…õ aŇčwe ‚ÄĻIy…Ēn…õ‚Äļ osom im nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 15 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku s…Ē Musa: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēloku aka Yisrayel: ‚ÄĻMARIKI, Kanu ka atem anu, Kanu ka Abraham, ka Siyaka, ka Yakuba k…ôsom im nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē.‚Äļ Tewe tem t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē ta t…õm o t…õm, k…Ē t…õc…õmc…õmn…õ tem tant…õ t…Ē d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp.
\v 16 M…ôk…Ē m…ôloŇčka abeki aka Yisrayel, m…ôloku Ňča: ‚ÄĻMARIKI, Kanu ka atem anu Abraham, Siyaka, k…Ē Yakuba owur…ôr im.‚Äļ K…Ē k…ôloku: ‚ÄĻInc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôwur…õ nu p…ôcuca p…Ēk…Ē anc…ômb…ôr nu Misira m…Ē.
\v 17 K'iloku a k…ôwur…õn…õ nu k'inder k…ôt…Ēr…ôs disr…õ nk…õ n…ôyi Misira m…Ē, ikek…ôr…õ nu at…Ēf Ňča aKanaŇč, aHit, aka Am…Ēr, aPerisi, aHiwy k…Ē aYebus, at…Ēf nŇč…õ ŇčoboŇč dal…õ k‚Äôawop m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\p 
\v 18 ¬ęAka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčk…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl dim dam, n…ôsol oŇč n…ôk…Ē, m…ôna k…Ē abeki aka Yisrayel, ndena w…ôb…õ w…ôka Misira, n…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻMARIKI, Kanu ka aHeb…ôre k…ômb…ôp su. Nd…õk…ôl m…ôwos…õ su k…ôk…Ēt mar…ônt ma mata maas nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôk…Ē s…ôloŇčn…õ MARIKI Kanu kosu m…Ē.‚Äļ
\v 19 Ina inc…ôr…õ a w…ôb…õ ka Misira …Ēf…Ēdek…Ēwos…õ nu k…ôk…Ē, ta p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē ti-…õ.
\v 20 K…ôtenci k'inder k…ôca isut Misira, mes m…õw…õy-w…õy m…Ēp…ĒŇč f…ôp m'indesut…õ Misira. K…Ē mes mam…Ēk…Ē mencep…ôr-…õ, Ňčadesak nu n…ôk…Ē.
\v 21 Indes…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčas…Ēt…Ē k…ômar ka k…ôb…Ēt…ôr ka aka Misira. K…Ē n…ônde n…ôck…Ē-…õ, n…ôf…Ēdek…Ē waca w…Ēs…Ēk…ôr.
\v 22 Aran aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčade Ňčawer aran a Misira aŇč…õ Ňčayi ndaraŇčan, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, aran ak…Ē Ňčand…õ m…Ē, ca ca gbeti, ya k…õma k…Ē yamos, ny…õ n…ôndesars…ôr awut anu arkun k…Ē aran m…Ē. Nt…õ t…Ē n…ôbaŇč…ôr aka Misira ca c…ôŇčan.¬Ľ
\c 4
\s1 Kanu k…ôment…ôr f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…Ēn Musa
\p 
\v 1 Mba k…Ē Musa oluks…õ MARIKI moloku: ¬ęŇäaf…Ēdek…ĒlaŇč im, Ňčaf…Ēdek…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl dim dem. Nt…õ Ňčandek…Ēloku m…Ē: ‚ÄĻMARIKI owur…ôr f'am.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\v 2 K…Ē MARIKI eyif k…Ē: ¬ęAke m…ônt…Ēmp…ôr-…õ?¬Ľ K…Ē Musa oloku: ¬ęK…ôgbo.¬Ľ
\v 3 K…Ē MARIKI oloku: ¬ęM…ôl…ôm ki ma d…ônt…Ēf.¬Ľ K…Ē Musa …õl…ôm k…ôgbo k…Ēn d…ônt…Ēf, k…Ē k…ôgbo k…ônt…ôŇčk…ôl…õ abok. K…Ē Musa …õy…õks…ôr Ňči.
\v 4 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôt…õnc k…ôca m…ôsump…ôr Ňči nde d…ôk…ôleŇča.¬Ľ K…Ē Musa …õnt…õnc k…ôca k'osump…ôr Ňči, k…Ē Ňč…õnt…ôŇčk…ôl…õ s…Ē k…ôgbo k…ôca k…Ēn disr…õ.
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęTant…õ t'endek…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôlaŇč oŇč a MARIKI Kanu ka atem aŇčan, Kanu ka Abraham, Siyaka, k…Ē Yakuba k…ôwur…ôr …ôm.¬Ľ
\v 6 K…Ē MARIKI oloku s…Ē Musa: ¬ęM…ôb…õr k…ôca duma tant…Ēf d…õb…ôk…ôc,¬Ľ k…Ē Musa …õmb…õr k…ôca k…Ēn duma tant…Ēf k'endeŇčn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc. Nt…õ eliŇčn…õ ki m…Ē, ¬ęEh!¬Ľ, k…Ē sen s…ôsump…ôr k…Ē k…ôca k…Ē k…ôfer…õ, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ kibi k…ôntuf…ôr paka m…Ē.
\v 7 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku k…Ē s…Ē: ¬ęM…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôdeŇčn…õ k…ôca d…õb…ôk…ôc.¬Ľ K…Ē Musa endeŇčn…õ s…Ē k…ôca k…Ēn duma tant…Ēf d…õb…ôk…ôc, ¬ęEh!¬Ľ, k…Ē akata Ňča k…ôca k…Ēn Ňčoluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôyi p…ôm…Ē Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē.
\v 8 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęK…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a ŇčalaŇč f'am, Ňčanc…ôŇčk…ôl f…õ dim da t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ t…õw…õy-w…õy t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē-…õ, ŇčandelaŇč …ôm teta t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ t…õw…õy-w…õy t…Ēc…Ēnc tant…õ.
\v 9 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a Ňčasump…ôr f…õ s…Ē moloku mam ta m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…õw…õy-w…õy mam…õ m…õr…ôŇč-…õ, ta Ňčanc…ôŇčk…ôl dim dam-…õ, m…ôk…õt domun da Nil, m…ôloŇč di ant…Ēf Ňčowosu k…ôroŇč, domun da k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Nil dad…Ēk…Ē m…ôŇčloŇč m…Ē, d…ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ mecir ant…Ēf Ňčowosu k…ôroŇč.¬Ľ
\s1 Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk Aruna p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôd…ôŇčk ka Musa
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē Musa oloku MARIKI: ¬ęM…ôŇčaŇčn…õ Mariki, mba fum nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēf…ôf…ôr…õn…õ temer m…Ē iy…Ēn…õ. Baf…Ē nendisna, baf…Ē nendecna, baf…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ m…ônal…õk k…ôlok-lok…ôr ina, w…ôcar kam, a k'ilel…õ kusu k…Ē temer m…Ē. T…õs…ôkp…ôr f…õ. Bawo ilel…õ kusu k…Ē temer.¬Ľ
\v 11 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęAn'…Ēs…ĒŇč fum kusu nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôtam k…ôlok-loku m…Ē-…õ? An'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ fum k…ôy…Ēn…õ bobo, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôt…Ēne-…õ? An'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ fum k…ôn…ôŇčk, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk-…õ? Baf…Ē in'…Ēf…Ē, ina MARIKI ba?
\v 12 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, m…ôk…Ē! Ina yati indek…Ēyi k…Ē kusu kam, indek…Ē ict…ôks'am t…Ēk…Ē m…ôndek…Ē m…ôcloku m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 13 Mba k…Ē Musa oloku s…Ē: ¬ęM…ôŇčaŇčn…õ Mariki mba il…õts…õn'am, m…ôsom w…ôl…Ēma w…ôk…Ē m…ôfaŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 14 K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ MARIKI nn…Ē Musa eyi m…Ē, k'oloku Musa: ¬ęBaf…Ē m…ôy…Ē w…õnc Aruna, w…ôLewy? Inc…ôr…õ a oŇčlok-loku belbel. Gb…õs, nk…Ēn ender w…ôk…Ē k…ôdefayn'am. K…ôn…ôŇčk kam k…ôndeb…Ēt k…Ē d…õb…ôk…ôc.
\v 15 M…ôde m…ôlok-lok…ôr k…Ē, m…ôde m…ôloku k…Ē nt…õ endek…Ēloku m…Ē. In'endek…Ēt…Ēmp…ôr kusu kam k…Ē k…Ēn, iŇčk…Ēt…ôks'on t…Ēk…Ē n…ôndek…Ē n…ôcy…Ē m…Ē.
\v 16 Aruna endek…Ēlok-lok…ôr'am afum aka Yisrayel, endek…Ē k…ôcy…Ēn'am kusu, m…ôna m…ôyi p…ôm…Ē kanu nk…õ k…ôsom k…Ē m…Ē.
\v 17 M…ôt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôgbo kaŇčk…õ d…ôk…ôca, ki k…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ē m…ôcment…ôr…õ m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…õw…õy-w…õy.¬Ľ
\s1 Musa olukus nde afum …Ēn Ňčayi m…Ē
\p 
\v 18 K…Ē Musa …ĒŇčk…Ē, k'oluks…ôrn…õ ndena Yetero papa ka w…ôran k…Ēn. K…Ē Musa oloku k…Ē: ¬ęIl…õts…õn'am k…ôwos'em k…ôluks…ôrn…õ Misira nde afum em Ňčayi m…Ē k…ôk…Ēn…ôŇčk k…Ē Ňčas…Ēr…Ēyi doru-…õ.¬Ľ K…Ē Yetero oloku Musa: ¬ęAwa m…ôk…Ēn…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňčoforu.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 19 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa, d…ôndo at…Ēf Ňča MadiyaŇč: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē, m…ôlukus Misira, bawo afum aŇč…õ ŇčanafaŇč k…ôdif …ôm m…Ē, Ňčafi.¬Ľ
\v 20 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk w…ôran k…Ēn k…Ē awut …Ēn, k'…õnd…ôs Ňča s…Ēfale k…ôroŇč, k'olukus at…Ēf Ňča Misira p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôgbo nk…õ Kanu k…ônaloku k…Ē k…ôl…õk m…Ē.
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęNt…õ m…ôyi k…ôlukus Misira m…Ē, m…ôk…Ēkc…õ m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…õw…õy-w…õy m…Ēk…Ē is…ĒŇč'am k…ôtam k…ôy…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, m…ôk…Ē m…ôy…Ē mi firawona f…Ēr kiriŇč. Mba ina Kanu, iŇčk…Ē icyeŇčk…ôs k…Ē domp nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta …õsak aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ē m…Ē.
\v 22 M…ôk…Ē m…ôloku firawona: ‚ÄĻNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI oloku: Yisrayel coco cem c…Ē.
\v 23 Ilok'…ôm a m…ôsak wan kem p…ôk…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôk…Ēsal…õn'em m…Ē. Mba nt…õ m…ôfati k…ôsak k…Ē p…ôk…Ē m…Ē, k…ôdif k'inder wan kam w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôk…ônc ka wan ka Musa
\p 
\v 24 K…ôlukus k…ôŇčan disr…õ, k…Ē Musa …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ pibi k…ôfo k…ôl…Ēma, k…Ē MARIKI ender p…ôb…ôp k…Ē, p…ôcfaŇč k…ôdif k…Ē.
\v 25 K…Ē Sefora w…ôran k…Ēn …õl…õk tasar towoŇču, k'eŇčgbint…õ k…ôrot ka wan k…Ēn, k'oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õn…õ ki w…õc…ôk wa Musa, k'oloku: ¬ęWos im w…ôka d…ômecir m…ôy…Ēn'em!¬Ľ
\v 26 MARIKI …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ f…õ s…Ē k…ôdif ka Musa teta k…ôk…ônc ka wan k…Ēn. It…Ē Sefora …õnalok…õn…õ s…Ē Musa: ¬ęWos im w…ôka d…ômecir!¬Ľ Toloku tant…õ t'aŇčloku teta k…ôk…ônc.
\s1 K…ôb…ôp…õn…õ ka Musa k…Ē Aruna
\p 
\v 27 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Aruna: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē m…ôb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Musa nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ.¬Ľ K…Ē Aruna …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…ôp w…õnc Musa nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Kanu, k'…õsapn…õ k…Ē.
\v 28 K…Ē Musa oloku w…õnc Aruna moloku k…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…õw…õy-w…õy f…ôp mm…õ MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē k…ôloku k…Ē k…ôy…Ē m…Ē.
\v 29 Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčasol, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē ŇčaloŇčka abeki aka Yisrayel f…ôp.
\v 30 K…Ē Aruna oluks…õ abeki a Yisrayel moloku mm…õ MARIKI …õnasom Musa k…ôdeloku m…Ē f…ôp, k'ement…ôr m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…õw…õy-w…õy f…Ēr ya afum kiriŇč.
\v 31 K…Ē afum a Yisrayel ŇčalaŇč. K…Ē Ňčanc…ôr…õ a MARIKI ender…õn…õ te taŇčan k'…õnc…ôr…õ p…ôcuca p…Ēk…Ē Ňčayi disr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčantontn…õ k…ôkor-koru belbel MARIKI.
\c 5
\s1 Musa k…Ē Aruna ŇčaŇčk…Ē nda firawona
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ tencep…ôr m…Ē, Musa k…Ē Aruna ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp firawona k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI oloku, Kanu ka aka Yisrayel: M…ôsak afum em Ňčak…Ē Ňčaboc'em k…ôsata ka sali nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ.¬Ľ
\v 2 K…Ē firawona eyif Ňča: ¬ęAn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI, nt…õ indec…ôŇčk…ôl dim d…Ēn, isak aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ē m…Ē? Inc…ôr…õ f…õ MARIKI, tam…õr…ôŇč ta ti s…Ē, if…Ēsak aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ē nn…Ē o nn…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 3 K…Ē Musa Ňčaloku k…Ē Aruna: ¬ęKanu ka aHeb…ôre k…ônab…ôp su. M…ôsak su, il…õts…õn'am, s…ôk…Ēt mata maas d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ s…ôk…ĒloŇčn…õ MARIKI Kanu kosu, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta osut…õ su arom k…Ē dakma m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 4 K…Ē w…ôb…õ ka Misira eyif Ňča: ¬ęM…ôna Musa k…Ē Aruna, ta ake t…Ē n…ôfaŇč k…ôyams…õ afum y…õb…ôc yaŇčan-…õ?¬Ľ A c…ôke? N…ôk…Ē n…ôsump…ôr y…õb…ôc yonu ya dacar.
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē firawona oloku: ¬ęN…ôn…ôŇčk, aka Yisrayel Ňčala oŇč d…Ēt…Ēf! K…Ē n…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôsak y…õb…ôc yaŇčan yeyeŇčki.¬Ľ
\s1 Firawona k…ôn…Ēc…ôr…õ ka aka Yisrayel y…õb…ôc
\p 
\v 6 D…Ēs…Ēk din dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ē firawona osom ab…õ a dacar aMisira k…Ē abum aYisrayel, p…ôcloku:
\v 7 ¬ęTa n…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôcs…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel m…õmp…ôl…õ mosut…õ birik p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē n…ôs…ĒŇčsa Ňča nendisna k…Ē nendecna m…Ē. M…õn…õ Ňčas…ôrka Ňčak…Ē oŇč Ňčact…õn mi!
\v 8 K…ôl…Ēm ka birik nk…õ Ňčasutsa nendisna k…Ē nendecna m…Ē, n…ôgb…ôc Ňča Ňčasut ki! Ta n…ôbel…õ Ňča k…ôl…Ēm kaŇčk…Ē de! Bawo acemb…ôr Ňč…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ! Ti t…Ē Ňčambok…õn…õn…õ, Ňčacloku: ‚ÄĻPaŇčk…Ēn loŇčn…õ Kanu kosu.‚Äļ
\v 9 N…ôb…õr…õn…õ y…õb…ôc ya afum akaŇč…õ, p…ômar Ňčab…ôc yi nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčanc…ôŇčk…ôl s…Ē moloku ma yem mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē ab…õ a dacar k…Ē abum aYisrayel Ňčaloku afum: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē firawona oloku: ‚ÄĻIf…Ēs…Ēs…ĒŇč nu m…õmp…ôl…õ!
\v 11 N…ôk…Ē, n…ônas…ôrka n…ôt…õn m…õmp…ôl…õ nn…Ē o nn…Ē n…ôntam k…ôs…Ēt…Ē mi m…Ē, mba ali p…ôpic af…Ēdebeli y…õb…ôc yonu yeyeŇčki ny…õ p…ômar nu k…ôb…ôc m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\v 12 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčasams…ôr at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp, k…ôt…õn toka ya m…õmp…ôl…õ mosut…õ birik.
\v 13 Ab…õ a dacar aMisira Ňčacgb…ôŇč-gb…ôŇč…ôr Ňča, Ňčacloku: ¬ęN…ôkuf…õ n…ôlip y…õb…ôc yonu ya d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk, p…ôm…Ē c…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē nt…õ m…õmp…ôl…õ mencyi m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 14 Ňäanak…Ē haŇč Ňčacsut abum aYisrayel aŇč…õ ab…õ a Misira aka firawona Ňčanac…ômb…ôr…õ aka Yisrayel m…Ē, Ňčacyif Ňča: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ônt…Ēb…ôp…õ m…Ēk…Ē k…ôl…Ēm ka birik b…Ēk…Ē n…ôsutsa nendisna k…Ē nendecna m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē abum aYisrayel ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčabok…õn…õ nn…Ē firawona eyi m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē m…ônt…Ērs…õ tant…õ acar am-…õ?
\v 16 Ayi f…õ s…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč acar am m…õmp…ôl…õ, k'aŇčloku su s…Ē: ‚ÄĻN…ôsut birik!‚Äļ M…ôn…ôŇčk nt…õ aŇčsut acar am m…Ē, mba afum am yati, Ňčasar…õ kiciya.¬Ľ
\v 17 Mba k…Ē firawona oluks…õ Ňča: ¬ęN…ôna n…ôncemb…ôr, n…ôfan…õ! Ti t…Ē n…ôŇčlok…õn…õ: ‚ÄĻPaŇčk…Ēn loŇčn…õ MARIKI!‚Äļ
\v 18 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, n…ôk…Ē n…ôsump…ôr y…õb…ôc yonu. Af…Ēs…Ēs…ĒŇč nu m…õmp…ôl…õ, mba k…ôl…Ēm ka birik b…Ēk…Ē ambonc…ôr nu k…ôsut m…Ē, k…Ē n…ôndesut.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 19 K…Ē abum aYisrayel Ňča s…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk p…ôcuca p…Ēk…Ē Ňčayi m…Ē nt…õ aloku Ňča: ¬ęAf…Ēbeli k…ôl…Ēm ka birik b…Ēk…Ē ambonc…ôr nu k…ôsut d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē!¬Ľ
\v 20 Nt…õ ab…õ aŇč…õ Ňčancs…ĒŇč…ôs aka Yisrayel y…õb…ôc yeyeŇčki Ňčawur nda firawona m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…ôp Musa k…Ē Aruna aŇč…õ Ňčackar Ňča m…Ē.
\v 21 K…Ē abum aYisrayel Ňčaloku Musa k…Ē Aruna: ¬ęMARIKI p…ôm…Ēm…ôn nu, p…ôs…ĒŇč nu k…ôway! N…ôs…ĒŇč…õ firawona k…Ē amar…ôs …Ēn k…ôter su. N…ôl…õk sakma k…Ē n…ômb…õr Ňča d…ôwaca Ňčadif su!¬Ľ
\v 22 K…Ē Musa oluks…ôrn…õ nn…Ē MARIKI eyi m…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęMariki ta ake t…Ē m…ôy…Ēn…õ afum akaŇč…õ p…ôl…õc-…õ? It…Ē m…ônasom em ba?
\v 23 K…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ iŇčk…Ē ndena firawona k'ilok-lok…ôr k…Ē tewe tam m…Ē, p…ôl…õc d…ôm peyi k…ôy…Ē afum akaŇč…õ, m…ôyi f…õ k…ôy…Ē t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm m…ôbaŇč afum am.¬Ľ
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęK…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ē m…ônder oŇč, nt…õ indey…Ē firawona m…Ē: K…ôca ka f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr k'indes…ĒŇč…õn…õ k…Ē k…ôsak aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ē. T…Ēy…Ē ta k…ôca ka f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fem tendes…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē yati k…ôb…õl…ôs aka Yisrayel at…Ēf Ňč…Ēn disr…õ.¬Ľ
\s1 Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč Musa temer k…ôdewur…õ aka Yisrayel dacar
\p 
\v 2 K…Ē Kanu k…ôlok-lok…ôr s…Ē Musa, k…ôcloku k…Ē: ¬ęIn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI.
\v 3 Inawur…ôr Abraham, k'iwur…ôr Siyaka, k'iwur…ôr Yakuba, ina, Kanu nk…õ k…ôntam mes ma doru f…ôp m…Ē, mba t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē inas…ĒŇč…õ f…õ Ňča k…ôc…ôr…õ tewe tem ta ‚ÄĻMARIKI‚Äļ.
\v 4 Inasek s…Ē danapa k…Ē Ňča, k'is…ĒŇč Ňča KanaŇč at…Ēf nŇč…õ Ňčanccep…õ-cep…õ k…ônd…õ m…Ē.
\v 5 K'ine s…Ē kigbis ka aka Yisrayel aŇč…õ aka Misira Ňčayi k…ôt…Ērs…õ dacar m…Ē, k'inc…õm-c…õmn…õ danapa nd…õ inasek k…Ē Ňča m…Ē.
\v 6 Ti t…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēlok…õn…õ aka Yisrayel a in'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI, indewur…õ nu y…õb…ôc yeyeŇčki ny…õ aka Misira Ňčanc…ômb…ôr nu m…Ē, indewur…õ nu y…õb…ôc ny…õ aka Misira Ňčayi k…ôt…Ērs…õ nu m…Ē. F…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fem f'indewurs…õ nu Ňča d…ôwaca a ideboc…ôr Ňča kiti k…ôlel.
\v 7 IndebaŇč nu nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôy…Ēn…õ afum em, iy…Ēn…õ Kanu konu m…Ē. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē n…ôndec…ôr…õ s…Ē a in'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI Kanu konu, nk…õ k…ôwur…õ nu y…õb…ôc yeyeŇčki ny…õ aka Misira Ňčanc…ômb…ôr nu m…Ē.
\v 8 IŇčk…Ēb…õrs…õ nu at…Ēf nŇč…õ inadot k…ôca id…õrm…õ Abraham, Siyaka, k…Ē Yakuba k…ôs…ĒŇč nu m…Ē. Ina MARIKI iŇčk…Ēs…ĒŇč nu Ňči Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňčonu.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 9 Ti t…Ē Musa …õnaloku aka Yisrayel, mba Ňčancne f…õ t…Ēk…Ē Musa oncloku Ňča m…Ē. B…ôk…ôc y…õnaf…ôf…ôr…õn…õ Ňča teta y…õb…ôc yeyeŇčki y…Ēk…Ē Ňčanayi disr…õ m…Ē.
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē MARIKI oloku s…Ē Musa:
\v 11 ¬ęM…ôk…Ē m…ôloku firawona w…ôb…õ ka Misira a p…ôsak aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ē, Ňčawur at…Ēf Ňč…Ēn.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 12 K…Ē Musa oloku f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč: ¬ęK…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčant…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl im, c…ôke c…Ē firawona …ĒŇčk…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl im-…õ, ina nw…õ ilel…õ temer m…Ē?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 13 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Aruna, k'osom Ňča teta aka Yisrayel k…Ē firawona w…ôb…õ ka Misira, Ňčawur…õn…õ aka Yisrayel at…Ēf Ňča Misira.
\s1 Mewe ma atem a Musa k…Ē Aruna
\mi1 
\v 14 Mewe ma akiriŇč aŇčan d…ôw…Ēl…Ē m…Ē mm…õ:
\b
\pi1 Awut a Ruben Coco ca Yisrayel (Yakuba): Henok, Palu, Hec…ôr…ĒŇč k…Ē Karmi. Cor ca Ruben c…ônayi cac…Ēk…Ē.
\pi1 
\v 15 Awut a Simey…ĒŇč: Yemuy…õl, Yamin, Ohad, Yakin k…Ē Cohar, Sawul w…ôk…Ē w…ôKanaŇčara …õnakom…õ k…Ē m…Ē. Cor ca Simey…ĒŇč c…ônayi cac…Ēk…Ē.
\pi1 
\v 16 Mewe ma awut a Lewy m…Ē mm…õ t…Ēk…Ē ŇčaŇčkom…õn…õ m…Ē: Kerson, Kehat k…Ē Merari. K…ôwon ka Lewy doru k…ônab…ôp meren tasar tin w…ôco maas k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (137).
\pi1 
\v 17 Awut a Kerson: Libni k…Ē Simeyi, k…Ē cor c…ôŇčan.
\pi1 
\v 18 Awut a Kehat: Amram, Yicahar, Heb…ôr…ĒŇč k…Ē Usiy…õl. K…ôwon ka Kehat doru k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren tasar tin w…ôco maas k…Ē maas (133).
\pi1 
\v 19 Awut a Merari: Mali k…Ē Musi.
\pi1 Cor ca Lewy c…ônayi cac…Ēk…Ē k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē anacic…ôs taruku ta dokomb…ôra da Lewy disr…õ m…Ē.
\pi1 
\v 20 K…Ē Amram …õn…õnc…õ w…ôran nw…õ ancwe Yok…õb…õd w…ôkir…õ ka kas m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôkak…Ē oŇčkom…õ k…Ē Aruna k…Ē Musa. K…ôwon ka Amram doru k…ônas…Ēt…Ē meren tasar tin w…ôco maas k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (137).
\pi1 
\v 21 Awut a Yicahar: Kore, Nef…õk k…Ē Sikiri.
\pi1 
\v 22 Awut a Usiy…õl: Misayel, ElcafaŇč k…Ē Sitiri.
\pi1 
\v 23 K…Ē Aruna …õn…õnc…õ w…ôran nw…õ ancwe Eliseba m…Ē, wan ka Aminadab w…ôran, w…ôkir…õ ka Nas…ĒŇč. K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē oŇčkom…õ k…Ē Nadab, Abihu, Elasar k…Ē Itamar.
\pi1 
\v 24 Awut a Kore: Asir, Elkana k…Ē Abiyasaf. Cor ca Kore c…ônayi cac…Ēk…Ē.
\pi1 
\v 25 K…Ē Elasar, wan ka Aruna, …õn…õnc…õ w…ôran awut aran a Putiyel dac…Ē, k…Ē w…ôkak…Ē oŇčkom…õ k…Ē wan w…ôrkun nw…õ anawe Finehas m…Ē. AkiriŇč a cor ca Lewy Ňč'akak…Ē.
\p 
\v 26 Afum akaŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňč…Ē MARIKI …õnaloku: ¬ęN…ôwur…õn…õ aka Yisrayel at…Ēf Ňča Misira d…ôcor d…ôcor.¬Ľ
\v 27 Aruna k…Ē Musa yati Ňčanalok-lok…ôr firawona w…ôb…õ w…ôka Misira teta k…ôwur…õn…õ ka aka Yisrayel at…Ēf Ňča Misira.
\s1 Kanu k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč ka Musa temer
\p 
\v 28 D…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ MARIKI …õnalok-lok…ôr Musa nde at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē,
\v 29 k…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęIn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI. M…ôk…Ē m…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ m…ôloku firawona w…ôb…õ ka Misira moloku f…ôp mm…õ ilok'…ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 30 K…Ē Musa oloku f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč: ¬ęIna nw…õ ilel…õ temer m…Ē: C…ôke c…Ē firawona …ĒŇčk…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl im-…õ?¬Ľ
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im, indes…ĒŇč'am k…ôy…Ēn…õ kanu nn…Ē firawona eyi m…Ē. W…õnc …ôm Aruna nk…Ēn ended…ôŇčk mi, nk…Ēn p…ôy…Ēn…õ sayib…õ sam.
\v 2 M…ôn'endek…Ē m…ôcloku t…Ēk…Ē indek…Ē icsom …ôm f…ôp, w…õnc …ôm p…ôcgb…Ēk…ôr…õn…õ mi firawona, nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôsak aka Yisrayel Ňčawur at…Ēf Ňč…Ēn m…Ē.
\v 3 K…Ē ina, in'…ĒŇčk…Ē icyeŇčk…ôs firawona domp, icy…Ē Misira m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…õw…õy-w…õy k…Ē m…Ēy…Ē m…Ēp…ĒŇč m…õlar…ôm.
\v 4 Firawona …Ēf…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl nu. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t'iŇčk…Ēsut…õ Misira k…ôca kem, iwur…õn…õ aka Yisrayel afum em d…ôcor d…ôcor, citi c…ôp…ĒŇč c'indewur…õn…õ Ňča at…Ēf Ňča Misira.
\v 5 Aka Misira Ňčandec…ôr…õ a in'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI nt…õ indesut…õ Ňča k…ôca kem, iwur…õn…õ aka Yisrayel di m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 6 Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčay…Ē belbel t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Ňča m…Ē.
\v 7 T…õnat…ôŇčn…õ Musa p…ôs…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco cam…ôt-maas (80), k…Ē w…õnc Aruna meren w…ôco cam…ôt-maas k…Ē maas (83), t…õm nt…õ Ňčanclok-lok…ôr firawona m…Ē.
\s1 Firawona …õfati k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl Musa k…Ē Aruna
\p 
\v 8 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Aruna:
\v 9 ¬ęT…õm nt…õ firawona endeloku: ‚ÄĻN…ôy…Ē t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ t…õw…õy-w…õy m…Ē,‚Äļ m…ôna m…ôloku Aruna: ‚ÄĻM…ôl…õk k…ôgbo kam m…ôl…ôm ki firawona d…ônt…Ēf.‚Äļ K…ôgbo kaŇčk…Ē k…ôndet…ôŇčk…ôl…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ abok.¬Ľ
\v 10 K…Ē Musa ŇčaŇčk…Ē k…Ē Aruna nde firawona eyi m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Ňča m…Ē. K…Ē Aruna …õl…ôm k…ôgbo k…Ēn d…ônt…Ēf f…Ēr ya firawona k…Ē amar…ôs …Ēn kiriŇč, k…Ē k…ôgbo kaŇčk…Ē k…ônt…ôŇčk…ôl…õ abok.
\v 11 Mba k…Ē firawona ewe as…õr k…Ē ac…ôr…õ mes a Misira. Dure f…ôp faŇčan k…Ē Ňča s…Ē Ňčay…Ē tin tayi.
\v 12 Akak…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčal…ôm…ôs c…ôgbo c…ôŇčan d…ônt…Ēf, k…Ē c…ônt…ôŇčk…ôl…õ bok. Mba k…Ē k…ôgbo ka Aruna k…ômer…ôs c…ôgbo c…ôŇčan.
\v 13 K…Ē firawona eyeŇčk s…Ē domp, k'…õfati k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl Musa k…Ē Aruna p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnaloku ti m…Ē.
\s1 P…ôl…õc p…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē: Domun da Nil d…õnt…ôŇčk…ôl…õ mecir
\p 
\v 14 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęFirawona …õntaŇč al…ôŇč…ôs, …õfati k…ôsak aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ē.
\v 15 B…ôtb…ôtana, m…ôdena m…ôk…Ē m…ôb…ôp firawona t…õm nt…õ endena p…ôcder nde d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē m…Ē. M…ôdena m…ôc…ôm…õ m…ôkar k…Ē nde agb…õp Ňča k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Nil, m…ôt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôgbo kaŇčk…Ē k…ônat…ôŇčk…ôl…õ abok m…Ē.
\v 16 M…ôdena s…Ē m…ôloku firawona: ‚ÄĻMARIKI Kanu k'aHeb…ôre k…ôsom im nn…Ē m…ôyi m…Ē, idelok'…ôm: M…ôsak afum em Ňčak…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčak…Ē Ňčasal…õn'em nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē.‚Äļ Mba m…ôna, haŇč nd…õk…ôl m…ôyi f…õ k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl ti.
\v 17 Nt…õ t…Ē MARIKI oloku: ‚ÄĻTant…õ tendes…ĒŇč'am k…ôc…ôr…õ a in'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI: K…ôsut…õ k'inder domun da k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Nil k…ôgbo kaŇčk…õ, d…õt…ôŇčk…ôl…õ d…Ēy…Ēn…õ mecir.
\v 18 Lop ny…õ yeyi d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, yendefi. Domun da d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē dendes…õn p…ôl…õc, aka Misira Ňčaf…Ēdewos…õ s…Ē k…ômun ka domun da k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē kaŇčk…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\v 19 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôloku Aruna: M…ôl…õk k…ôgbo kam m…ôcenc k…ôca kam domun da Misira k…ôroŇč k…ôy…õf…õ ka domun da d…ôs…ôbo k…ôb…ôp ka da d…ôs…ôŇčgb…ôl, haŇč da d…ôcumbul k…ôk…Ē ka da y…õm…õŇčk…õ domun yaŇčan f…ôp.¬Ľ Domun dendet…ôŇčk…ôl…õ mecir, mecir mendeyi Misira f…ôp, haŇč d…ôy…õm…õŇčk…õ domun ya masar k…Ē ya t…Ēk.
\p 
\v 20 Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčanay…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Ňča m…Ē. K…Ē Musa eyekti k…ôgbo k…ôsut…õ ki domun da Nil f…Ēr ya firawona k…Ē amar…ôs …Ēn kiriŇč, k…Ē domun da d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē f…ôp d…õnt…ôŇčk…ôl…õ mecir.
\v 21 K…Ē lop ny…õ y…õnayi k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Nil m…Ē f…ôp yefi, k…Ē domun da Nil d…õs…õn p…ôl…õc, aka Misira Ňčanctam f…õ s…Ē k…ômun domun da Nil, k…Ē mecir meyi Misira f…ôp.
\v 22 K…Ē dure aka Misira Ňčay…Ē deser daŇčan f…ôp. K…Ē firawona eyeŇčk s…Ē domp, …õnc…ôŇčk…ôl f…õ Musa k…Ē Aruna, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnaloku ti m…Ē.
\v 23 K…Ē firawona olukus nde nd…Ēr…Ēn, …õnab…õr f…õ m…Ēy…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē d…õb…ôk…ôc.
\p 
\v 24 K…Ē aka Misira f…ôp ŇčaŇčkay…ôs c…ôl…ômp nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Nil k…ôs…ôk nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēt…Ē domun domun m…Ē, bawo Ňčanctam f…õ s…Ē k…ômun domun da Nil.
\v 25 K…Ē mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč mencep…ôr k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ MARIKI osut domun da Nil m…Ē.
\s1 Pucuy pa m…õr…ôŇč: F…ônt…ôl
\p 
\v 26 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôde m…ôk…Ē nde firawona eyi m…Ē, m…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI oloku: M…ôsak afum em Ňčak…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčak…Ē Ňčasal…õn'em m…Ē.
\v 27 K…Ē m…ôfati k…ôsak Ňča Ňčak…Ē-…õ, ina MARIKI, iŇčsut…õ at…Ēf Ňčam f…ônt…ôl.
\v 28 K…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Nil k…ôndes…õp f…ônt…ôl, ny…õ yendep…õ y…õb…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē kam disr…õ, y…õb…õr…õ nde d…ôk…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ dam, y…õp…õs…õ nde k…ôf…ônc kam, y…õb…õr…õ s…Ē nde w…Ēl…Ē wa amar…ôs am k…Ē afum am f…ôp, yendeb…õr…õ s…Ē nde anc…Ēf'am c…ôcom, haŇč amp…Ēc…ôk'am c…ôcom m…Ē.
\v 29 F…ônt…ôl yendef…ôr…ôŇčk …ôm, y…õf…ôr…ôŇčk afum am k…Ē amar…ôs am f…ôp.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\c 8
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ t…Ē k…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôloku Aruna: ‚ÄĻM…ôcenc k…ôca kam k…Ē k…ôgbo kam k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē k…ôroŇč, nde d…ôs…ôŇčgb…ôl sa Nil f…ôp, haŇč nde d…ôcumbul, m…ôp…õn…õ f…ônt…ôl at…Ēf Ňča Misira.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\v 2 K…Ē Aruna encenc k…ôca k…Ēn domun da Misira k…ôroŇč, k…Ē f…ônt…ôl y…õmp…õ k…Ē yoŇčkump ant…Ēf Ňča Misira.
\v 3 K…Ē dure k…Ē deser daŇčan Ňča s…Ē Ňčay…Ē p…ôm…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamp…õn…õ f…ônt…ôl ant…Ēf Ňča Misira.
\p 
\v 4 K…Ē firawona ewe Musa k…Ē Aruna k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôtolan…õ su MARIKI p…ôb…Ēl…õn'em f…ônt…ôl yay…õ k…Ē afum em. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē iŇčsak afum aka Yisrayel, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčak…Ē ŇčaloŇčn…õ MARIKI m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 5 K…Ē Musa oloku firawona: ¬ęP…ôlel pam, ake t…õm t'indetolan'on, k…Ē amar…ôs am, k…Ē afum aka at…Ēf Ňčam, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôs…Ēl…õn…õ f…ônt…ôl ya nde ndaram k…Ē ya nde w…Ēl…Ē wam, p…ôc…ôm…õ ya nde d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē gb…ôc…ôr…ôm ny…õ …Ēnt…ĒdeliŇč m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 6 K…Ē firawona oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôy…Ē ti alna.¬Ľ K…Ē Musa oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTendeyi p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ôloku ti m…Ē, t…Ēs…ĒŇč'am k…ôc…ôr…õ a ali fum eyi f…õ p…ôm…Ē MARIKI Kanu kosu!
\v 7 F…ônt…ôl yendeb…Ēl'am k…Ē w…Ēl…Ē wam, k'amar…ôs am, k'afum am, m…õn…õ nde d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Nil gb…ôc…ôr…ôm yendeyi.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 8 Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčawur ndena firawona, k…Ē Musa …õl…õts…õn…õ MARIKI teta f…ônt…ôl ny…õ …õnak…õr…õ firawona k…ôt…Ēr…ôs k…Ēn m…Ē.
\v 9 K…Ē MARIKI …Ēy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnaloku k…Ē m…Ē. K…Ē f…ônt…ôl yefis-fis k…ôy…õf…õ nde d…ôw…Ēl…Ē, d…ôc…ôbaŇčka haŇč nde dal…õ.
\v 10 K'aloŇčka-loŇčka yi m…õp…õsa m…õp…õsa, k…Ē amb…Ēnc Ňča p…ôte pa yi Ňčosump…ôr at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp.
\p 
\v 11 Mba nt…õ firawona …õn…ôŇčk a k…ôŇčes…ôm k…ônder m…Ē, k'eyeŇčk s…Ē domp, …õnc…ôŇčk…ôl f…õ s…Ē Musa k…Ē Aruna p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnaloku ti m…Ē.
\s1 P…ôcuy pa maas: Mes-y…õŇčaŇč
\p 
\v 12 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôloku Aruna: ‚ÄĻM…ôcenc k…ôgbo kam, m…ôsut…õ ki k…ôbof ka d…ônt…Ēf.‚Äļ K…ôbof kaŇčk…Ē k…ôndet…ôŇčk…ôl…õ mes-y…õŇčaŇč Misira f…ôp.¬Ľ
\v 13 It…Ē Ňčanay…Ē. K…Ē Aruna encenc k…ôgbo k…Ēn k'osut…õ ki k…ôbof ka d…ônt…Ēf. K…Ē k…ôbof kaŇčk…Ē k…ônt…ôŇčk…ôl…õ mes ny…õ y…õncŇčaŇč afum k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôbof ka at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp k…ôy…Ēn…õ mes.
\v 14 K…Ē dure Ňča s…Ē Ňčawak…ôs deser daŇčan f…ôp nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča s…Ē Ňčawur…õ mes-y…õŇčaŇč m…Ē, mba Ňčanatam f…õ. K…Ē mes y…õlar-lar afum k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl.
\v 15 K…Ē dure Ňčaloku firawona: ¬ęK…ôca ka Kanu k…Ē!¬Ľ Mba firawona encyeŇčk k…ôyeŇčk d…ôm domp, owos…õ f…õ k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl Musa k…Ē Aruna, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnaloku ti m…Ē.
\s1 P…ôcuy pa maŇčk…ôl…õ: WaŇčk…ôp
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôde m…ôy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy, m…ôk…Ē m…ôc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēk…Ē firawona encep…ôr m…Ē. K'ende k…ôcwur k…ôk…Ē ka nde d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē-…õ, m…ôde m…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI oloku: M…ôsak afum em nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčak…Ē Ňčasal…õn'em m…Ē!
\v 17 K…Ē m…ônt…Ēsak afum em Ňčak…Ē-…õ, iŇčw…õn…ôr'on k…ônay ka waŇčk…ôp y…õlar…ôm, k…ôy…õf…õ m…ôna, k…ôk…Ē amar…ôs am, k…ôb…ôp afum am haŇč w…Ēl…Ē wam. W…Ēl…Ē wa aka Misira wendelar…õ waŇčk…ôp haŇč yokump ant…Ēf nŇč…õ Ňčayi m…Ē.
\v 18 Mba d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē indegb…õy at…Ēf Ňča Kos…õŇč nde afum em Ňčayi m…Ē, d…ôndo taŇč waŇčk…ôp y…õlar…ôm y…Ēf…Ēk…Ēyi di, is…ĒŇč'am oŇč k…ôc…ôr…õ a ina, MARIKI, iyi at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ dac…Ē.
\v 19 Indeboc t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ afum em k…Ē afum am dac…Ē, nt…õ tendey…Ēn…õ t…õyac…õ ta afum em m…Ē. Alna t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ t…õw…õy-w…õy tat…Ēk…Ē teŇčyi.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\p 
\v 20 K…Ē MARIKI …Ēy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē waŇčk…ôp y…õlar…ôm yender nde k…ôl…Ē ka firawona k…Ē nde k…ôl…Ē ka amar…ôs …Ēn, k…Ē nde at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp k…Ē waŇčk…ôp y…õlar…ôm yay…Ēk…Ē y…õl…ôs…ôr at…Ēf.
\v 21 K…Ē firawona ewe Musa k…Ē Aruna, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē n…ôloŇčn…õ Kanu konu nn…Ē at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ disr…õ.¬Ľ
\v 22 K…Ē Musa oluks…õ firawona: ¬ęP…ôntes…õ f…õ k…ôy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē, bawo k…ôloŇčn…õ nk…õ s…ôŇčk…ĒloŇčn…õ MARIKI Kanu kosu m…Ē, k…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ē nk…õ k…ôyik-yik aka Misira m…Ē teta din…õ daŇčan, k…Ē s…ôloŇčn…õ ki f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč-…õ, baf…Ē Ňčandeca-cas su ba?
\v 23 Mata maas m…Ē s…ôndek…Ēt nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ a s…ôk…ĒloŇčn…õ MARIKI Kanu kosu, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ēloku su ti m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 24 K…Ē firawona oloku: ¬ęIna k…ôsak nu k'inder n…ôk…ĒloŇčn…õ MARIKI Kanu konu nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ. Mba ta n…ôb…Ēl…õ de, n…ôtolan…õn'em!¬Ľ
\v 25 K…Ē Musa oloku firawona: ¬ęInck…Ēwur nn…Ē ndaram intola MARIKI, alna tuŇč waŇčk…ôp y…õlar…ôm yay…õ y…Ēmb…Ēl…õ firawona, amar…ôs …Ēn k…Ē afum …Ēn. Mba ta firawona p…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôyemb…ôr su, ta p…ôfati k…ôsak aka Yisrayel Ňčak…ĒloŇčn…õ MARIKI.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 26 Nt…õ Musa owur ndena firawona m…Ē, k'ontola MARIKI.
\v 27 K…Ē MARIKI …Ēy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnaloku k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē waŇčk…ôp y…õlar…ôm y…Ēmb…Ēl…õ firawona, k…Ē afum …Ēn, k…Ē amar…ôs …Ēn. Ali awaŇčk…ôp Ňčin Ňč…õnayi f…õ s…Ē Misira.
\p 
\v 28 Mba k…Ē firawona …õntaŇč al…ôŇč…ôs, owos…õ f…õ k…ôsak aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ē.
\c 9
\s1 P…ôcuy pa k…ôcam…ôt: Docu da y…Ēc…Ēl
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē m…ôb…ôp firawona, m…ôk…Ē m…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI, Kanu ka aHeb…ôre k…ôloku: M…ôsak afum em Ňčak…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčak…Ē Ňčasal…õn'em m…Ē.‚Äļ
\v 2 K…Ē m…ôfati k…ôsak Ňča Ňčak…Ē, m…ôwon s…Ē k…ôsump…ôr Ňča s…Ē-…õ,
\v 3 MARIKI oŇčsut…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yam k…ôca ny…õ yeyi d…ôkulum m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ ka f…ôl…õs k…ôb…ôp ka s…Ēfale, y…Ēk…Ēm…õ k…ôk…Ē ka nde c…ôna k…Ē Ňčkesiya yeyi m…Ē, yendes…Ēt…Ē arom Ňč…õl…õc.
\v 4 Mba MARIKI endegb…õy y…Ēc…Ēl ya aka Yisrayel nn…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl ya aka Misira yeyi m…Ē, ali p…Ēc…Ēl pin p…Ēf…Ēdefi y…Ēc…Ēl ya aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.
\v 5 MARIKI ombonc d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ toncop m…Ē, oloku a alna …ĒŇčy…Ē ti at…Ēf Ňča Misira disr…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 6 K…Ē MARIKI …Ēy…Ē ti d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk. K…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl ya aka Misira yefi, ali p…Ēc…Ēl pa aka Yisrayel pin p…õnafi f…õ.
\v 7 K…Ē firawona osom pak…Ē pat…õn mes mam…Ēk…Ē. K'aŇčk…Ē pab…ôp ali p…Ēc…Ēl pa aka Yisrayel pin p…õnafi f…õ. Mba haŇč t…õm tant…õ firawona …õntaŇč al…ôŇč…ôs, …õsak f…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ē.
\s1 P…ôcuy pa cam…ôt-tin: B…õc…õ
\p 
\v 8 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Aruna: ¬ęN…ôw…õt asum Ňča kar…Ēr…Ē k…ôca pet, Musa p…ôl…ôm Ňči darenc f…Ēr ya firawona kiriŇč.
\v 9 Asum ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčendet…ôŇčk…ôl…õ k…ôf…ôl at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp k…ôroŇč. K…ôf…ôl kaŇčk…Ē k…ôndes…ĒŇč at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ afum k…ôb…ôp ka y…Ēc…Ēl p…ôk…ôf…ôr-k…ôf…ôr mp…õ pendey…Ēn…õ Ňča b…õc…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 10 Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčaw…õt asum Ňča kar…Ēr…Ē k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp firawona, k…Ē Musa …õl…ôm asum ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē darenc, k…Ē Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč afum k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl b…õc…õ ya arom.
\v 11 Dure aMisira Ňčanctam f…õ k…ôc…ôm…õ Musa f…Ēr kiriŇč, teta b…õc…õ ny…õ y…õnawur Ňča p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē y…õnawur aka Misira f…ôp m…Ē.
\v 12 K…Ē MARIKI …Ēnc…ĒŇč…ôs s…Ē firawona k…ôyeŇčk domp, …õnc…ôŇčk…ôl f…õ Ňča s…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnaloku ti Musa m…Ē.
\s1 P…ôcuy pa cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč: Let…ôr
\p 
\v 13 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôde m…ôy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy, m…ôk…Ē m…ôment…ôrn…õ firawona kiriŇč. M…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI, Kanu ka aHeb…ôre k…ôloku: M…ôsak afum em Ňčak…Ē, Ňčasal…õn'em.
\v 14 Bawo tant…õ taŇč m…ôn'indes…ĒŇč pucuy pem f…ôp, k…ôy…õf…õ ka amar…ôs am k…ôb…ôp ka afum am f…ôp, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ m…ôc…ôr…õ a paka mp…õ o mp…õ powur…õn…õ f…õ k…Ē ina doru dand…õ.
\v 15 Inacenc k…ôca isut am arom, m…ôna k…Ē afum am-…õ, k…Ē m…ôm…ôlk…õ nt…õ doru dand…õ.
\v 16 Mba isak …ôm k…Ē m…ôyi doru nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ iment…ôr …ôm f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fem, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ s…Ē tewe tem t…õsams…ôr doru f…ôp m…Ē.
\v 17 K…Ē m…ômp…ôt…ôs s…Ē afum em, m…ôsak f…õ Ňča Ňčak…Ē-…õ,
\v 18 intuf…ôr aka Misira alna dec dand…õ let…ôr d…õlar…ôm nd…õ d…õntat…Ētuf Misira k…ôy…õf…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ moncop m…Ē haŇč nd…õk…ôl.
\v 19 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, m…ôsom nde dal…õ pak…õr…õ p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ o mp…õ k…Ē daka nd…õ o nd…õ d…Ēy…Ēn…õ dam m…Ē, let…ôr dendetor…ôr afum k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl f…ôp k…ôroŇč ny…õ yeyi dal…õ ta aloŇčka yi d…ôk…ôl…Ē m…Ē, yendefi.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\p 
\v 20 Amar…ôs a firawona aŇč…õ Ňčananes…õ toloku ta MARIKI m…Ē, Ňčamb…õrs…õ acar aŇčan k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan d…ôc…ôk…õr kat…ôna.
\v 21 Mba aŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ēb…õr moloku ma MARIKI d…õb…ôk…ôc m…Ē, Ňčasak acar aŇčan k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan dal…õ disr…õ.
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôp…õn…õ k…ôca kam darenc, let…ôr dotor at…Ēf Ňča Misira disr…õ f…ôp, afum k…ôroŇč, y…Ēc…Ēl k…ôroŇč k…Ē yika ya dal…õ da Misira k…ôroŇč.¬Ľ
\v 23 K…Ē Musa …õmp…õn…õ k…ôgbo k…Ēn darenc, k…Ē MARIKI owur…õ dim da pukul…õ-kul…õ, k…Ē let…ôr dontor, k…Ē d…õw…õ dosut ant…Ēf. K…Ē MARIKI ontor…õ let…ôr d…ônt…Ēf p…ôp…ĒŇč.
\v 24 K…Ē let…ôr dontor, n…õnc d…õcc…õs…ôŇč…õ let…ôr dac…Ē. K…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ doru d…õnacop m…Ē haŇč m…Ēk…Ē, let…ôr, afef k…Ē d…õw…õ y…õntator f…õ Misira p…ôm…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē.
\v 25 K…Ē let…ôr dontor…ôr ca y…Ēk…Ē y…õnayi dal…õ m…Ē f…ôp, ant…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ ka afum k…ôb…ôp ka y…Ēc…Ēl. K…Ē let…ôr dosut s…Ē yika ya dal…õ f…ôp, k…Ē dentep-tepi s…Ē t…Ēk ya dal…õ f…ôp.
\v 26 At…Ēf Ňča Kos…õŇč gb…ôc…ôr…ôm nde aka Yisrayel Ňčanayi m…Ē, Ňč…Ē let…ôr d…õnat…Ētor.
\p 
\v 27 K…Ē firawona osom pawen…õ k…Ē Musa k…Ē Aruna k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęTant…õ taŇč, inciya. MARIKI olomp, ina k…Ē afum em s…ôn'eciya.
\v 28 N…ôtola MARIKI. Pukul…õ-kul…õ k…Ē let…ôr y…õc…ôm…õ! IŇčsak nu n…ôk…Ē, af…Ēs…Ēc…ômb…ôr…ôs nu k…ôk…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 29 K…Ē Musa oloku firawona: ¬ęK…Ē indenawur dare-…õ, indep…õn…õ waca wem nde MARIKI eyi m…Ē. Pukul…õ-kul…õ pendenasak…õ, let…ôr d…Ēf…Ēdenayi, tendes…ĒŇč'am k…ôc…ôr…õ a doru dand…õ da MARIKI d…Ē.
\v 30 Mba inc…ôr…õ a m…ôna k…Ē amar…ôs am, n…ôf…Ēdes…Ēnes…õ MARIKI Kanu.¬Ľ
\v 31 Akotan Ňč…õnal…õŇčk, pundu pokom let…ôr d…õnas…ĒŇč…õ yi k…ôl…õc…õ.
\v 32 Mba m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ēl…Ēma m…õnal…õc…õ f…õ, bawo mi moncwon k…ôkom, ti t…Ē let…ôr d…õnat…Ēl…ôs…ôr…õ mi.
\v 33 K…Ē Musa owur ndena firawona k…Ē dare disr…õ, k…Ē Musa encenc…ôr MARIKI waca. Pukul…õ-kul…õ pa darenc k…Ē let…ôr y…õsak…õ, k…Ē w…ôcaf…ôn …õsak k…ôtuf.
\p 
\v 34 Nt…õ firawona …õn…ôŇčk w…ôcaf…ôn, k…Ē let…ôr y…õsak k…ôtuf k…Ē pukul…õ-kul…õ pa darenc p…õsak…õ m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôciya k'…õntaŇč al…ôŇč…ôs, nk…Ēn k…Ē amar…ôs …Ēn.
\v 35 K…Ē firawona eyeŇčk domp, …õsak f…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnas…ĒŇč…õ ti Musa k…ôloku m…Ē.
\c 10
\s1 P…ôcuy pa cam…ôt-maas: C…ôlaŇčk…ôma
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē m…ôb…ôp firawona, bawo in'endes…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôtaŇč al…ôŇč…ôs, nk…Ēn k…Ē amar…ôs …Ēn, nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ iment…ôr m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…õw…õy-w…õy mem f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč m…Ē.
\v 2 Nt…õ tendes…ĒŇč'am k…ôs…Ēt…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ônde m…ôcloku awut am k…Ē awut-s…Ē am m…Ē, mes mm…õ iy…Ē aMisira, k…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…õw…õy-w…õy mm…õ iwur…õ ndaraŇčan m…Ē. Tendes…ĒŇč'on k…ôc…ôr…õ a in'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 3 Musa k…Ē Aruna ŇčaŇčk…Ē nde firawona eyi m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI Kanu ka aHeb…ôre k…ôloku: Ake t…õm t…Ē m…ôndesak k…ôfati k…ôtontn…õn'em-…õ? M…ôsak afum em Ňčak…Ēsal…õn'em.
\v 4 K…Ē m…ôfati k…ôsak afum em Ňčak…Ē-…õ, alna iŇčk…õr…õ c…ôlaŇčk…ôma at…Ēf Ňčam.
\v 5 C…ôndekump at…Ēf Ňčam ali ant…Ēf ta aŇčn…ôŇčk-…õ. Ci c…ôndes…Ēm y…Ēb…Ēf y…õlp…ôs ny…õ let…ôr d…õsak m…Ē, c…ôndes…Ēm t…Ēk yonu y…Ēk…Ē yeyi k…ôpoŇč nde d…ôkulum m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 6 C…ôndelas w…Ēl…Ē wam, w…Ēl…Ē wa amar…ôs am, k…Ē w…Ēl…Ē wa aka Misira f…ôp. K…ôy…õf…õ awisi aŇča k…ôb…ôp ka atem am, ali w…ôkin …õn…ôŇčk f…õ towur…õn…õ ta ti haŇč m…Ēk…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Musa …õmb…õr firawona kumunt, k'owur nd…Ēr…Ēn.
\v 7 K…Ē amar…ôs a firawona Ňčayif k…Ē: ¬ęAke t…õm t…Ē fum w…ôkaw…õ endesak k…ôy…Ēn…õ su towul-…õ? M…ôsak afum aŇč…õ Ňčak…Ēsal…õn…õ MARIKI, Kanu k…ôŇčan. M…ôntac…ôr…õ f…õ a Misira meyi k…ôl…õc…õ ba?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 8 K'aŇčk…Ē s…Ē pawe Musa k…Ē Aruna, k…Ē Ňčander nn…Ē firawona eyi m…Ē. K…Ē firawona oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôntam k…ôk…Ēsal…õn…õ MARIKI, Kanu konu. Mba are ŇčaŇčk…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 9 K…Ē Musa oloku k…Ē: ¬ęS…ôŇčk…Ē k…Ē at…õmp asu, atem asu, s…ôŇčk…Ē k…Ē awut asu arkun k…Ē ayec…ôra, s…ôŇčk…Ē k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yosu y…Ēp…ĒŇč k…Ē y…õf…õt, bawo k…ôsata ka MARIKI k…Ē nn…Ē s…ôna s…ôyi m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 10 Mba k…Ē firawona oloku Ňča: ¬ęMARIKI p…ômar nu k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ icsak nu n…ôk…Ē n…ôna k…Ē aran anu k…Ē awut anu-…õ! T…Ēs…Ēk p…õs a n…ôy…Ē m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ m…õl…õc!
\v 11 T…õfaŇč tonu t…Ēf…Ētam k…ôk…Ēt! N…ôna arkun n…ôk…Ē n…ôsal…õn…õ MARIKI, tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē n…ôfaŇč!¬Ľ K'amb…õl…ôs Ňča firawona f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\p 
\v 12 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôcenc k…ôca at…Ēf Ňča Misira, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ c…ôlaŇčk…ôma k…ôder m…Ē, c…ôp…õ, c…ôs…Ēm yika ya d…Ēt…Ēf f…ôp k…Ē yobuk y…õlp…ôs ny…õ let…ôr d…õnasak at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 13 K…Ē Musa encenc k…ôgbo k…Ēn at…Ēf Ňča Misira, k…Ē MARIKI owur…õ afef k…ôy…õf…õ ka ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…Ē afef Ňčowur Misira d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē f…ôp pibi k…Ē p…ôwaŇčk…ôra. Dec dendes…Ēk, afef Ňča ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē Ňč…õŇčk…õr…õ c…ôlaŇčk…ôma.
\v 14 K…Ē c…ôlaŇčk…ôma c…ômp…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp, k…Ē c…ônd…õs-d…õs mofo f…ôp Misira disr…õ. Nt…õ t…Ē doru doncop c…ôlaŇčk…ôma c…ôntayi f…õ p…ôm…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē, c…ôf…Ēs…Ēyi p…ôm…Ē ti.
\v 15 K…Ē c…ôlaŇčk…ôma c…ôŇčkump ant…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp, k…Ē c…ômbiy…ôs…ôr ant…Ēf. K…Ē c…ôs…Ēm yika ya d…ônt…Ēf f…ôp, k…Ē yokom ya t…Ēk f…ôp, k…Ē ca nc…õ let…ôr d…õnasak m…Ē f…ôp. Misira disr…õ f…ôp anasak f…õ ali pubuk pin pa k…ôt…Ēk k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ pa ayika Ňča dal…õ.
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē firawona …õmb…õlk…ôr k…ôwe ka Musa k…Ē Aruna. K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęInciyan…õ MARIKI Kanu konu, k'inciyan…õ s…Ē n…ôna.
\v 17 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč il…õts…õn'am m…ôŇčaŇčn…õn'em kiciya kem t…õlp…ôs tant…õ. N…ôtolan'em nn…Ē MARIKI Kanu konu eyi m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôluks'em dar…ôŇč defi dand…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 18 K…Ē Musa owur ndena firawona, k'ontola MARIKI.
\v 19 K…Ē MARIKI …õŇčkaf…ôli afef Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč nŇč…õ Ňč…õnay…õf…õ k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, afef ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnaf…õl…ôr…õn…õ c…ôlaŇčk…ôma cac…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē ŇčeŇčkek…ôr…õ nde k…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma. Ali k…ôlaŇčkma kin afef ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnasak f…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp.
\v 20 Mba k…Ē MARIKI eyeŇčk…ôs s…Ē firawona domp, k…Ē firawona …õfati k…ôsak ka aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ē.
\s1 P…ôcuy pa cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ: Kubump
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôcenc k…ôca kam darenc, kubump k…ôtor at…Ēf Ňča Misira, kubump ka k…ôwak…ôs.¬Ľ
\v 22 K…Ē Musa encenc k…ôca k…Ēn darenc, k…Ē kubump ka k…ôwak…ôs k…ôntor at…Ēf Ňča Misira f…ôp haŇč mata maas.
\v 23 Nw…õ o nw…õ …õncn…ôŇčk f…õ w…ôk…Ē, ali fum …õnctam f…õ k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôkiyi d…Ēn haŇč mata maas. Mba aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčanay…Ē p…ôwaŇčk…ôra nde Ňčanayi m…Ē.
\p 
\v 24 K…Ē firawona ewe Musa k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē n…ôsal…õn…õ MARIKI! Mba y…Ēc…Ēl yonu y…õf…õt k…Ē y…Ēp…ĒŇč taŇč n…ôndesak yi nn…Ē, awut anu af…õt af…õt k…Ē aran anu, n…ôntam k…ôkek…ôr…õ Ňča.¬Ľ
\v 25 Mba k…Ē Musa oluks…õ k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôna yati, m…õn…õ m…ôdes…ĒŇč su y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēl…Ēma ny…õ s…ôndek…ĒloŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē y…Ēk…Ē s…ôndek…Ēc…Ēf…õ MARIKI Kanu kosu m…Ē.
\v 26 Nt…õ tendeŇč…ôrn…õ ti m…Ē, s…ôndeken…õn…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yosu ali k…ôgboro kin s…ôf…Ēdesak, bawo yi y…Ē s…ôndek…Ēwur…õ dac…Ē ny…õ s…ôndek…ĒloŇčn…õn…õ MARIKI Kanu kosu. S…ôntac…ôr…õ f…õ k…ôr…õsna mp…õ s…ôŇčk…ĒloŇčn…õn…õ MARIKI m…Ē, m…õn…õ s…ôcb…õr…õ d…ôndo.¬Ľ
\v 27 K…Ē MARIKI eyeŇčk…ôs s…Ē firawona domp, firawona …õnafaŇč f…õ s…Ē k…ôsak aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ē.
\p 
\v 28 K…Ē firawona oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôwur nn…Ē nderem! M…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ ta in…ôŇčk …ôm s…Ē f…Ēr yem kiriŇč, d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ o nd…õ m…ônder s…Ē nn…Ē m…Ē, m…ôŇčfi d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 29 K…Ē Musa oloku firawona: ¬ęNt…õ m…ôloku ti tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, awa! If…Ēs…Ēgb…Ēk…ôr…õ k…ôder nn…Ē f…Ēr yam kiriŇč.¬Ľ
\c 11
\s1 K…ôd…ôŇčk ka pucuy p…õlp…ôs
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęP…ôcuy pin gboŇč p'indes…ĒdeŇč…ôr firawona, k…Ē Misira. K…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, endesak nu n…ôwur d…õ. K'endelip k…ôsak nu a n…ôk…Ē-…õ, endek…Ē haŇč p…ôcb…õl…ôs nu d…õ few.
\v 2 M…ôm…õŇčk…ôs afum am, il…õts…õn'am, a w…ôrkun nw…õ o nw…õ k…Ē w…ôran nw…õ o nw…õ Ňčawer and…õ aŇčan ca ca gbeti k…Ē k…õma.¬Ľ
\v 3 K…Ē MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel k…ômar ka k…ôb…Ēt…ôr nde f…Ēr ya aka Misira kiriŇč. Musa s…Ē yati fum …õnayi nw…õ amar…ôs a firawona k…Ē afum Ňčanalel…ôs at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē.
\p 
\v 4 K…Ē Musa oloku: Nt…õ t…Ē MARIKI oloku: ¬ęC…õkc…õkana, indenacep…ôr Misira dac…Ē.
\v 5 Awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē f…ôp Ňčandenafi at…Ēf Ňča Misira, k…ôy…õf…õ coco ca firawona w…ôkak…Ē …õnd…õ d…Ēc…Ēm d…Ēn dab…õ k…ôroŇč m…Ē, haŇč k…ôk…Ēb…ôp coco ca w…ômar…ôs k…Ēn w…ôran w…ôk…Ē …õŇčgb…õnt…õ k…Ē k…ôcom m…Ē, k…ôk…Ē haŇč awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē f…ôp a y…Ēc…Ēl.
\v 6 K…ôbok k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôndeyi Misira, k…ôbok nk…õ k…ôntat…Ēyi Misira, a k…Ē k…ônt…Ēs…Ēyi d…õ m…Ē.
\v 7 Mba ndena aka Yisrayel, ali acen Ňč…Ēf…Ēdekul-kul…ôr di k…ôy…õf…õ fum, haŇč p…Ēc…Ēl, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôc…ôr…õ t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õŇčgb…õy k…ôy…Ē aka Misira nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē.
\v 8 Amar…ôs am f…ôp Ňčandeder Ňčatontn…õn'em Ňčacloku: ‚ÄĻM…ôna k…Ē afum aŇč…õ Ňčanc…ôm'am dar…ôŇč m…Ē f…ôp, n…ôk…Ē!‚Äļ K…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, indewur at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ.¬Ľ K…Ē Musa owur nda firawona, p…ôt…õl…õ k…Ē p…ôp…ĒŇč.
\p 
\v 9 Awa k…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęFirawona …Ēf…Ēk…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl nu, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…õw…õy-w…õy mem m…õla at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 10 Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčay…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…õw…õy-w…õy mm…õ f…ôp f…Ēr ya firawona kiriŇč. K…Ē MARIKI eyeŇčk…ôs domp da firawona tuŇč, …õsak f…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčawur at…Ēf Ňč…Ēn.
\c 12
\s1 K…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Aruna nde at…Ēf Ňča Misira:
\v 2 ¬ęŇäof ŇčaŇč…õ Ňčendey…Ēn…õ nu oŇč Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Ňča yof. Ňäi Ňčendey…Ēn…õ nu Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Ňča teren.
\v 3 N…ôloku ti k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp, n…ôcloku Ňča: Tataka ta w…ôco ta Ňčof ŇčaŇč…õ, w…ôkomb…ôra o w…ôkomb…ôra, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, k…ôl…Ē o k…ôl…Ē Ňčal…õk aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ambiyofo.
\v 4 K…Ē afum a k…ôl…Ē ka w…ôkayi disr…õ Ňčampic…ôr p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē-…õ, w…ôkayi p…ôl…õk…õn…õ and…õ …Ēn ak…Ē Ňčal…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ w…Ēl…Ē m…Ē, w…ôkayi p…ôm…Ēm…ôn d…õlay da afum a k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn. N…ôyer…ôs p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē, nt…õ nw…õ o nw…õ …õntam k…ôs…Ēm m…Ē.
\v 5 P…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…Ēc…Ēl porkun pa teren tin mp…õ p…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp m…Ē. N…ôntam k…ôl…õk aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ambiyofo.
\v 6 N…ôm…õŇčk pi haŇč tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ ta Ňčof ŇčaŇč…õ. Fitiri fa d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē, k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčasur…õn…õ k…ôfay…ôs nw…õ o nw…õ p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēk…Ē …õm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ k…ôdif m…Ē.
\v 7 Pal…õk mecir mam…Ēk…Ē pasop mi c…ôs…ôk k…Ē tak…ôroŇč ta f…ôr…õm fa kusuŇčka ka k…ôl…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē andes…Ēm s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.
\v 8 Pakak…ôl s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē pibi payi, pas…Ēm…õ s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēy…Ē lebin k…Ē b…Ēp…ôr yodok…ôt.
\v 9 Af…Ēs…Ēm s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē yogbulpun, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, pap…õc…õ yi domun de! AŇčkak…ôl yi k…ôkak…ôl d…ôm, k…ôy…õf…õ domp k…ôb…ôp ka c…ôgboro cayi, k…ôk…Ē yedisr…õ ya p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē.
\v 10 Ali t…õs…õm tin ta n…ôsak pa d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk. Mba k…Ē n…ôsak t…õs…õm t…Ēl…Ēma-…õ, d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk n…ôc…Ēf pi.
\v 11 Nt…õ t…Ē p…ômar n…ôlomp…ôsn…õ k…ôs…Ēm s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē: N…ôkotn…õ mabamaba d…ôfi, n…ôb…õrn…õ c…Ēfta, n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr mogbo d…ôwaca. N…ôs…Ēm yi kat…ôna kat…ôna. Ti tendey…Ēn…õ k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka m…õl…õk…õ medif teta k…ôlel…ôs ka MARIKI.
\p 
\v 12 Pibi pamp…õ pender m…Ē, indecep…ôr at…Ēf Ňča Misira disr…õ f…ôp, idif…ôt awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a at…Ēf Ňča Misira, k…ôy…õf…õ ka nn…Ē afum Ňčayi m…Ē haŇč nn…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yeyi m…Ē, k…ôboc…ôr k'inder canu ca Misira kiti k…ôlel. In'…Ēf…Ē MARIKI.
\v 13 Mecir mam…Ēk…Ē mendek…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ta d…ôw…Ēl…Ē nw…õ n…ôndek…Ēyi m…Ē: K'indek…Ē icn…ôŇčk mecir-…õ, indek…Ē iccep…ôr nu ta intor…ôr nu p…ôl…õc mp…õ o mp…õ p…õŇčm…ôl…ôk m…Ē-…õ, mp…õ indek…Ē icsut…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē.
\p 
\v 14 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē dendey…Ēn…õ nu d…Ēs…Ēk d…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ, n…ôdek…Ē n…ôcboc…õ k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē MARIKI. N…ôde n…ôcboc k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē n…ôt…Ēmp…ôrn…õ sariy…õ sas…Ēk…Ē d…õt…õmp donu t…õm o t…õm.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôsata ka k…ôcom k…ôt…Ēy…Ē lebin
\p 
\v 15 ¬ęMata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč disr…õ, n…ônde n…ôcs…Ēm c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēy…Ē lebin. Tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, n…ôwur…õn…õ lebin nde w…Ēl…Ē wonu, bawo nw…õ o nw…õ …ĒŇčs…Ēm k…ôcom k…ôy…Ē lebin m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē haŇč tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ta k…ôsata kaŇčk…õ, aŇčwur…õ w…ôkayi afum aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.
\v 16 Tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…Ē tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč n…ôde n…ôwe k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku teta k…ôlel…ôs ina MARIKI. Ali y…õb…ôc ta fum p…ôsump…ôr d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, m…õn…õ yeri yonu yedi gb…ôc…ôr…ôm y…Ē n…ôŇčlomp…ôs d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē ny…õ nw…õ o nw…õ …õntam k…ôdi m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 17 ¬ęN…ôboc…õ k…ôsata ka C…ôcom c…ôt…Ēy…Ē lebin, bawo d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē yati d'inawur…õn…õ afum anu at…Ēf Ňča Misira d…ôcor d…ôcor. N…ôde n…ôcboc k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē t…õm o t…õm d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp.
\v 18 Ňäof Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ (14) tayi dec d…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy, n…ôs…Ēm c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin haŇč tataka ta w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē tin (21) dec d…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy.
\v 19 Mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč mm…õ disr…õ, p…ômar f…õ pab…ôp lebin nde w…Ēl…Ē wonu disr…õ. Nw…õ o nw…õ …ĒŇčs…Ēm k…ôcom k…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin m…Ē, aŇčwur…õ w…ôkayi k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel dac…Ē, p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôka Yisrayel, p…ôm…Ē w…ôcik…ôra.
\v 20 Ta n…ôs…Ēm mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ēy…Ē lebin m…Ē. C…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin gb…ôc…ôr…ôm c…Ē n…ôntam k…ôs…Ēm, nn…Ē o nn…Ē n…ônd…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē Musa ewe abeki a Yisrayel f…ôp, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē n…ôl…õk Ňčkesiya, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ cir k…ôl…Ē o k…ôl…Ē p…Ēc…Ēl pin teta k…ôcep…ôr ka m…õl…õk…õ medif, n…ôfay…ôs yi. N…ôsu m…Ēb…Ēl mecir mam…Ēk…Ē m…õb…õr…õ mi.
\v 22 N…ôl…õk s…Ē l…õ ya his…Ēp n…ôcgb…ôt yi d…ômecir ma poloŇčn…õ m…Ēk…Ē meyi d…ôt…Ēb…Ēl m…Ē, n…ôcsop…ôt mi d…ôf…ôr…õm fa cumba ca cusuŇčka c…ôs…ôk k…Ē tak…ôroŇč ta w…Ēl…Ē wonu. K…Ē n…ôna dac…Ē ali fum ta p…ôwur nde k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn haŇč dec d…Ēs…Ēk.
\v 23 Nt…õ MARIKI endenan…ĒŇčk…ôr Misira k…ôcsut…õ Ňča p…ôl…õc m…Ē, k'…õn…ôŇčk mecir mam…Ēk…Ē nde f…ôr…õm fa cusuŇčka ca w…Ēl…Ē wonu-…õ, MARIKI encep…ôr k…ôcep…ôr d…ôm w…Ēl…Ē wonu k…ôroŇč, …Ēf…Ēsak w…ôm…ôl…ôk k…Ē p…ôl…õc p…Ēn k…ôb…õr…õ w…Ēl…Ē wonu.
\v 24 N…ôde n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ ti, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ oŇč sariy…õ sa m…ôna k…Ē yuruya yam doru o doru.
\v 25 K…Ē n…ôndek…Ē nde at…Ēf nŇč…õ MARIKI endek…Ēs…ĒŇč nu m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē oloku ti m…Ē-…õ, n…ôdek…Ē n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ tokor-koru tant…õ.
\v 26 K…Ē awut anu Ňčandek…Ēyif nu: ‚ÄĻC…ôke c…Ē t…Ēy…Ē tokur tant…õ toloku-…õ?‚Äļ
\v 27 N…ôloku Ňča: ‚ÄĻK…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs nt…õ MARIKI …õnacep…ôr w…Ēl…Ē wa aka Yisrayel d…ôndo Misira nt…õ oncsut…õ Misira p…ôl…õc, p…ôcyay w…Ēl…Ē wosu m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ K'aka Yisrayel Ňčantontn…õn…õ MARIKI, k…Ē Ňčanc…ôp…õ k…Ē suwu.
\p 
\v 28 Nt…õ tat…Ēk…Ē tencep…ôr m…Ē, k'aka Yisrayel Ňčasump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē. K…Ē Ňčay…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa k…Ē Aruna m…Ē.
\s1 P…ôcuy p…õlp…ôs: Defi da awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a Misira
\p 
\v 29 C…õkc…õk c…ôndeb…ôp, k…Ē MARIKI endif…ôt awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē f…ôp nde at…Ēf Ňča Misira, k…ôy…õf…õ ka wan ka firawona w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē nw…õ …õnand…õ d…Ēc…Ēm d…Ēn dab…õ m…Ē, haŇč wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôka fum nw…õ osump…ôr k'…õmb…õr d…ôbili m…Ē, k…ôb…ôp ka awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a y…Ēc…Ēl f…ôp.
\v 30 K…Ē firawona …õy…õf…õ pibi, nk…Ēn k…Ē amar…ôs …Ēn, k…ôb…ôp ka aka Misira f…ôp, bawo k…ôl…Ē k…ônayi f…õ nk…õ k…ônat…Ēy…Ē w…ôfi m…Ē.
\p 
\v 31 Pibi disr…õ k…Ē firawona ewe Musa k…Ē Aruna, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôy…õf…õ n…ôwur afum em dac…Ē, n…ôna k'aka Yisrayel f…ôp! N…ôk…Ē n…ôsal…õn…õ MARIKI p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē n…ôloku ti m…Ē.
\v 32 N…ôken…õn…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yonu p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē n…ôloku ti m…Ē. N…ôk…Ē! N…ôtolan'em s…Ē!¬Ľ
\v 33 Aka Misira Ňčancb…õlk…ôr aka Yisrayel k…ôwur ka d…Ēt…Ēf bawo Ňčancloku: ¬ęK…ôfi k…Ē s…ônder f…ôp!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 34 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčal…õk…õn…õ c…ôcom c…ôŇčan ta lebin d…õntak…ôf…ôs ci-…õ. K…Ē ŇčaŇčgbaŇč…ôsn…õ y…Ēn…Ēkt…õ yaŇčan c…ôcom paf…Ēkt…ôr yi d…ôyamos yaŇčan.
\v 35 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnaloku Ňča m…Ē: K…Ē Ňčantola aka Misira ca ca gbeti, ya k…õma, k…Ē yamos.
\v 36 K…Ē MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel k…ômar ka k…ôb…Ēt…ôr nde f…Ēr ya aka Misira, k…Ē akak…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel ca c…ôk…Ē ŇčanafaŇč…ôr Ňča m…Ē. Ti disr…õ k…Ē ŇčafoŇč…ôt aka Misira.
\p 
\v 37 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčay…õf…õ Rams…õs k…ôk…Ē ka Suk…Ēt, k…ônay k'as…Ēdar k…ônatam k…ôyi arkun wul masar cam…ôt-tin (600.000) ta al…Ēm awut k'aran aŇčan-…õ.
\v 38 Acik…ôra al…Ēma Ňčanan…ĒŇčk…ôl…õn…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôk…Ē. Ňäasol…õn…õ y…Ēc…Ēl y…õf…õt k…Ē y…Ēp…ĒŇč yaŇčan y…õlar…ôm.
\v 39 K…Ē Ňčalomps…õ biskit b…Ēt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin ambefe Ňč…Ēk…Ē Ňčanay…õf…õn…õ Misira m…Ē. K…ômbefe kaŇčk…Ē k…ônap…õ f…õ bawo anan…ĒŇčk…ôl f…õ ki lebin. Nt…õ anab…õl…ôs Ňča Misira m…Ē, Ňčanatam f…õ k…ôkar k…ôlomp…ôsn…õ Ňčad…õmn…õ yeri ya d…Ēp…Ē.
\p 
\v 40 K…ônd…õ ka aka Yisrayel Misira k…ônawon meren masar maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē w…ôco maas (430).
\v 41 D…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ meren mm…õ masar maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē w…ôco maas (430) melip m…Ē, d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē yati d…Ē afum a MARIKI f…ôp Ňčawur Misira d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\p 
\v 42 Pibi pap…Ēk…Ē camcam MARIKI …õnacep…ôr…õn…õ pi k…ôwur…õn…õ aka Yisrayel at…Ēf Ňča Misira, p…ômar pibi pap…Ēk…Ē p…Ēy…Ēn…õ aka Yisrayel p…õm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp k…ôt…Ēdir…õn…õ teta MARIKI, tendey…Ēn…õ Ňča oŇč t…Ēy…Ē taŇčan tokur ta doru o doru.
\s1 Sariy…õ s…ôboc…õ k…ôsata ka Pak
\p 
\v 43 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Aruna: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē sariy…õ sa k…ôsata ka k…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs ka K…ôcep…ôr ka m…õl…õk…õ medif s…ôloku: Ali w…ôcik…ôra ta p…ôde p…ôcdi yeri yay…Ēk…Ē.
\v 44 W…ôcar nw…õ away…õ p…ôsam m…Ē, …õntam k…ôdi yeri yonu, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a aŇčk…ônc k…Ē-…õ.
\v 45 Am…Ēn…õ w…ôcik…ôra w…ôcep…ôr k…Ē w…ôb…ôc nw…õ aŇčs…ĒŇč k…ôway m…Ē k…ôdi yi.
\v 46 S…õm yay…Ēk…Ē d…õk…õr aŇčs…Ēm yi, af…Ēkek…ôr…õ yi k…ôfo k…ôcuru, ali k…ôb…õnt kin ta papor-poru.
\v 47 K…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčamboc k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē.
\v 48 M…ôna w…ôcik…ôra nw…õ m…ôfaŇč k…ôboc…õ MARIKI k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē m…Ē, m…õn…õ arkun a k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ f…ôp, pak…ônc Ňča. W…ôkayi …õntam k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…ôsata, p…ôyi k…Ē p…ôm…Ē w…ôka Yisrayel. Mba w…ôt…Ēk…ônc nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēf…Ēs…Ēm s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē.
\v 49 T…õt…ôks…õ tin tat…Ēk…Ē t'ambonc…ôr w…ôYisrayel yati k…Ē w…ôcik…ôra nw…õ eyi nu dac…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 50 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčasur…õn…õ k…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa k…Ē Aruna m…Ē.
\v 51 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ē MARIKI …õnawur…õn…õ aka Yisrayel at…Ēf Ňča Misira, p…ôc…õk Ňča c…ôgba c…ôŇčan d…ôcor d…ôcor.
\c 13
\s1 M…õt…ôk…ôs m…Ēl…Ēma ma Pak
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęN…ôpus'em awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, p…ôy…Ēn…õ aka afum, p…ôy…Ēn…õ aka y…Ēc…Ēl, nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ wan ka k…õr…õ w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel dac…Ē, w…ôkemi …Ēf…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 3 K…Ē Musa oloku afum: ¬ęN…ôde n…ôcc…õm-c…õmn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ n…ôwur at…Ēf Ňča Misira, nde n…ônay…Ēn…õ acar m…Ē, bawo s…Ēk…ôt sa k…ôca ka nk…Ēn MARIKI s…ônawur…õn…õ nu di. Ti disr…õ ta pas…Ēm paka o paka p…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin.
\v 4 N…ôŇčwur m…Ēk…Ē Ňčof Ňča Abib\f + \fr 13:4 \fq Ňäof Ňča Abib\ft = ¬ęT…õm ta L…õŇčk¬Ľ\f*.
\v 5 T…õm nt…õ MARIKI endek…Ēb…õrs'am at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč, nda aHit, nda Am…Ēr, nda aHiwy, nda aYebus, at…Ēf nŇč…õ ŇčomboŇč dal…õ k‚Äôawop m…Ē, nŇč…õ MARIKI …õnad…õrm…õ atem anu k…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm m…Ē, m…ôdek…Ē m…ôcboc…õ MARIKI k…ôsata kaŇčk…õ Ňčof ŇčaŇč…õ.
\v 6 Mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…ôcs…Ēm k…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin. Tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…ôboc…õ MARIKI k…ôsata.
\v 7 C…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin c'andek…Ē pacs…Ēm mata mam…Ēk…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. P…ômar f…õ padek…Ē pacn…ôŇčk nda nw…õ o nw…õ daka o daka d…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin, p…ômar f…õ yati padek…Ē s…Ē pacn…ôŇčk ndaram lebin, at…Ēf Ňčam disr…õ f…ôp.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 8 ¬ęD…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē m…ôde m…ôloku wan kam nt…õ: ‚ÄĻTeta t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnay…Ēn'em nt…õ incwur Misira m…Ē.‚Äļ
\v 9 Tendey…Ēn…õ nu t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ k…ôca kam k…ôroŇč k…Ē t…õc…õmc…õm…ôs ta f…Ēr yam, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ m…õt…ôks…õ ma MARIKI mey'…ôm d…ôkusu, bawo k…ôca ka s…Ēk…ôt k…Ē MARIKI …õnawur…õn'am Misira.
\v 10 Tataka tant…õ ombonc m…Ē t…Ē m…ônde m…ôcboc oŇč k…ôsata k…Ēn, k…ôren o k…ôren.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 11 ¬ęK…Ē MARIKI endek…Ēb…õrs'am KanaŇč, p…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm di, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnd…õrm'am ti k…Ē atem am m…Ē,
\v 12 m…ôde m…ôcs…ĒŇč nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ wan w…ôrkun w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôka w…ôran, k…Ē awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a y…Ēc…Ēl yam. Arkun ak…Ē, MARIKI …Ēy…Ē Ňča.
\v 13 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôka s…Ēfale …Ēf…Ē-…õ, m…ôwurus…õ si aŇčkesiya, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ambiyofo. K…Ē m…ônt…Ēwurus si-…õ, m…ôtepi s…Ēfale sas…Ēk…Ē kilim. M…ôwurus s…Ē awut arkun ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a afum.
\v 14 Alna k…Ē wan kam endeyif …ôm: ‚ÄĻC…ôke c…Ē tant…õ toloku-…õ?‚Äļ, m…ôloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻS…Ēk…ôt sa k…ôca s…Ē MARIKI …õnawur…õn…õ su Misira, nde at…Ēf nŇč…õ s…ônay…Ēn…õ acar m…Ē.
\v 15 Nt…õ firawona …õncfati k…ôsak su s…ôk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē MARIKI endif…ôt awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē f…ôp at…Ēf Ňča Misira, k…ôy…õf…õ ka awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a afum haŇč awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a y…Ēc…Ēl. Ti t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ iŇčloŇčn…õn…õ MARIKI p…Ēc…Ēl porkun mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē pa k…õr…õ ka pi m…Ē, icwurus awut em arkun ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē.‚Äļ
\v 16 Tendey…Ēn'am t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ k…ôca kam k…ôroŇč k…Ē taf…ôc mp…õ aŇčkot …ôm d…ôtobu f…Ēr yam dac…Ē m…Ē, bawo s…Ēk…ôt sa k…ôca s…Ē MARIKI …õnawur…õn…õ su Misira.¬Ľ
\s1 Kanu k…ôsol…õ afum …Ēn k…ôk…Ē
\p 
\v 17 Nt…õ firawona …õsak aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ē m…Ē, Kanu k…ôsoln…õn…õ f…õ Ňča d…Ēp…Ē da at…Ēf Ňča aFilisti, ali nt…õ p…ônay…Ēn…õ a d…Ēp…Ē dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ m…Ē. Bawo Kanu k…ônalokun…õ: ¬ęK'aka Yisrayel Ňčan…ôŇčk k…ôwan-…õ, ŇčaŇčaŇčn…õ t…õl…ôr k…ôwur k…ôŇčan Misira, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča s…Ē k…ôluks…ôrn…õ di.¬Ľ
\v 18 K…Ē Kanu k…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr…õn…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôca ka d…Ēp…Ē da d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, ntende k…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma. Aka Yisrayel Ňčanawur at…Ēf Ňča Misira Ňčalomp…ôsn…õ c…ôk…ôwan.
\p 
\v 19 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk…õn…õ b…õnt ya Isifu, bawo Isifu …õnas…ĒŇč…õ awut a Yisrayel k…ôd…õr…ôm, p…ôcloku: ¬ęK…Ē Kanu k…ôndemar nu-…õ, n…ônde n…ômit…õn…õ b…õnt yem, n…ôkek…ôr…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 20 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčay…õf…õ Suk…Ēt, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčac…ômb…ôr saŇčka s…ôŇčan Etam, ntende t…õgb…ôr…õ d…ôkusu.
\v 21 MARIKI …Ēnck…Ēt k…Ē Ňča, daŇč p…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ Ňča k…Ē acul Ňča k…ôp nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôsoln…õ d…Ēp…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē pibi p…ômot pa acul Ňča n…õnc p…Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča p…ôwaŇčk…ôra, t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôtam k…ôk…Ēt daŇč k…Ē pibi.
\v 22 Acul Ňča k…ôp ŇčencliŇčn…õ f…õ aka Yisrayel f…Ēr kiriŇč daŇč, acul Ňča p…ômot pa n…õnc ŇčencliŇčn…õ f…õ Ňča s…Ē f…Ēr kiriŇč pibi.
\c 14
\s1 Firawona …õy…õf…õ k…ôb…õl…ôs aka Yisrayel
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel a Ňčaluks…ôrn…õ Ňčader Ňčac…ômb…ôr saŇčka s…ôŇčan nde Pi Hir…Ēt tekiriŇč, Mik…ôd…Ēl k…Ē k…ôba dac…Ē, Ňčat…õf…ôrn…õ Bal Cef…ĒŇč. K…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē tekiriŇč k…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēc…ômb…ôr saŇčka k…ôba k…ôs…ôk.
\v 3 Firawona …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôclok…õ aYisrayel: ‚ÄĻK…ôyara-yara k…Ē Ňčand…õ d…Ēt…Ēf, p…ônciyan…õ Ňča, t…õgb…ôr…õ tendi Ňča!‚Äļ
\v 4 IndeyeŇčk…ôs firawona domp, endec…ôm…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč k…ôb…õl…ôs. Ti disr…õ, indes…Ēt…Ē k…ôyek-yek…ôs d…ôm…Ēy…Ē mm…õ indey…Ē firawona k…Ē as…Ēdar …Ēn f…ôp m…Ē, aka Misira Ňčandec…ôr…õ a in'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI.¬Ľ K'aka Yisrayel Ňčay…Ē ti.
\p 
\v 5 K'aŇčk…Ē paloku w…ôb…õ w…ôMisira a aka Yisrayel Ňčay…õks…õ. K'ab…ôk…ôc Ňča firawona k…Ē amar…ôs …Ēn y…õŇčkaf…ôl…õ s…Ē teta aka Yisrayel. K…Ē Ňčayifn…õ: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē s…ônay…Ē tant…õ k…ôsak aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ē-…õ? S…ôŇčgbal ab…ôc…õ asu!¬Ľ
\v 6 K…Ē firawona osom a pasekt…ôr abil Ňč…Ēn Ňča d…ôk…ôwan, k'osol…õ as…Ēdar …Ēn k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē.
\v 7 K…Ē firawona …õl…õk cibil ca d…ôk…ôwan c…ôt…Ēt masar cam…ôt-tin (600), k…Ē cibil ca d…ôk…ôwan ca Misira c…ôlp…ôs, ab…õ as…Ēdar Ňčanayi ci k…ôroŇč.
\v 8 K…Ē MARIKI eyeŇčk…ôs domp da firawona w…ôb…õ ka Misira: k'…õnc…ôm…õ aka Yisrayel dar…ôŇč k…ôb…õl…ôs, mba aka Yisrayel ŇčanaŇč…õc s…ôbomp k…ôwur at…Ēf Ňča Misira.
\v 9 K'aka Misira Ňčanc…ôm…õ aka Yisrayel dar…ôŇč k…ôb…õl…ôs: F…ôl…õs ya firawona f…ôp k…Ē cibil c…Ēn ca d…ôk…ôwan, k…ôb…ôp ka ay…õks…õn…õ …Ēn f…ôl…õs, k…ôk…Ē ka as…Ēdar …Ēn, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp aka Yisrayel nde Pi Hir…Ēt ntende k…ôba k…ôs…ôk nde Ňčanac…ômb…ôr saŇčka Ňčat…õf…ôr…õn…õ Bal Cef…ĒŇč m…Ē.
\p 
\v 10 Nt…õ firawona …Ēncl…Ēt…ôrn…õ m…Ē, aka Yisrayel Ňčandeyekti f…Ēr, apayo! k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk aka Misira Ňčanc…ôm…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč k…ôb…õl…ôs. K'aka Yisrayel Ňčanes…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkul…õ-kul…õ MARIKI.
\v 11 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčaloku Musa: ¬ęCufu c…ôla f…õ Misira nt…õ m…ôŇčk…õr…õ su k…ôdedif nn…Ē d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē ba? C…ôke c…Ē m…ôŇčy…Ē su tant…õ-…õ, m…ôwur…õn…õ su Misira m…Ē?¬Ľ
\v 12 Baf…Ē s…ônalok'…ôm Misira: ¬ęM…ôce su s…ôb…ôc…õ aka Misira, bawo k…ôb…ôc…õ ka aMisira k…ôncep…ôr su k…ôfi nn…Ē d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ!¬Ľ
\v 13 K…Ē Musa oloku aka Yisrayel: ¬ęTa n…ônes…õ, n…ôc…ôm…õ gbiŇč, n…ôgb…ôtn…õ nt…õ MARIKI endeyac nu m…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, bawo aka Misira akaŇč…õ n…ôŇčgb…ôtn…õ m…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, n…ôf…Ēs…Ēn…ôŇčk Ňča few.
\v 14 MARIKI endesutn…õn…õ nu, k…Ē n…ôna, n…ônd…õ n…ôcaŇčk.¬Ľ
\s1 Kanu k…ôwur…õn…õ k…Ēn d…Ēp…Ē k…ôba disr…õ
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē m…ôŇčkul-kul…õn'em-…õ? M…ôloku aka Yisrayel Ňčasoln…õ d…Ēp…Ē daŇčan dar…ôŇč tuŇč k…ôk…Ē.
\v 16 K…Ē m…ôna Musa m…ôyekti k…ôgbo kam, m…ôcenc ki d…ôk…ôba, m…ôgberi ki. Aka Yisrayel Ňčak…Ēt k…ôba disr…õ ant…Ēf Ňčowosu k…ôroŇč.
\v 17 K…Ē ina MARIKI, k…ôyeŇčk…ôs k'inder s…ôbomp s'aka Misira, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčac…ôm…õ nu dar…ôŇč k…ôb…õl…ôs m…Ē. Dif…Ē indeyek-yek…ôsn…õn…õ k…ôl…ôs…ôr firawona, as…Ēdar …Ēn f…ôp, cibil c…Ēn ca d…ôk…ôwan, k'ay…õks…õn…õ a ci.
\v 18 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, aka Misira Ňčandec…ôr…õ a in'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI, k'indeyek-yek…ôsn…õn…õ firawona, k…Ē cibil c…Ēn ca d…ôk…ôwan k'ay…õks…õn…õ …Ēn f…ôl…õs.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 19 M…õl…õk…õ ma Kanu mm…õ mencyi as…Ēdar aka Yisrayel tekiriŇč m…Ē, m…ĒŇčk…Ē m…õc…ôm…õ as…Ēdar aka Yisrayel tadar…ôŇč, acul Ňča k…ôp nŇč…õ Ňčencyi Ňča tekiriŇč m…Ē, Ňči s…Ē k…Ē Ňč…ĒŇčk…Ē Ňča tadar…ôŇč.
\v 20 K'acul Ňča k…ôp Ňč…ĒŇčk…Ē Ňčeyi as…Ēdar aka Yisrayel k'as…Ēdar aka Misira dac…Ē. Acul Ňča k…ôp nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēncs…ĒŇč pibi k…ôs…ôk k'aka Misira, k…ôs…ôk ka m…õr…ôŇč Ňč…Ēcs…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel p…ôwaŇčk…ôra pibi disr…õ. Pibi pap…Ēk…Ē disr…õ f…ôp, aka Yisrayel k…Ē aka Misira Ňčanal…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ f…õ.
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē Musa entenci k…ôca k…Ēn d…ôk…ôba, k…Ē MARIKI owur…õ afef Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč nŇč…õ Ňč…õncy…õf…õ k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē. K…Ē Ňč…õw…õn pibi pap…Ēk…Ē f…ôp domun da d…ôk…ôba k…Ē Ňčowos…ôs k…ôba, k…Ē domun d…õgb…õy…õn…õ.
\v 22 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčantor d…ôk…ôba ant…Ēf Ňčowosu, k…Ē domun deyi k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…Ē k…ômeriya p…ôm…Ē biŇčk…ôli.
\v 23 K'aka Misira Ňčanc…ôm…õ aka Yisrayel dar…ôŇč k…ôb…õl…ôs k…ôy…õf…õ f…ôl…õs ya firawona k…ôb…ôp cibil c…Ēn ca d…ôk…ôwan, k…ôk…Ē ka ay…õks…õn…õ …Ēn f…ôl…õs, f…ôp faŇčan k…Ē Ňčantor d…ôk…ôba.
\v 24 D…Ēs…Ēka d…õl…ôp…ôs k…Ē MARIKI ontor…õ f…Ēr, k'…Ēm…Ēm…ôn as…Ēdar aka Misira p…ôyi acul Ňča n…õnc k…Ē Ňča k…ôp disr…õ, k'osut…õ as…Ēdar aka Misira p…ôyamayama.
\v 25 K…Ē MARIKI …õyams…ôr s…ôntef sa cibil ca d…ôk…ôwan ca aka Misira k…ôkaf…ôl…õ belbel, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ ci k…ôy…õln…õ k…ôk…Ēt. K'aka Misira Ňčaloku: ¬ęPay…õks…õ pamulp…ôr aka Yisrayel, bawo MARIKI eyi k…ôsutn…õn…õ Ňča nn…Ē aka Misira Ňčayi m…Ē!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 26 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôcenc k…ôca kam d…ôk…ôba, domun d…õgb…ôp…ôrn…õ aka Misira, k…ôy…õf…õ ka cibil c…ôŇčan ca d…ôk…ôwan k…ôb…ôp ka ay…õks…õn…õ f…ôl…õs aŇčan.¬Ľ
\v 27 K…Ē Musa encenc k…ôca k…Ēn d…ôk…ôba, d…Ēs…Ēka d…õl…ôp…ôs k…Ē k…ôba k…ôluks…ôrn…õ t…Ēk…Ē k…ônayi m…Ē. Aka Misira Ňčanayi k…ôy…õks…ôr k…ôba, mba k…Ē MARIKI …õŇčgb…ôp…ôr Ňča domun.
\v 28 K…Ē domun dender k…Ē d…õŇčgb…ôp…ôrn…õ cibil c…ôŇčan ca d…ôk…ôwan, k…Ē ay…õks…õn…õ f…ôl…õs k…Ē as…Ēdar a firawona f…ôp, aŇč…õ Ňčanator d…ôk…ôba k…ôc…õps…õ ka aka Yisrayel m…Ē. Ali w…ôkin …õnamulp…õ f…õ.
\v 29 Mba aka Yisrayel Ňča Ňčack…Ēt k…ôba disr…õ ant…Ēf Ňčowos f…ôr. Domun deyi Ňča k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…Ē k…ômeriya p…ôm…Ē biŇčk…ôli.
\v 30 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ē MARIKI …õnabaŇč aka Yisrayel aMisira d…ôwaca. K'aka Yisrayel Ňčan…ôŇčk aka Misira Ňčafis-fis daparpara.
\v 31 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčan…ôŇčk f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr nf…õ MARIKI …õnasut…õ aka Misira m…Ē. K'aka Yisrayel Ňčanes…õ MARIKI, k…Ē ŇčalaŇč MARIKI k…Ē Musa w…ômar…ôs k…Ēn.
\c 15
\s1 TeleŇč ta Musa k…Ē aka Yisrayel
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ tencep…ôr m…Ē, Musa k'aka Yisrayel ŇčaleŇčs…õ MARIKI teleŇč nt…õ:
\q1 ¬ęIndeleŇčs…õ MARIKI
\q1 bawo …õnament…ôr debeki da k…ôtam k…Ēn:
\q1 ∆źŇčgbal af…ôl…õs k…Ē w…ôy…õks…õn…õ ka Ňči d…ôk…ôba.
\q1 
\v 2 MARIKI …Ēy…Ēn…õ s…Ēk…ôt sem k…Ē teleŇč tem,
\q1 Nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôyac kem.
\q1 Kanu kem k…Ē, indeyek-yek…ôs k…Ē.
\q1 Kanu ka papa kem k…Ē,
\q1 indekor-koru debeki d…Ēn.
\q1 
\v 3 MARIKI korgba k…Ē! Tewe t…Ēn t…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI.
\q1 
\v 4 ∆źl…ôm d…ôk…ôba cibil ca d…ôk…ôwan ca firawona k…Ē k…ônay k…Ēn k'as…Ēdar.
\q1 As…Ēdar abaŇčs…õ aMisira,
\q1 anakal Ňča nde k…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma.
\q1 
\v 5 K…Ē putukum pa k…ôba p…õŇčgb…ôp…ôrn…õ Ňča, k…Ē Ňčantor k…ôba d…ônt…Ēf p…ôm…Ē masar.
\q1 
\v 6 K…ôca kam k…ôt…Ēt, MARIKI, k…ôy…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…ôw…õy-w…õy! K…ôca kam k…ôt…Ēt, MARIKI, k…ômputuk w…ôter…õn…õ kam.
\q1 
\v 7 Debeki da d…õb…õ dam d…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôy…õt aŇč…õ Ňčanc…ôm'am d…õb…ôk…ôc m…Ē.
\q1 K…Ē m…ôwur…õ m…õt…õl…õ mam-…õ:
\q1 Mendi Ňča p…ôm…Ē nt…õ n…õnc dendi tuktukur ya m…õmp…ôl…õ m…Ē.
\q1 
\v 8 Kifir k'alol…ôm Ňčam gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ domun da d…ôk…ôba k…ôgb…õy…õn…õ,
\q1 k…Ē yam y…õnc…ôm…õ p…ôm…Ē biŇčk…ôli,
\q1 k…Ē domun da k…ôba d…ônt…Ēf d…õnc…ôp.
\q1 
\v 9 W…ôter…õn…õ kosu oncloku: ‚ÄĻK…ôb…õl…ôs Ňča k'inder, isump…ôr Ňča!
\q1 IbaŇč…ôr Ňča ca c…ôŇčan p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē p…ôncep…ôr…ôr k…ôb…Ēt im m…Ē.
\q1 K…ôwur…õ k'inder dakma, im…ôlk…õ Ňča k…ôca kem!‚Äļ
\q1 
\v 10 K…Ē m…ôfurup,
\q1 k…Ē k…ôba k…ôŇčkal Ňča,
\q1 k…Ē ŇčaŇčkal…õ p…ôm…Ē nt…õ tomunt pegb…ôleŇč pontor domun da d…ôk…ôba d…õw…õy-w…õy disr…õ m…Ē.
\q1 
\v 11 Canu c…ôyi f…õ nc…õ c…ônt…ôŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē m…ôna MARIKI m…Ē!
\q1 An'eyi p…ôm…Ē m…ôna, dosoku dam d…õmb…õk, d…Ēy…Ē w…õyw…õy,
\q1 nw…õ p…ômar a pakor-koru m…Ē,
\q1 m…ôna nw…õ m…ôŇčy…Ē mes mm…õ moŇčwos…ôs kusu m…Ē?
\q1 
\v 12 M…ôntenci k…ôca kam k…ôt…Ēt gb…ôc…ôr…ôm,
\q1 k…Ē ant…Ēf Ňčendi Ňča.
\q1 
\v 13 K…ôsekt…ôrn…õ kam danapa k…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēt…õn…õ afum am akaŇč…õ m…ônawurus m…Ē,
\q1 f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fam f…Ē m…ôndesol…õ Ňča,
\q1 m…ôliŇč…ôrn…õ Ňča nde d…ôkiyi dam dosoku.
\q1 
\v 14 Nt…õ and…õ asu Ňčane ti m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčayikc…õ.
\q1 K…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôsump…ôr afum aka Filisti.
\q1 
\v 15 Ayekyek Ňčosump…ôr ab…õ a at…Ēf Ňča Ed…Ēm,
\q1 k…Ē k…ôyikc…õ k…ôsump…ôr afum akiriŇč a Mohab,
\q1 k…Ē b…ôk…ôc y…õl…õc…õ-l…õc…õ aka KanaŇč f…ôp.
\q1 
\v 16 K…ônes…õ k…Ē ayekyek Ňčontor…ôr Ňča.
\q1 Debeki da k…ôca kam, d…õnas…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôcaŇčk p…ôm…Ē tasar
\q1 haŇč afum am Ňčaclip k…ôcep…ôr, MARIKI, haŇč afum aŇč…õ m…ônaway m…Ē Ňčaclip k…ôcep…ôr.
\q1 
\v 17 M…ôde m…ôkek…ôr…õ Ňča m…ôk…Ē m…ôd…ôs
\q1 nde t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč mp…õ m…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča k…õ m…Ē,
\q1 k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē m…ônalomp…ôs d…ôkiyi dam m…Ē, MARIKI,
\q1 d…ôndo k…ôfo k…ôsoku kaŇčk…Ē m…ônac…ômb…ôr…õ, Mariki, waca wam m…Ē.
\q1 
\v 18 MARIKI …Ēnt…Ēmp…ôr d…õb…õ doru o doru.
\q1 
\v 19 Bawo f…ôl…õs ya firawona k…Ē cibil c…Ēn ca d…ôk…ôwan k…Ē ay…õks…õn…õ f…ôl…õs …Ēn Ňčant…õmp…õn…õ d…ôk…ôba.
\q1 K…Ē MARIKI …õŇčgb…ôp…ôr Ňča domun da d…ôk…ôba,
\q1 mba aYisrayel ŇčaŇčk…Ēt ant…Ēf Ňčowosu k…ôba dac…Ē, w…õc…ôk waŇčan wowos f…ôr.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 20 K…Ē sayib…õ Miriyam, w…ôkir…õ ka Aruna …õl…õk tamba, k…Ē aran aYisrayel f…ôp Ňčanc…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč, Ňčacpis…õ Ňčacfer mamba.
\v 21 K…Ē Miriyam oluks…õ Ňča:
\q1 ¬ęN…ôleŇčs…õ MARIKI, bawo …õnament…ôr debeki da k…ôtam k…Ēn.
\q1 ∆źl…ôm d…ôk…ôba af…ôl…õs k…Ē w…ôy…õks…õn…õ ka Ňči.¬Ľ
\ms2 Aka Yisrayel k…ôk…Ēt k…ôŇčan d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ
\mr 15-18
\s1 Domun da Mara
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē Musa …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôy…õf…õ k…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma, k'osoln…õn…õ Ňča d…Ēp…Ē da t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sur. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ēt mata maas d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, Ňčas…Ēt…Ē f…õ domun.
\p 
\v 23 K…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ Mara, mba Ňčanatam f…õ k…ômun domun da Mara, bawo d…õnadokt…õ. Ti t…Ē awen…õ di tewe ta Mara ¬ęp…ôdok…ôt¬Ľ.
\v 24 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčancop k…ôc…Ēp…õn…õ-c…Ēp…õn…õ nn…Ē Musa eyi m…Ē, Ňčacloku: ¬ęAke andemun-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 25 K…Ē Musa oŇčkorn…õ MARIKI, k…Ē MARIKI ement…ôr k…Ē k…ôt…Ēk nk…õ …õnal…ôm d…ôromun m…Ē, k…Ē domun dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ēy…Ēn…õ dobotu. Dif…Ē MARIKI …õnas…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel sariy…õ k…Ē t…Ēy…Ē tokur t…Ēk…Ē Ňčande Ňčacy…Ē doru o doru m…Ē. D…ôndo MARIKI …õnawak…ôs k…ôlaŇč k…ôŇčan.
\v 26 K…Ē Musa oloku: ¬ęK…Ē m…ônc…ôŇčk…ôl belbel dim da MARIKI Kanu kam, k…Ē m…ôy…Ē nt…õ tentes…õ MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē, m…ôsu l…ôŇč…ôs m…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl mosom m…Ēn k…Ē m…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ sariy…õ s…Ēn f…ôp-…õ, ali docu din if…Ēs…ĒŇč …ôm nd…õ is…ĒŇč aka Misira m…Ē. In'…Ēf…Ē MARIKI, nw…õ …õntam…ôs …ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 27 K'aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…õr…õ Elim nde c…ôl…ômp w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (12) c…ônayi k…Ē komp w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (70) m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčac…ômb…ôr saŇčka s…ôŇčan d…ôndo domun k…ôs…ôk.
\c 16
\s1 Yeri ya man k…Ē bak…Ērn…õ
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ Elim k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…õr…õ t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sin, mp…õ p…ôyi Elim k…Ē Sinayi dac…Ē m…Ē, tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt ta Ňčof Ňča m…õr…ôŇč nŇč…õ Ňčay…õf…õ Misira m…Ē.
\v 2 Awa k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčancop k…ôc…Ēp…õn…õ-c…Ēp…õn…õ d…ôndo d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ nn…Ē Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčayi m…Ē.
\v 3 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčaloku Ňča: ¬ęAh! Ali MARIKI …õnadift…õ su k…ôca k…Ēn Misira, nt…õ s…ônand…õ car…Ēr…Ē ca s…õm k…ôs…ôk m…Ē, nt…õ s…ôncs…Ēm c…ôcom haŇč s…ôn…õmb…ôr…õ m…Ē! K…ôdift…õ ka k…ôloŇčkan…õ kaŇčk…õ f…ôp dor k…Ē n…ôwur…õn…õ su k…ôdesak t…õgb…ôr…õ tant…õ!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 4 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęK…ôtuf…ôr nu k'inder c…ôcom k…ôy…õf…õ ka darenc. Afum Ňčande Ňčacwur Ňčacw…õt…ôs d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk nc…õ Ňčantam k…ôs…Ēm d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē indewak…ôs Ňča ic…ôr…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ Ňčanc…ôm…õ m…õt…ôks…õ mem dar…ôŇč-…õ.
\v 5 Tataka ta cam…ôt-tin, k…Ē Ňčandelomp…ôs y…Ēk…Ē Ňčaw…õt…ôs m…Ē, n…ôndes…Ēt…Ē k…ôm…õr…ôŇč ka yeri ya d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 6 Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčaloku aka Yisrayel f…ôp: ¬ęD…Ēf…Ēyana, n…ôndenac…ôr…õ a MARIKI …õnawur…õn…õ nu at…Ēf Ňča Misira.
\v 7 B…ôtb…ôtana, n…ôndenan…ôŇčk n…Ēr…Ē da debeki da MARIKI, bawo ene k…ôc…Ēp…õn…õ konu nn…Ē nk…Ēn MARIKI eyi m…Ē. K…Ē s…ôna, ake s…ôy…Ēn…õ nt…õ n…ôndec…Ēp…õn…õ nn…Ē s…ôyi m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 8 K…Ē Musa oloku: ¬ęMARIKI endenas…ĒŇč nu m…Ēk…Ē d…Ēf…Ēy s…õm y…Ēs…Ēm, b…ôtb…ôtana c…ôcom nc…õ n…ôndes…Ēm haŇč n…ôn…õmb…ôr…õ m…Ē. K…Ē MARIKI ene k…ôc…Ēp…õn…õ nk…õ n…ônc…Ēp…õn…õ nn…Ē eyi m…Ē. K…Ē s…ôna ake s…ôy…Ēn…õ-…õ? Baf…Ē nn…Ē s…ôyi m…Ē n…ônc…Ēp…õn…õ, mba nn…Ē MARIKI eyi m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 9 K…Ē Musa oloku Aruna: ¬ęM…ôloku k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel: N…ôder n…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, bawo ene k…ôc…Ēp…õn…õ konu.¬Ľ
\v 10 Aruna eyi k…ôlok-lok…ôr k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp, Ňčandekaf…ôli f…Ēr k…ôca ka ntende d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk n…Ēr…Ē da debeki da MARIKI dowur k…ôp disr…õ.
\p 
\v 11 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 12 ¬ęIne k…ôc…Ēp…õn…õ ka aka Yisrayel. M…ôloku Ňča nt…õ: D…Ēf…Ēyana s…õm y…Ē n…ôndenas…Ēm, b…ôtb…ôtana c…ôcom c…Ē n…ôndenan…õmb…ôr…õ. Ti disr…õ n…ôndec…ôr…õ a in'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI, Kanu konu.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 13 P…ôndeyi d…Ēf…Ēy, k…Ē b…õmp yender y…õf…ônt…ôr…õ yokump saŇčka. Dec dendes…Ēk k…Ē kibi k…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ ant…Ēf mofo f…ôp mm…õ m…õŇčk…õl saŇčka m…Ē.
\v 14 Nt…õ kibi k…ôndeliŇčn…õ d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôyi ant…Ēf Ňča t…õgb…ôr…õ k…ôroŇč p…ôm…Ē ca nc…õ yowur…õ m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ē, ca cac…Ēk…Ē yefer…õ p…ôm…Ē nt…õ anc…õ mal…Ē m…Ēs…Ēk…ôr ant…Ēf k…ôroŇč m…Ē.
\v 15 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčam…Ēm…ôn k…Ē Ňčayif…õn…õ: ¬ęAke d…Ē dand…õ-…õ?¬Ľ bawo Ňčanac…ôr…õ f…õ daka nd…õ d…õnayi m…Ē. K…Ē Musa oloku Ňča: ¬ęYeri y…Ē ny…õ MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč nu m…Ē.
\v 16 Nt…õ t…Ē MARIKI osom: N…ôw…õt…ôs nw…õ o nw…õ, yeri ny…õ y…õntam k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē m…Ē. Nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôw…õt lit…õr m…õr…ôŇč da fum w…ôkin, k…ôl…Ēm ka t…Ēk…Ē n…ôyi d…ôc…ôbal m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 17 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčay…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnaloku Ňča m…Ē, k'al…Ēma Ňčancep…ôr…ôr k…ôl…Ēm, k'al…Ēma Ňčant…Ēb…ôp k…ôl…Ēm.
\v 18 Mba nt…õ anatubuc m…Ē, nw…õ …õnaw…õt p…ôcep…ôr…ôr k…ôl…Ēm m…Ē, ombut t…Ēk…Ē …õnacep…ôr…ôr m…Ē. K…Ē w…ôk…Ē …õnaw…õt p…ôpic m…Ē, …ĒŇčs…Ēt…Ē k…ôl…Ēm k…ôŇčk…Ē p…ônamar m…Ē. K…Ē nw…õ o nw…õ …õw…õt…ôs yeri ny…õ Ňč…õnatam k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ Ňča m…Ē.
\s1 Sariy…õ s…ôl…Ēma ns…õ s…ôŇčkot…ôrn…õ teta man m…Ē
\p 
\v 19 K…Ē Musa oloku Ňča: ¬ęAli fum ta p…ôf…ôn…ôrn…õ yeri ya d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk.¬Ľ
\v 20 Mba Ňčanac…ôŇčk…ôl f…õ Musa, k'afum al…Ēma Ňčaf…ôn…ôrn…õ yeri ya d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk. P…ôndeyi b…ôtb…ôt k…Ē yeri yay…Ēk…Ē y…õmb…õr…õ y…õt, k…Ē y…õs…õn. K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Musa nn…Ē afum akak…Ē Ňčayi m…Ē.
\v 21 B…ôtb…ôt o b…ôtb…ôt, nw…õ o nw…õ …õncw…õt yeri y…Ēk…Ē y…õnct…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē k…ôdi ka d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē nne y…Ēnck…Ēnawon…õ-…õ, y…õs…ôŇčgb…ôr.
\p 
\v 22 Tataka ta cam…ôt-tin, k…Ē nw…õ o nw…õ …õw…õt potubuc pa mata m…õr…ôŇč, lit…õr maŇčk…ôl…õ da fum w…ôkin. K'akiriŇč a k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčaluks…õ ti Musa.
\v 23 K…Ē Musa oloku Ňča: ¬ęTi t…Ē MARIKI oloku. Alna d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm d…Ē, nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē. N…ôp…õc y…Ēk…Ē p…ômar nu k…ôp…õc t…Ēk…Ē n…ôfaŇč m…Ē, yecern…õ y…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ yi haŇč b…ôtb…ôtana.¬Ľ
\v 24 K…Ē Ňčam…õŇčk yeri yay…Ēk…Ē haŇč b…ôtb…ôt p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnasom Ňča ti m…Ē. Yeri yay…Ēk…Ē Ňčanam…õŇčk m…Ē, y…õt y…õnab…õr…õ f…õ yi, y…õnas…õn f…õ s…Ē.
\v 25 K…Ē Musa oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôdi yeri yay…õ m…Ēk…Ē, bawo d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē deyi m…Ēk…Ē, n…ôf…Ēs…Ēt…Ē m…Ēk…Ē yeri y…õw…õt…ôs dal…õ.
\v 26 Mata cam…ôt-tin disr…õ n…ôntam k…ôw…õt…ôs yeri, mba simiti tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč yeri y…õw…õt…ôs y…Ēf…Ēyi.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 27 Tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē afum al…Ēma Ňčawur k…ôk…Ēw…õt…ôs yeri, mba Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē f…õ.
\v 28 K…Ē MARIKI eyif Musa: ¬ęHaŇč t…õm tere t…Ē n…ôndesak k…ôcfati k…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ mosom k…Ē m…õt…ôks…õ mem-…õ?
\v 29 N…ôm…Ēm…ôn! K…Ē MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč nu simiti d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm-…õ, p…ôs…ĒŇč nu s…Ē tataka ta cam…ôt-tin yeri y…Ēk…Ē p…ômar nu k…ôdi mata m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē. Nw…õ o nw…õ p…ômar p…ônd…õ k…ôfo nk…õ eyi m…Ē, ta nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôwur nd…Ēr…Ēn tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 30 Nt…õ t…Ē, k'aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčes…ôm simiti tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.
\p 
\v 31 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčawe yeri yay…Ēk…Ē ¬ęman\f + \fr 16:31 \ft K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčawe yeri yay…Ēk…Ē ¬ęman,¬Ľ ti tat…Ēk…Ē kusu k…ôŇčan ¬ęAke yeri y…Ē yay…õ-…õ?¬Ľ\f*¬Ľ. Yeri yay…Ēk…Ē y…õnawur…õn…õ m…õŇčgb…õn ma yika y…Ēl…Ēma, mefer…õ, meyi d…ôkusu p…ôm…Ē nt…õ k…ôcom k…ôŇčy…Ē m…õs…õ ma c…ôme m…Ē.
\p 
\v 32 K…Ē Musa oloku: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI osom: N…ôlas k…ôfala ka lit…õr m…õr…ôŇč katin yeri ya man, n…ôm…õŇčk…õ yi awut-s…Ē anu, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčade Ňčan…ôŇčk c…ôcom nc…õ iŇčs…ĒŇč nu n…ôcdi nn…Ē d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ nt…õ iwur…õn'on at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 33 K…Ē Musa oloku Aruna: ¬ęM…ôl…õk t…Ēnd…õ m…ôb…õr pi yeri ya man lit…õr m…õr…ôŇč. M…ôk…Ē m…ôc…ômb…ôr pi nde MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pam…õŇčk…õ yi oŇč d…õt…õmp da awut-s…Ē anu m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 34 P…ôm…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē, k…Ē Aruna …õlas t…Ēnd…õ k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôc…ômb…ôr pi kiriŇč nde walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa d…Ēn, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pam…õŇčk yi m…Ē.
\p 
\v 35 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčandi man meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) haŇč t…õm nt…õ Ňčanader at…Ēf nŇč…õ afum Ňčanand…õ m…Ē. Ňäanadi man haŇč k…ôren nk…õ Ňčanader nde k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē.
\v 36 W…ôco wa potubuc…õ pa om…õr\f + \fr 16:36 \ft Potubuc…õ pa man ancwos…õ fum k…ôl…õk d…Ēs…Ēk din m…Ē p…Ēy…Ēn…õ lit…õr m…õr…ôŇč, pi p…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčancwe ¬ęom…õr¬Ľ. Potubuc…õ pamp…õ w…ôco p…Ēncy…Ē ¬ęefah¬Ľ katin.\f* p…Ēncy…Ē potubuc…õ pa efah katin.
\c 17
\s1 Domun da Masa k…Ē Meriba
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sin k…Ē k…ôcep…õ-cep…õ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI oncsom Ňča ti m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčanc…ômb…ôr saŇčka nde Refidim, mba domun domun d…õnayi f…õ nd…õ afum Ňčanctam k…ômun m…Ē.
\v 2 Awa, k'afum Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôt…õns…ôr Musa k…ôc…Ēp. K…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęM…ôs…ĒŇč su domun s…ômun!¬Ľ K…Ē Musa oluks…õ Ňča moloku: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ônt…õns'em k…ôc…Ēp-…õ? Ta ake t…Ē n…ôŇčwaks…õ MARIKI-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 3 Mera y…õnawos aka Yisrayel, afum Ňčacc…Ēp…õn…õ nn…Ē Musa eyi m…Ē. Ňäacloku: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē m…ônas…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôp…õ Misira, m…ôdes…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôfin…õ mera yowosu, s…ôna, awut asu k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yosu-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 4 K…Ē Musa oŇčkul…õ-kul…õ p…ôckorn…õ MARIKI, p…ôcloku: ¬ęC…ôke c'indey…Ēn…õ afum akaŇč…õ-…õ? K…Ē p…ôncep…ôr nd…õk…ôl nn…Ē-…õ, Ňčandeca-cas im.¬Ľ
\v 5 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôcep…ôr aka Yisrayel tekiriŇč, m…ôl…õk…õn…õ abeki aka Yisrayel. M…ôl…õk…õn…õ s…Ē k…ôgbo kam nk…õ m…ônasut…õ k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Nil m…Ē, m…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ kiriŇč.
\v 6 K'ina, inc…ôm…õ nn…Ē tekiriŇč tam, tasar ta t…Ēr…Ē ta Hor…õb k…ôroŇč. M…ôsut…õ tasar k…ôgbo kam, poŇčwur domun nd…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčantam k…ômun m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Musa …Ēy…Ē ti, f…Ēr ya abeki aka Yisrayel kiriŇč.
\v 7 K…Ē Ňčawe k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē Masa ¬ęk…ôd…ôkt…ôr¬Ľ, k…Ē Meriba ¬ęk…ôc…Ēp¬Ľ, bawo aka Yisrayel Ňčanat…õns…ôr di Musa k…ôc…Ēp, k…Ē Ňčawak…ôs di MARIKI, k…ôcyifn…õ: ¬ęMARIKI eyi su dac…Ē ba, ka eyi f…õ su dac…Ē?¬Ľ
\s1 Aka Amal…õk Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ aYisrayel k…ôsut…õn…õ
\p 
\v 8 D…ôndo k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē ancwe Refidim m…Ē, dif…Ē aka Amal…õk Ňčander Ňčayekt…ôr aka Yisrayel k…ôwan.
\v 9 Awa, k…Ē Musa oloku Yosuwe: ¬ęM…ôy…õk-y…õk…õ su dac…Ē arkun, m…ôwur m…ôsut…õn…õ k'aka Amal…õk. Alna inc…ôm…õ nde t…Ēr…Ē d…ôtelempan it…Ēmp…ôr k…ôgbo ka Kanu.¬Ľ
\v 10 K…Ē Yosuwe …Ēy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnaloku k…Ē m…Ē, k…ôk…Ēsut…õn…õ k'aka Amal…õk. Musa, Aruna k…Ē Hur Ňčamp…õ nde t…Ēr…Ē d…ôtelempan.
\v 11 K…Ē Musa …õmp…õn…õ k…ôca darenc-…õ, aka Yisrayel Ňčatas…ôrn…õ aka Amal…õk. Mba k'…Ēnck…Ēnator…õ waca-…õ, aka Amal…õk Ňčatas…ôrn…õ aka Yisrayel.
\v 12 Nt…õ waca wendel…Ēl Musa m…Ē, Aruna k…Ē Hur Ňčal…õk tasar k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčaboc pi Musa d…ônt…Ēf k…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …õnd…õ pi k…ôroŇč. Aruna k…Ē Hur Ňčasoc Musa waca darenc, Aruna k…ôca kin Hur k…ôca ka m…õr…ôŇč haŇč k…Ē dec d…ĒŇčk…Ē d…õkal…õ.
\v 13 K…Ē Yosuwe …õntam Amal…õk k'afum …Ēn, k'endift…õ Ňča dakma.
\p 
\v 14 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôcic…ôs ti nde d…ôbuk, tede t…Ēy…Ēn…õ t…õc…õmc…õmn…õ, m…ôloku Yosuwe belbel, a indenim Amal…õk nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ali fum ta endec…õm-c…õmn…õ Ňča doru dand…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē Musa …õnc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ k'ewe di: ¬ęMARIKI …Ēy…Ēn…õ t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ta k…ôtam kem.¬Ľ
\v 16 K…Ē Musa oloku: ¬ęBawo ayekt…ôr d…õb…õ da MARIKI k…ôca k…ôl…Ēma, MARIKI endesut…õn…õ k…ôsut…õn…õ d…ôm k…Ē d…õt…õmp o d…õt…õmp da aka Amal…õk.¬Ľ
\c 18
\s1 K…ôb…ôp…õn…õ ka Yetero k…Ē Musa
\p 
\v 1 Yetero, w…ôloŇčn…õ ka MadiyaŇč papa ka w…ôran ka Musa, ene mes m…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônay…Ēn…õ Musa k'aka Yisrayel afum …Ēn m…Ē, k'…õnc…ôr…õ t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI owur…õn…õ aka Yisrayel Misira m…Ē.
\v 2 K…Ē Yetero papa ka w…ôran ka Musa, …õl…õk Sefora, w…ôran ka Musa nw…õ …õnalukus nd…Ēr…Ēn k'awut …Ēn m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē,
\v 3 Musa …õnas…ĒŇč tewe ta K…õrs…Ēm coco c…Ēn, bawo …õnaloku: ¬ęW…ôcik…ôra iy…Ēn…õ nn…Ē at…Ēf Ňčocuru ŇčaŇč…õ.¬Ľ
\v 4 K…Ē wan w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč, nk…Ēn …õnawe Eliyeser, bawo Musa …õnaloku: ¬ęKanu ka papa w…ôkem k…ônder k…ôdemar im, k…Ē k…ôyac im dakma da firawona.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 5 W…ôran ka Musa k'awut …Ēn k…Ē kas Yetero Ňčander Ňčab…ôp Musa d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, nde …õnac…ômb…ôr saŇčka t…Ēr…Ē ta Kanu k…ôs…ôk m…Ē.
\v 6 K…Ē Yetero oloku Musa: ¬ęIna papa w…ôka w…ôran kam, Yetero, inder nn…Ē m…ôyi m…Ē k…Ē w…ôran kam k…Ē awut …Ēn m…õr…ôŇč.¬Ľ
\v 7 K…Ē Musa eŇčgbint…ôrn…õ papa ka w…ôran k…Ēn, k'…õnc…ôp…õ k…Ē suwu, k'…õmak…ôrn…õ k…Ē. K…Ē Ňčayif…õn…õ nw…õ o nw…õ nt…õ p…ôyi k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ dabal.
\v 8 K…Ē Musa …Ēl…Ēm…ôr papa ka w…ôran k…Ēn mes m…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnay…Ē firawona k'aka Misira m…Ē f…ôp teta aka Yisrayel, k'…Ēl…Ēm…ôr k…Ē s…Ē p…ôcuca p…Ēk…Ē Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē d…Ēp…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnayac Ňča pi m…Ē.
\v 9 K'amera Ňč…Ēmb…Ēt Yetero teta p…ôt…Ēt p…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnay…Ēn…õ aka Yisrayel m…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnabaŇč aka Yisrayel aka Misira d…ôwaca m…Ē.
\v 10 K…Ē Yetero oloku: ¬ęIŇčkor-koru Kanu nk…õ k…ôbaŇč nu aka Misira k…Ē firawona d…ôwaca m…Ē, MARIKI nw…õ owur…õ nu dacar da aka Misira m…Ē!
\v 11 Inc…ôr…õ oŇč a MARIKI …õmb…õk p…ôtas canu f…ôp, …õnament…ôr ti nt…õ aka Misira Ňčanct…Ēr…ôs aka Yisrayel m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 12 K…Ē Yetero papa ka w…ôran ka Musa …õl…õk p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ …õnadek…Ēc…Ēf…õ Kanu m…Ē, k'oloŇčn…õ s…Ē yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēl…Ēma. Aruna k…Ē abeki aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčander Ňčadi yeri yay…Ēk…Ē k…Ē papa ka w…ôran ka Musa Kanu f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\s1 Musa k…ôd…ôs k…Ēn ab…õ aboc kiti
\p 
\v 13 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk, k…Ē Musa …õnd…õ k…ôboc kiti ka aka Yisrayel, k'aka Yisrayel Ňčac…ôm…õ Musa f…Ēr kiriŇč k…ôy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt haŇč d…Ēf…Ēy nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Musa p…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl moloku maŇčan m…Ē.
\v 14 K…Ē papa ka w…ôran ka Musa …õn…ôŇčk t…Ēk…Ē Musa …Ēncy…Ēn…õ aka Yisrayel m…Ē f…ôp, k'oloku: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē m…ôŇčy…Ēn…õ aka Yisrayel tant…õ f…ôp-…õ? Ta ake t…Ē m…ôn…Ēn…õ nn…Ē sona-…õ, ta ake t…Ē afum Ňčac…ôm…õn'am f…Ēr kiriŇč k…ôy…õf…õ t…õb…ôtb…ôt haŇč d…Ēf…Ēy-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 15 K…Ē Musa oloku papa ka w…ôran k…Ēn: ¬ęD…Ēp…Ē da Kanu d'afum Ňčander k…ôt…õn nn…Ē iyi m…Ē.
\v 16 Afum aŇč…õ k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…ômb…õr…õ dac…Ē m…Ē, Ňčader Ňčan…ôŇčk im. Iboc kiti afum akak…Ē m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē, ics…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôc…ôr…õ sariy…õ sa Kanu k…Ē m…õt…ôks…õ m…Ēn.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 17 K…Ē papa ka w…ôran ka Musa oloku k…Ē: ¬ęTant…õ m…ôŇčy…Ē m…Ē, tentes…õ f…õ.
\v 18 M…ôŇčl…Ēl…ôsn…õ dis, m…ôl…Ēl…ôs s…Ē afum aka Yisrayel aŇč…õ n…ôyi m…Ē dis. T…Ēy…Ē tant…õ t…õnaŇčkan…õ k…ôlel…õ, m…ôf…Ētam k…ôy…Ē ti sona.
\v 19 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč m…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl dim dem m…ôwos…õ im…õŇčk…ôs …ôm nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôsol k…Ē Kanu m…Ē! Nt…õ p…ômar m…Ē, m…ôna m…ôy…Ēn…õ afum aka Yisrayel nn…Ē Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē, m…ôn'…Ē p…ômar m…ôcken…õ Kanu moloku ma k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ ma aka Yisrayel.
\v 20 M…ôl…Ēm…ôr Ňča sariy…õ sa Kanu, k…Ē m…õt…ôks…õ m…Ēn. M…ôment…ôr Ňča s…Ē d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēk…Ē p…ômar Ňčac…ôm…õ dar…ôŇč m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ē nt…õ p…ômar Ňča k…ôy…Ē m…Ē.
\v 21 M…ôy…õk-y…õk afum alompu aka Yisrayel f…ôp dac…Ē, aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčnes…õ Kanu m…Ē, afum ak…Ē ŇčayeŇčk…õ kance, aŇč…õ Ňčant…ĒfaŇč daka nd…õ d…Ēnt…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē. M…ôc…ômb…ôr afum wul o wul (1.000), afum am akak…Ē m…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē, w…ôkin p…ôy…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôb…õ, w…ôl…Ēma w…ôb…õ w…ôka afum tasar tin (100), w…ôl…Ēma w…ôb…õ w…ôka afum w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50), w…ôl…Ēma w…ôb…õ w…ôka afum w…ôco.
\v 22 Afum ay…õk-y…õk akak…Ē Ňčacboc…õ aka Yisrayel kiti t…õm f…ôp. Ňäacken…õ m…ôna Musa mes m…Ēp…ĒŇč, Ňča Ňčackiti mes m…õf…õt m…Ēk…Ē. M…ôbelin…õ p…õsar…õ, Ňča s…Ē Ňčamar …ôm k…ôsar…õ pi.
\v 23 K…Ē m…ôy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē, Kanu k…ôcsom…ôs …ôm ti-…õ, m…ôf…Ēt…Ēr…ôsn…õ. Tam…õr…ôŇč ta ti, afum akaŇč…õ ŇčaŇčk…Ē ndaraŇčan p…ôforu disr…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 24 K…Ē Musa …õnc…ôŇčk…ôl dim da papa ka w…ôran k…Ēn, k'…Ēy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …õnaloku k…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 25 K…Ē Musa …õy…õk-y…õk afum alompu Yisrayel f…ôp disr…õ, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr Ňča d…õb…õ: W…ôb…õ w…ôka afum wul win (1.000), w…ôb…õ w…ôka afum tasar tin (100), w…ôb…õ w…ôka afum w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50), w…ôb…õ w…ôka afum w…ôco.
\v 26 K'akak…Ē Ňčamboc…õ oŇč aka Yisrayel kiti t…õm f…ôp. Ňäacken…õ Musa mes mocuca k…ôboc kiti, Ňča Ňčacboc kiti ka mes m…õf…õt m…Ēk…Ē.
\p 
\v 27 K…Ē Musa elemb…ôrn…õ papa ka w…ôran k…Ēn, k…Ē w…ôkak…Ē olukus nde at…Ēf Ňč…Ēn.
\c 19
\ms2 Kanu k…ôsek danapa k…Ē Yisrayel
\r 19-24
\s1 Kanu k…ôwen…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôsek danapa
\p 
\v 1 Ňäof Ňča maas k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ Ňčawur Misira m…Ē, k'aka Yisrayel Ňčamb…õr…õ d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sinayi.
\v 2 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčay…õf…õ Refidim m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sinayi. D…ôndo k…Ē Ňčanc…ômb…ôr saŇčka Ňčat…õf…ôrn…õ t…Ēr…Ē ta di.
\v 3 K…Ē MARIKI ewe Musa t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč, k…Ē Musa …õmp…õ di. K…Ē MARIKI oloku k…Ē: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēloku afum a Yakuba akaŇč…õ, moloku mam…õ m…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēd…ôŇčk…ôr aka Yisrayel:
\v 4 N…ônan…ôŇčk n…ônas…ôrka t…Ēk…Ē inay…Ē aka Misira m…Ē: P…ôyi p…ôm…Ē banca ya asiksik y'if…õl…ôr…õn…õ nu, k…ôk…õr…õ nu nn…Ē iyi m…Ē.
\v 5 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, k…Ē n…ôsu l…ôŇč…ôs n…ônc…ôŇčk…ôl dim dem belbel, n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ s…Ē danapa dem nd…õ s…ônasek m…Ē-…õ, n…ôna aka Yisrayel n…ôŇčy…Ēn…õ akemi aka d…ôtim afum f…ôp dac…Ē. In'…Ēy…Ē doru f…ôp,
\v 6 mba k…Ē n…ôna aka Yisrayel, n…ôndey…Ēn'em afum aloŇčn…õ, n…ôy…Ēn'em s…Ē afum asoku. Moloku mam…õ m…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēloku Ňča.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 7 K…Ē Musa …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôwe abeki aka Yisrayel, k'ement…ôr Ňča moloku mm…õ MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē m…Ē.
\v 8 K'aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčasur…õn…õ k…ôloku Musa: ¬ęS…ôndey…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI oloku m…Ē f…ôp.¬Ľ K…Ē Musa oluks…õ MARIKI moloku mam…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel.
\v 9 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęIndeder nn…Ē m…ôyi m…Ē, igb…Ēpn…õ d…ôk…ôp k…ôp…ĒŇč, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčacn'em dim nt…õ inde iclok-lok…ôr …ôm m…Ē, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča s…Ē k…ôcgb…õk…ôr …ôm k…ôlaŇč t…õm f…ôp.¬Ľ K…Ē Musa k…ôluks…õ MARIKI moloku ma aka Yisrayel.
\s1 K…ôb…ôp…õn…õ ka Kanu k…Ē Musa nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē nde aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē, m…ôpus'em Ňča m…Ēk…Ē k…Ē alna teta k…ôb…ôp…õn…õ k…ôŇčan k…Ē ina, Ňčayak s…Ē yamos yaŇčan.
\v 11 Ňäalip k…ôlomp…ôsn…õ Ňčackar d…Ēs…Ēk…Ē, bawo tataka tat…Ēk…Ē, MARIKI endetor f…Ēr ya aka Yisrayel f…ôp kiriŇč nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi k…ôroŇč.
\v 12 M…ôk…Ē m…ôc…ômb…ôr Ňča agb…õp Ňča t…Ēr…Ē haŇč m…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr, m…ôcloku Ňča: ‚ÄĻN…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ ta n…ôp…õ d…ôt…Ēr…Ē, ta n…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ s…Ē agb…õp Ňča pi. Nw…õ o nw…õ ogbuŇč…õn…õ pi, m…õn…õ padif k…Ē.
\v 13 W…ôkayi, k…ôca k…ôf…ĒgbuŇč…õn…õ k…Ē, mba anca-cas k…Ē k…ôca-cas d…ôm, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, pas…Ē-s…Ēs…õ k…Ē c…ôb…ôlma. P…ôy…Ēn…õ w…õs…õm, p…ôy…Ēn…õ fum, nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčgbuŇčn…õ pi m…Ē, w…ôkayi …Ēf…Ēyi s…Ē doru.‚Äļ T…õm nt…õ afula k…ôl…õn ka aŇčkesiya dim d…Ēp…ĒŇč m…Ē, afum ay…õk-y…õk Ňčandenatam k…ôp…õs…õ t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 14 K…Ē Musa ontor d…ôt…Ēr…Ē k…ôder nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē, k'ompus Ňča, k…Ē Ňčayak s…Ē yamos yaŇčan.
\v 15 K…Ē Musa oloku aka Yisrayel: ¬ęN…ôlomp…ôsn…õ haŇč d…Ēs…Ēk…Ē, ta n…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ aran.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 Tataka ta maas b…ôtb…ôt k…Ē p…ôŇčkul…õ-kul…õ darenc, k…Ē p…ômot…ôr-mot…ôr, k…Ē k…ôp k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôyi t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč. K'aluk Ňčowur…õ dim p…ôp…ĒŇč, aka Yisrayel ak…Ē Ňčanayi d…ôsaŇčka m…Ē f…ôp, Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôyikc…õ.
\v 17 K…Ē Musa owur…õn…õ aka Yisrayel d…ôsaŇčka k…ôk…Ēb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčac…ôm…õ t…Ēr…Ē d…ônt…Ēf.
\v 18 T…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi f…ôp p…õncp…õ kinim…õ, bawo MARIKI …õnator di n…õnc disr…õ. Kinim…õ ka pi k…ôcp…õ p…ôm…Ē kinim…õ ka doco, k…Ē t…Ēr…Ē f…ôp p…õy…õf…õ k…ôyikc…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč.
\v 19 Nt…õ dim da aluk d…õncnaŇčkan…õ k…ôkul…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč m…Ē, Musa p…ôclok-loku, Kanu k…ôcluks…õ k…Ē moloku d…ôpukul…õ-kul…õ.
\v 20 K…Ē MARIKI ontor nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi k…ôroŇč, d…ôndo d…ôtelempan, k…Ē MARIKI ewe Musa, k…Ē Musa …õmp…õ.
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôtor m…ôk…Ē m…ôm…Ēn…õ aka Yisrayel ta Ňčab…õlk…ôr k…ôdem…Ēm…ôn MARIKI de, ta tedes…ĒŇč…õ alar…ôm k…ôfi.
\v 22 Ali aloŇčn…õn…õ aŇč…õ Ňčantam k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn'em m…Ē yati, Ňča s…Ē Ňčapusn…õ teta k…ôb…ôp…õn…õ k…ôŇčan k…Ē ina, ta Ňčas…ĒŇč…õ MARIKI k…ôdedif…ôt aloŇčn…õ al…Ēma k…ôgba k…ôŇčan.¬Ľ
\v 23 K…Ē Musa oloku MARIKI: ¬ęAka Yisrayel Ňčaf…Ēdetam k…ôp…õ t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi, bawo m…ônasom im belbel, m…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻM…ôment…ôr Ňča k…ôl…ônc…ôr, m…ôpus t…Ēr…Ē teta k…ôb…ôp…õn…õ k…ôŇčan k…Ē ina, m…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ pi afum.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\v 24 K…Ē MARIKI oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē, m…ôtor, n…ôp…õ k…Ē Aruna. Mba ta aloŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčab…õlk…ôr k…ôp…õ nn…Ē MARIKI eyi m…Ē de, ta Ňčades…ĒŇč'em k…ôdif…ôt afum k…ôgba k…ôŇčan dac…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 25 K…Ē Musa ontor nn…Ē afum Ňčayi m…Ē, k'olok-lok…ôr Ňča.
\c 20
\s1 Mosom w…ôco ma sariy…õ sa MARIKI mm…õ …õnas…ĒŇč Musa m…Ē
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku moloku mam…õ f…ôp:
\p 
\v 2 ¬ęIn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI Kanu kam, in'owur…õn'am at…Ēf Ňča Misira nde k…ôl…Ē ka dacar.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 3 ¬ęM…ôf…Ēdey…Ē canu c…ôl…Ēma f…Ēr ya ina kiriŇč.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 4 ¬ęTa m…ôpat s…Ē t…õr…ôŇčka, ta m…ôlomp…ôs paka o paka mp…õ powur…õn…õ k…Ē p…Ēk…Ē peyi d…ôk…Ēm, d…ônt…Ēf, k…Ē d…ôk…ôba m…Ē.
\v 5 Ta m…ôde m…ôctontn…õ ca yay…Ēk…Ē f…Ēr kiriŇč, ta m…ôde m…ôcsal…õn…õ yi s…Ē, bawo ina MARIKI, Kanu kam, Kanu k'iy…Ēn…õ nk…õ k…ôy…Ē k…ôraca m…Ē, nk…õ k…ôŇčluks…õ k…ôway ka kiciya ka papa nn…Ē awut …Ēn Ňčayi m…Ē, haŇč d…õt…õmp maas haŇč d…õt…õmp maŇčk…ôl…õ da ak…Ē Ňčanter im m…Ē.
\v 6 Mba int…Ēmp…ôr k…ôsekt…ôrn…õ danapa haŇč d…õt…õmp wul win (1.000) da afum aŇč…õ Ňčamb…Ēt…ôr im, Ňčam…õŇčk…ôrn…õ mosom mem m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 7 ¬ęTa m…ôdek…Ē m…ôcbonc tewe ta MARIKI Kanu kam kif…ôli. MARIKI …Ēf…ĒŇčaŇčn…õn…õ nw…õ ombonc…ôs tewe t…Ēn kif…ôli m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 8 ¬ęM…ôcc…õm-c…õmn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, m…ôpus'em di.
\v 9 Mata cam…ôt-tin tataka toluks…ôr disr…õ m…ôdek…Ē m…ôcb…ôc, m…ôclomp…ôs y…õb…ôc yam f…ôp mataka mam…Ēk…Ē disr…õ.
\v 10 Mba tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI Kanu kam m…Ē d…Ē. Ali y…õb…ôc ta m…ôb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ m…ôna, wan kam w…ôrkun k…Ē w…ôran, k…ôk…Ē ka w…ôcar kam w…ôrkun k…Ē w…ôran, k…ôb…ôp ka y…Ēc…Ēl yam k…Ē acik…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčayi s…ôdare sam m…Ē.
\v 11 Bawo mata cam…ôt-tin m…Ē MARIKI …õnalomp…ôs ant…Ēf, k…Ēm, k…ôba k…Ē ca c…ôk…Ē yeyi doru m…Ē f…ôp, k'eŇčes…ôm tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ MARIKI ompoc…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm p…ôt…Ēt, k'ampus…õ k…Ē di m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 12 ¬ęM…ôlel…ôs wisi k…Ē wiri, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ mataka mam meyi doru m…Ēb…Ēl nde ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēk…Ē MARIKI Kanu kam …Ēs…ĒŇč …ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 13 ¬ęTa m…ôdif fum.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 14 ¬ęTa m…ôsump…ôr dalak…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 15 ¬ęTa m…ôkiy…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 ¬ęTa m…ôbaŇč…õ w…õnc …ôm sede sa yem.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 17 ¬ęTa m…ôy…Ē f…Ēr gban-gban nn…Ē k…ôl…Ē ka w…õnc …ôm k…ôyi m…Ē. Ta m…ôy…Ē f…Ēr gban-gban nn…Ē w…ôran ka w…õnc …ôm eyi m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ w…ôcar k…Ēn w…ôrkun k…Ē w…ôran, wana w…Ēn, k…ôb…ôp ka s…Ēfale s…Ēn, ta m…ôfaŇč…õ daka o daka da w…õnc …ôm ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õl…õc.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 18 K'afum f…ôp, Ňčane pukul…õ-kul…õ pa darenc k…Ē dim da aluk k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk p…ômot…ôr-mot…ôr k…Ē kinim…õ k…ôcp…õ t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč. Nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčan…ôŇčk mes mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčayikc…õ, k…Ē Ňčanc…ôm…õ Ňčab…Ēl…õn…õ t…Ēr…Ē.
\v 19 K'aka Yisrayel Ňčaloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôlok-lok…ôr su, s…ôndec…ôŇčk…ôl …ôm, mba ta Kanu k…ôlok-lok…ôr su, ta t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôdefi.¬Ľ
\v 20 K…Ē Musa oloku aka Yisrayel: ¬ęTa n…ônes…õ, bawo k…ôwak…ôs konu k…Ē Kanu k…ônder…õn…õ. Nt…õ …õfaŇč m…Ē a n…ônes…õ k…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta n…ônciya m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 21 Aka Yisrayel Ňčac…ôm…õ p…ôb…Ēl…õ, mba Musa nk…Ēn p…ôcl…Ēt…ôrn…õ kubump nk…õ MARIKI …õnayi disr…õ m…Ē.
\s1 Sariy…õ ns…õ s…ôŇčkot…ôrn…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu m…Ē
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēloku aka Yisrayel: ‚ÄĻN…ôn…ôŇčk a d…ôk…Ēm iyi k…ôlok-lok…ôr nu.
\v 23 Ta n…ôde n…ôclomp…ôs ina f…Ēr kiriŇč canu ca gbeti, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, canu ca k…õma.
\v 24 M…ôde m…ôlomp…ôs'em tetek toloŇčn…õ pa dos, mp…õ n…ônde k…ôcloŇčn…õn'em k…ôroŇč yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf k…Ē yoloŇčn…õ yam ya k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu, Ňčkesiya k…Ē cir k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, c…ôna. Ina s…Ē indeder …ôm icpoc'am p…ôt…Ēt k…ôfo nk…õ o nk…õ inde ics…ĒŇč…õ k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ tewe tem m…Ē.
\v 25 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a tetek toloŇčn…õ pa masar p…Ē m…ôŇčlomp…ôs-…õ, ta m…ôlomps…õ pi masar m…õpat. Bawo k…Ē m…ômpat mi-…õ, m…ôŇčs…ĒŇč…õ mi k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk teta tetek toloŇčn…õ pem.
\v 26 Ta n…ôlomps'em tetek toloŇčn…õ mp…õ ande pacf…ôr…ôŇčk a pak…Ē paloŇčn'em m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta pan…ôŇčk w…ôk…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ēp…õs…õ k…ôk…ĒloŇčn'em m…Ē k…ôs…Ēk…ôr.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\c 21
\s1 Sariy…õ nn…Ē acar aHeb…ôre Ňčayi m…Ē
\p 
\v 1 ¬ęM…Ēy…Ē mokur f…Ēr ya Kanu kiriŇč mm…õ m…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēloku Ňča:
\v 2 K…Ē m…ôway w…ôcar w…ôHeb…ôre-…õ, p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôcar meren cam…ôt-tin. Teren ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, p…ôwur y…õŇč…ôn dacar ali k…ôway …Ēf…Ēs…ĒŇč.
\v 3 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ sona s'…õnayi t…õm nt…õ …õcb…õr…õ dacar m…Ē, sona s…Ēn s'oŇčwur s…Ē. K'…õnan…õnc…õ-…õ, w…ôran k…Ēn ŇčaŇčwur dacar.
\v 4 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a mariki m…Ēn …Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē w…ôran, w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē p…ôkom…õ k…Ē awut arkun k…Ē awut aran-…õ, awut k…Ē w…ôran, aka mariki m…Ēn Ňč…Ē ŇčaŇčy…Ēn…õ, nk…Ēn p…ôwur dacar sona s…Ēn.
\v 5 K…Ē w…ôcar nw…õ oloku: ‚ÄĻImb…Ēt…ôr mariki mem, awut em k…Ē w…ôran kem, ifaŇč f…õ k…ôwur dacar-…õ,‚Äļ
\v 6 awa, mariki m…Ēn p…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, p…ôbakc…ôr k…Ē d…ôkumba k…Ē p…ôyi f…õ ti-…õ, p…ôl…õk k…Ē p…ôbakc…ôr d…ôf…ôr…õm fa kumba k…Ēn. Mariki m…Ēn p…ôpif…õ k…Ē abak al…ôŇč…ôs, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē w…ôcar w…ôkak…Ē endey…Ēn…õ oŇč w…ôb…ôc…õ k…Ēn doru o doru.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 7 ¬ęK…Ē fum …õncam…ôs wan k…Ēn w…ôran p…ôk…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôcar-…õ, w…ôkak…Ē …Ēf…Ēwur dacar p…ôm…Ē awut arkun acar.
\v 8 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a mariki m…Ēn …õnaway k…Ē p…ôn…õnc…õ-…õ, t…õlp…ôs ta …Ēmb…Ēt k…Ē s…Ē mes-…õ, p…ômar p…ôce fum w…ôl…Ēma p…ôwurus k…Ē, mba sariy…õ s…ôf…Ēwos…õ mariki mam…Ēk…Ē k…ôcams…ôr k…Ē acik…ôra at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aHeb…ôre, bawo elip k…ôyemb…ôr k…Ē.
\v 9 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a mariki mam…Ēk…Ē wan k…Ēn w…ôrkun …õway…õ k…Ē k…ôn…õnc…õ-…õ, p…ômar p…ôy…Ē k…Ē t…Ēy…Ē tin tayi k…Ē awut …Ēn aran akom k…Ē Ňčandek…Ē d…ôk…ôl…Ē-…õ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē t…Ēy…Ē tokur f…Ēr ya Kanu kiriŇč toloku ti m…Ē.
\v 10 K…Ē mariki m…Ēn …õn…õnc…õ s…Ē w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma, p…ômar f…õ p…ôbeli nt…õ o nt…õ …Ēncy…Ē w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ yeri k…ôb…ôp ka yamos, haŇč k…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ.
\v 11 K…Ē mariki mm…õ …Ēnt…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôran nw…õ mes mam…õ maas-…õ, w…ôran w…ôkaw…õ …õntam k…ôwur dacar ali daka …Ēf…Ēs…ĒŇč, ali p…ôsam …Ēf…Ēs…ĒŇč.¬Ľ
\s1 Meciya mm…õ p…ômar padif…õ fum m…Ē
\p 
\v 12 ¬ęFum nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčsut w…ôl…Ēma haŇč p…ôdif k…Ē m…Ē, m…õn…õ padif w…ôkayi.
\v 13 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a m…ôŇčy…õf…õn…õ f…õ k…ôdif k…Ēn-…õ, Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k'efir …ôm d…ôwaca, indement…ôr …ôm k…ôfo nk…õ m…ôntam k…ôy…õks…õ m…ôk…Ē m…ôyacn…õ m…Ē.
\v 14 Nw…õ endif…õ w…õnc c…ômp…ônp…ôn p…ôy…õf…õn…õ ti m…Ē, ali p…ôyacn…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ pem k…ôroŇč, m…ôk…Ē m…ôl…õk k…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ padif k…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 15 ¬ęNw…õ o nw…õ oŇčsut kas, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, k…õr…õ m…Ē, m…õn…õ padif w…ôkayi.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 ¬ęNw…õ o nw…õ eŇčkiy…õ fum p…ôcam…ôs, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, pan…ôŇčk…õ k…Ē fum w…ôkak…Ē d…ôwaca m…Ē, m…õn…õ padif w…ôkayi.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 17 ¬ęNw…õ o nw…õ ontolan…õ kas, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, k…õr…õ p…ôl…õc m…Ē, m…õn…õ padif w…ôkayi.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôsut k…Ē k…ôbop…ôr
\p 
\v 18 ¬ęK…Ē afum ŇčaŇčgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ, w…ôkin p…ôt…õmp w…ôka m…õr…ôŇč k…Ēn tasar, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti aŇčkulma, k…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …Ēnt…Ēfi mba p…ôwon k…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ ti-…õ,
\v 19 k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a w…ôkak…Ē …õntam k…ôy…õf…õ p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôgbo p…ôk…Ēt…ôs doru-…õ, p…ômar pace w…ôkak…Ē …õnasut k…Ē m…Ē. Mba w…ôkak…Ē …õnasut k…Ē p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôcu m…Ē, …õmar k…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôway ka nt…õ …õyams…õ k…Ē y…õb…ôc m…Ē, p…ôt…õn…õ k…Ē s…Ē ac…Ēl haŇč p…ôtamn…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 20 ¬ęK…Ē fum …õnt…õmp w…ôcar k…Ēn k…ôt…Ēk, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôcar w…ôrkun, w…ôran, k…Ē w…ôcar w…ôkak…Ē efin…õ ti-…õ, aŇčluks…õ w…ôkayi ay…õk.
\v 21 Mba k…Ē w…ôcar w…ôkak…Ē efi f…õ haŇč tataka tin, mata m…õr…ôŇč mecep…ôr-…õ, af…Ēy…Ē fum w…ôkak…Ē nt…õ o nt…õ bawo daka da mariki m…Ēn d'…Ēy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 22 ¬ęK…Ē afum Ňčasut…õn…õ Ňčak…Ē Ňčasut…ôr…õn…õ w…ôran w…ôb…õk…ôs, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôkak…Ē k…ôkom mba ta daka o daka d…Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…Ē s…Ē-…õ, p…ômar wos ka w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē Ňčat…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē aboc kiti Ňčabonc…ôr asut…õn…õ k…ôway nk…õ ŇčaŇčs…ĒŇč f…ôp m…Ē.
\v 23 Mba k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a t…Ēs…ĒŇč w…ôran w…ôb…õk…ôs kak…Ē dolok…ôp-…õ, k…ôway ka defi k…ôy…Ēn…õ defi,
\v 24 d…Ēf…Ēr k…Ē d…Ēf…Ēr, desek k…Ē desek, k…ôca k…Ē k…ôca, k…ôc…ôk k…Ē k…ôc…ôk,
\v 25 k…ôc…Ēf k'aŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôc…Ēf k…ôway, k…ôbop…ôr k'aŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôbop…ôr k…ôway, k…ôfat k'aŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôfat k…ôway.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 26 ¬ęK…Ē fum oŇčsut w…ôcar k…Ēn w…ôrkun, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôran haŇč p…ôpici k…Ē d…Ēf…Ēr-…õ, p…ômar p…ôsak w…ôcar w…ôkak…Ē p…ôk…Ē y…õŇč…ôn, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôway ka d…Ēf…Ēr d…Ēn.
\v 27 K…Ē fum osut w…ôcar k…Ēn haŇč p…ôyotu k…Ē desek-…õ, p…ômar p…ôsak w…ôcar w…ôkak…Ē p…ôk…Ē y…õŇč…ôn, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôway ka desek d…Ēn.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 28 ¬ęK…Ē wana w…õncaŇč w…ôrkun, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôran l…õn, fum w…ôkak…Ē p…ôfin…õ ti-…õ, wana waw…Ēk…Ē w…õmar k…ôca-cas haŇč wefi, s…õm ya wana waw…Ēk…Ē y…õmar f…õ k…ôs…Ēm, ti disr…õ kiti nk…õ o nk…õ af…Ēs…Ēboc…ôr w…ôka wana waw…Ēk…Ē.
\v 29 Mba k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a wana w…Ē, tokur aŇča w…õnccaŇč afum l…õn, pacs…ĒŇč…õ ti w…ôs…ôrka k…ôc…ôr…õ ta w…ôkak…Ē …õŇčk…õmb…ôrn…õ wi haŇč wana waw…Ēk…Ē wedif fum-…õ, p…ômar paca-cas wana waw…Ēk…Ē haŇč wefi, w…ôka wana s…Ē m…õn…õ padif k…Ē.
\v 30 Mba k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a k…ôway k'awer w…ôka wana waw…Ēk…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta andif k…Ē m…Ē, p…ômar p…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôway kaŇčk…Ē awer k…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 31 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a wana, wan w…ôrkun k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ wan w…ôran wendif-…õ, t…Ēy…Ē tokur f…Ēr ya Kanu kiriŇč tin tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē p…ômar pak…Ēt…õn…õ.
\v 32 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a wana nw…õ w…ôcar w…ôrkun k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, w…ôcar w…ôran wendif-…õ, p…ômar pas…ĒŇč sik…ôl w…ôco maas (30) mariki ma w…ôcar w…ôkak…Ē, nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta wana m…Ē, paca-cas wi haŇč wefi.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 33 ¬ęK…Ē fum …õŇčkay abi, p…ôsak Ňči fos ta …õŇčgb…ôp…ôr Ňči, a wana w…ôder k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, s…Ēfale s…ôder s…ôtor abi ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē disr…õ-…õ,
\v 34 w…ôkay ka abi …õŇčl…õk p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē pefi m…Ē, p…ôs…ĒŇč w…ôka p…Ēc…Ēl p…ôsam p…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôway ka p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēn.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 35 ¬ęK…Ē wana wa fum wendif wana wa w…ôk…Ē-…õ, Ňčacam…ôs wana w…Ēk…Ē w…Ēnt…Ēfi m…Ē, Ňčayer…õn…õ p…ôsam, Ňčayer…õn…õ s…Ē s…õm ya wana w…Ēk…Ē wefi m…Ē.
\v 36 Mba k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ tokur aŇča wana w…Ē w…õnccaŇč l…õn, paloku ti w…ôs…ôrka ta owos…õ k…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ wi-…õ, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē w…ôka wana nw…õ w…õncaŇč w…Ēk…Ē l…õn a k…Ē wefi m…Ē, …õŇčl…õk wana wefi, p…ôs…ĒŇč w…ôk…Ē wana weyi w…ôyeŇč.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôkiy…õ ka y…Ēc…Ēl
\p 
\v 37 ¬ęK…Ē fum eŇčkiy…õ wana k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti aŇčkesiya, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti wir-…õ, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a …õfay p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē amera k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti p…ôcam…ôs pi-…õ, p…ômar p…ôluks…õ c…ôna k…ôcam…ôt k…ôway ka wana win w…Ēk…Ē eŇčkiy…õ m…Ē, Ňčkesiya maŇčk…ôl…õ k…ôway ka Ňčin Ňč…Ēk…Ē eŇčkiy…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\c 22
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ pab…ôp…õn…õ w…ôke p…ôcb…õr…õ k…ôk…Ēkiy…õ, pasut k…Ē haŇč p…ôfi-…õ, anc…ôr…õ f…õ teta mecir ma w…ôkak…Ē, af…Ēluks…õ ay…õk ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē.
\v 2 Mba k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a p…ôwaŇčk…ôra p…Ē amb…ôp…õn…õ w…ôkayi dec d…Ēs…Ēr…Ēyi d…õ-…õ, fum nw…õ oŇčsut w…ôke haŇč p…ôdif k…Ē m…Ē, t…õy…õf…õn…õ t…Ē. W…ôdif k…Ēn …õsar…õ teta mecir ma w…ôke w…ôkak…Ē. Mba w…ôke nw…õ aŇčsump…ôr m…Ē oŇčluks…õ k…ôway ka paka p…Ēk…Ē eŇčkiy…õ m…Ē, k'…Ēnt…Ētam k…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôway ka pi-…õ, p…ômar pacam…ôs w…ôke w…ôkak…Ē pas…ĒŇč k…ôway ka pi.
\v 3 K'amb…ôp…õ k…Ē paka pap…Ēk…Ē eŇčkiy…õ m…Ē p…Ēs…Ēr…Ēyi w…ôyeŇč-…õ, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ wana, s…Ēfale, aŇčkesiya, wir, w…ôkayi p…ômar p…ôluks…õ p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē p…ôdeŇč…ôr pi p…Ēc…Ēl pin.
\s1 K…ôl…ôs…ôr…õ ka fum daka d…Ēn
\p 
\v 4 K…Ē fum …õsak y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēn, y…Ēk…Ē y…Ēs…Ēm…õ w…õnc y…Ēb…Ēf y…Ēn ya dal…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē y…Ēn ya w…õn-…õ, p…ômar pam…Ēm…ôn ab…Ēf Ňč…Ēn nŇč…õ ŇčoŇčkom belbel m…Ē, pas…ĒŇč w…ôk…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēn y…Ēs…Ēm…õ y…Ēb…Ēf m…Ē, yokom y…Ēn y…Ēk…Ē yentes…õ m…Ē.
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē fum …õmb…õr yika n…õnc, n…õnc dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ēk…Ē d…Ēc…Ēf kur ka y…õt…õl d…Ēb…Ēf, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a y…Ēb…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ēl…Ēl, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti y…Ēs…Ēr…Ēbuk…õ-…õ, p…ômar w…ôb…õr ka n…õnc dad…Ēk…Ē p…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôway yi.
\v 6 K…Ē fum …Ēs…ĒŇč w…ônd…õ k…Ēn k…ôm…õŇčk ka p…ôsam, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti daka d…Ēl…Ēm, a pak…Ē pakiy…ôr w…ôkak…Ē anas…ĒŇč k…ôm…õŇčk m…Ē nde k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ k'an…ôŇčk w…ôke w…ôkak…Ē-…õ, p…ômar p…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôm…õr…ôŇč ka daka d…Ēk…Ē …õnakiy…õ m…Ē.
\v 7 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ an…ôŇčk f…õ w…ôke ka ca yay…Ēk…Ē-…õ, p…ômar w…ôk…Ē anas…ĒŇč daka k…ôm…õŇčk p…ôk…Ē p…ôment…ôrn…õ Kanu p…ôd…õr…ôm a …õnc…ôr…õ f…õ t…Ēs…Ēl…õ nt…õ o nt…õ ta daka dad…Ēk…Ē.
\p 
\v 8 Tes o tes t'aŇčgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta wana, s…Ēfale, aŇčkesiya, wir k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, yamos, paka mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ēs…Ēl…õ, afum m…õr…ôŇč Ňčacgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka w…ôka p…Ēc…Ēl k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti paka p…Ēl…Ēm-…õ, agb…õk…ôl…õn…õ akak…Ē m…õr…ôŇč Ňčak…Ē Ňčament…ôrn…õ nda akiti f…Ēr ya Kanu kiriŇč. Nw…õ kiti k…ôŇčk…Ēl…õc…õ m…Ē, fum w…ôkak…Ē p…ôs…ĒŇč w…ôk…Ē Ňčanayi k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ m…Ē m…õr…ôŇč ma paka p…Ēk…Ē Ňčanayi k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ ta pi m…Ē.
\p 
\v 9 K…Ē fum …Ēs…ĒŇč w…õnc k…ôc…Ēl t…Ēy…Ēn…õ wana, s…Ēfale, aŇčkesiya, wir t…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ o mp…õ, a p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē pefi, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, p…ôt…õp…õ k…ôc…ôk, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti pakiy…õ pi, ta fum o fum …õnt…ôŇčn…õ ti-…õ,
\v 10 p…ômar fum w…ôk…Ē anas…ĒŇč k…ôc…Ēl m…Ē, p…ôk…Ē p…ôd…õrm…õ w…õnc w…ôk…Ē …õnas…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôc…Ēl m…Ē a …õŇčkiy…õ f…õ p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēk…Ē w…õnc …õnas…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôc…Ēl m…Ē. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē p…ômar w…ôka p…Ēc…Ēl p…ôwos…õ k…ôd…õr…ôm kaŇčk…Ē, p…ômar f…õ s…Ē w…õnc p…ôluks…õ k…ôway ka pi.
\v 11 Mba k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a aŇčkiy…õ p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ nde k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn-…õ, p…ômar p…ôluks…õ k…ôway ka pi w…õnc w…ôk…Ē …õnas…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôc…Ēl m…Ē.
\v 12 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a w…õs…õm wa dop w…õwat…ôri-wat…ôri p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē-…õ, fum w…ôk…Ē anas…ĒŇč k…ôc…Ēl m…Ē, …õmar k…ôken…õ s…õm y…õlp…ôs yay…Ēk…Ē w…ôk…Ē …õnas…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôc…Ēl m…Ē, w…ôkak…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ s…Ē w…ôn…ôŇčk ka ti. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē p…ômar f…õ k…Ē s…Ē k…ôluks…õ k…ôway ka pi nw…õ …õnas…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôc…Ēl m…Ē.
\p 
\v 13 K…Ē fum …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôyefu p…Ēc…Ēl nn…Ē w…õnc eyi m…Ē, a p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē pede p…õt…õp…õ k…ôc…ôk, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti pefi kumunt ka w…ôka p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē dar…ôŇč-…õ, p…ômar w…ôk…Ē …õnak…Ē p…ôyefu w…õnc p…Ēc…Ēl m…Ē, p…ôluks…õ pi k…ôway.
\v 14 K…Ē p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē pefi f…Ēr ya w…ôka pi kiriŇč-…õ, k…ôluks…õ k…ôway ka p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē k…ôyi f…õ s…Ē. K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ anas…ĒŇč k…Ē daka a p…ôcyefu k…Ē p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē-…õ, p…ônt…ôŇčn…õ tat…Ēk…Ē.
\s1 Sariy…õ sa amera k…Ē din…õ s…ôl…Ēma
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē w…ôrkun …õŇčk…õlt…ôr w…ôyec…ôra w…ôt…Ēc…ôr…õ w…ôrkun, nw…õ w…ôrkun …õntat…Ēfac m…Ē, haŇč Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…õ-…õ, p…ômar p…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôfac ka w…ôyec…ôra w…ôkak…Ē, p…ôl…õk k…Ē s…Ē p…ôn…õnc…õ.
\v 16 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a papa ka w…ôyec…ôra nw…õ owos…õ f…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč ka w…ôrkun nw…õ w…ôyec…ôra k…Ēn-…õ, t…Ēf…Ēyams…õ w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč ka k…ôfac ka w…ôyec…ôra w…ôkak…Ē Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn m…Ē.
\p 
\v 17 Ta n…ôsak w…ôran dure p…ôyi doru.
\p 
\v 18 Nw…õ o nw…õ …õŇčf…ônt…ôr…ôr w…õs…õm m…Ē, m…õn…õ padif w…ôkak…Ē.
\p 
\v 19 Nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčloŇčn…õ canu c…ôcuru ta p…ôy…Ēn…õ MARIKI-…õ, m…õn…õ pasut k…Ē haŇč p…ôm…ôlk…õ.
\p 
\v 20 Ta m…ôdir w…ôcik…ôra, ta m…ôment…ôr k…Ē s…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr, bawo n…ôna s…Ē n…ônayi decik…ôra at…Ēf Ňča Misira.
\p 
\v 21 Ta n…ôt…Ēr…ôs w…ôc…ôbok…ôra nw…õ o nw…õ, ta n…ôt…Ēr…ôs s…Ē wan nw…õ o nw…õ akomb…ôra …Ēn Ňčafi m…Ē.
\v 22 K…Ē m…ôt…Ēr…ôs fum w…ôkak…Ē haŇč k…ôbok k…Ēn k…ôder im-…õ, iŇčne k…ôbok k…Ēn,
\v 23 p…ônt…õl'em p…ôp…ĒŇč, d…ôk…ôwan indif'am dakma. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē m…ôna s…Ē w…ôran kam endey…Ēn…õ w…ôc…ôbok…ôra, awut am Ňčay…Ēn…õ at…Ēy…Ē kas.
\p 
\v 24 K…Ē m…ômb…Ēr w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka p…ôsam afum em dac…Ē-…õ, ta m…ôy…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē w…ôb…Ēs-b…Ēs…ôr w…ôl…Ēma …ĒŇčy…Ē m…Ē, ta m…ôloku a m…õn…õ p…ôdeŇč…ôr'am gb…õs d…ôk…ôluks…õ da debe dam.
\v 25 K…Ē fum …õnc…ômb…ôr'am s…õk…õ duma d…Ēn da k…ôfe-…õ, m…ôluks…õ k…Ē di a dec d…õckal…õ,
\v 26 bawo duma dad…Ēk…Ē gb…ôc…ôr…ôm d…Ēy…Ē dokump…õ da dis d…Ēn. Dere d'…ĒŇčk…Ēkump…õn…õ a p…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ-…õ? K…Ē w…ôkayi oŇčkorn'em-…õ, iŇčne k…Ē dim bawo Kanu nk…õ iy…Ēn…õ m…Ē, iŇčy…Ēn…õ n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr.
\p 
\v 27 Ta m…ôf…ôr-f…ôr…ôs Kanu, ta m…ôtolan…õ w…ôkiriŇč w…ôka afum am p…ôl…õc.
\p 
\v 28 Ta n…ôcwon k…ôk…õr'em yoloŇčn…õ ya y…õt…õl yonu. N…ôcs…ĒŇč im awut anu arkun ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē.
\v 29 Ti t…Ē p…ômar s…Ē m…ôcy…Ē nn…Ē wana wam, aŇčkesiya Ňčam k…Ē wir wam p…ômar wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôka p…Ēc…Ēl pam Ňčayi k…Ē k…õr…õ mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. Tataka ta cam…ôt-maas, m…ôs…ĒŇč im pi.
\p 
\v 30 Afum apus Ňč…Ē n…ôndey…Ēn'em, p…ômar f…õ n…ôde n…ôcs…Ēm s…õm ny…õ w…õs…õm w…õwat…ôri-wat…ôri d…ôkulum m…Ē, n…ôde n…ôcgbal…õ yi cen.
\c 23
\s1 K…ôlel…ôs ka at…Ēy…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr
\p 
\v 1 ¬ęTa m…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ yem. Ta m…ôbaŇč…õ fum w…ôl…õc k…ôbaŇč…õ ka yem.
\v 2 Ta m…ôc…ôm…õ k…ônay dar…ôŇč k…ôk…Ēy…Ē p…ôl…õc. K'andeboc…õ afum kiti-…õ, ta m…ôlasn…õ k…ôca k'afum alar…ôm yem disr…õ n…ôs…ĒŇč…õ aboc kiti k…ôf…õr kiti.
\v 3 Ta m…ôbaŇč…õ w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka d…ôŇčkiti k'…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē kance-…õ.
\p 
\v 4 K…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ē m…ôp…ôt…ôrn…õ wana wa w…ôter…õn…õ kam k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti s…Ēfale s…Ēn s…ôs…Ēl…õ-…õ, m…ôsump…ôr si m…ôk…õr…õ k…Ē dare.
\v 5 K…Ē m…ôn…ôŇčk s…Ēfale sa w…ôter…õn…õ kam s…ôt…õmp…õn…õ p…õsar…õ pa si d…ônt…Ēf-…õ, ta m…ôcep…ôr, m…ômar k…Ē k…ôdeŇč-deŇči si p…õsar…õ.
\p 
\v 6 Ta n…ôyay sariy…õ sa w…õnc …ôm w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka d…ôŇčkiti.
\v 7 M…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ toloku ta yem, ta m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôt…Ēl…ôs…ôr tes k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ ti-…õ w…ôlompu k…ôfi, bawo if…Ēsak fum w…ôl…õc p…ôk…Ē y…õŇč…ôn.
\v 8 Ta m…ôbaŇč k…ôpoc…õ ka d…ôŇčkiti, bawo k…ôpoc…õ kaŇčk…Ē k…ôŇčs…ĒŇč…õ an…ôŇčk k…ôt…Ēs…Ēn…ôŇčk kance, k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ s…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk kance ka alompu.
\p 
\v 9 Ta m…ôt…Ēr…ôs w…ôcik…ôra nw…õ …õnd…õ ndaram m…Ē. N…ônc…ôr…õ belbel t…Ēk…Ē p…ôŇčyi k…Ē m…Ē, bawo acik…ôra Ňč…Ē n…ônay…Ēn…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira.¬Ľ
\s1 Teren ta k…ôŇčes…ôm k…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm
\p 
\v 10 ¬ęMeren cam…ôt-tin m…ôcb…Ēf ant…Ēf Ňčam, m…ôcpim yokom Ňča Ňči.
\v 11 Mba teren ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňči k…ôŇčes…ôm m…ôsak Ňči. It…Ē afum am at…Ēy…Ē daka Ňčandin…õ s…Ē Ňči k…Ē s…õm ya dop s…Ē y…Ēs…Ēm y…õlp…ôs y…Ēk…Ē. M…ôy…Ē s…Ē tin tayi ta Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē yam ya w…õn k…Ē t…Ēk yam ya olif.
\p 
\v 12 M…ôb…ôc y…õb…ôc yam mata cam…ôt-tin. Mba tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, m…ôlel…ôs d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ wana k…Ē s…Ēfale sam yeŇčes…ôm d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…Ē wan ka w…ôcar kam w…ôran k…Ē w…ôcik…ôra Ňčatam s…Ē k…ôŇčes…ôm m…Ē.
\p 
\v 13 N…ôc…ôm…õ mam…õ iloku nu m…Ē f…ôp dar…ôŇč. N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ belbel ta n…ôde n…ôckorn…õ canu c…ôcuru. Ta n…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs mewe ma canu c…ôcuru, ta panen…õ nu mi d…ôkusu yati!¬Ľ
\s1 C…ôsata ca sali nc…õ p…ômar pacboc Yisrayel m…Ē
\p 
\v 14 ¬ęK…ôren o k…ôren m…ôdek…Ē m…ôcboc'em c…ôsata ca sali maas.
\v 15 M…ôde m…ôcboc'em k…ôsata ka c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin. Mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ma k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē disr…õ, Ňčof Ňča Abib\f + \fr 23:15 \fq Ňäof Ňča Abib\ft = C…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęŇčof Ňča L…õŇčk¬Ľ\f*, m…ôde m…ôcs…Ēm c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē isom …ôm ti Misira m…Ē, bawo Ňčof ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē disr…õ Ňč…Ē m…ônawur di. P…ômar f…õ pade pacment…ôrn…õ f…Ēr yem kiriŇč waca w…Ēs…Ēk…ôr.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 ¬ęM…ôde m…ôcboc'em s…Ē k…ôsata ka K…ôt…õl, yokom y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ya y…Ēb…Ēf yam ya dal…õ.¬Ľ
\p ¬ęK…Ē m…ônde m…ôcboc'em k…ôsata ka K…ôpim ka y…Ēb…Ēf yam ya teren d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr, k…Ē m…ôlip k…ôloŇčka ka yokom ya t…Ēk yam-…õ.
\v 17 K…ômaas teren disr…õ p…ômar arkun f…ôp afum anu dac…Ē Ňčament…ôrn…õ f…Ēr ya W…ôb…õ MARIKI kiriŇč.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 18 ¬ęTa m…ôloŇč mecir ma yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ m…ôŇčk…õr'em m…Ē paka p…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin mp…õ o mp…õ. Ta n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ moro ma poloŇčn…õ pem haŇč d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk b…ôtb…ôt.
\v 19 M…ôde m…ôck…õr…õ nde k…ôl…Ē ka MARIKI Kanu kam yokom y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ya y…Ēb…Ēf ya at…Ēf Ňčam. Ta m…ôp…õc…õ wir m…õs…õ ma k…õr…õ ka wi de.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôs…ĒŇč temer k…Ē k…ôt…ôk…ôs t…Ēk…Ēt a Ňčacl…õk d…Ēp…Ē k…ôk…Ē
\p 
\v 20 ¬ęK'ina, indesom m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ mendey'…ôm kiriŇč, mm…õ mendek…Ē mocbum …ôm d…Ēp…Ē m…Ē, mosol'am haŇč m…ôb…õr…õ k…ôfo nk…õ inalomps'am m…Ē.
\v 21 M…ôdek…Ē m…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ f…Ēr ya mi kiriŇč, m…ôdek…Ē m…ôc…ôm…õ dim da mi dar…ôŇč. Ta m…ôyeŇčk…ôr mi domp, bawo m…Ēf…Ēdek…ĒŇčaŇčn…õ d…õtaŇči l…ôŇč…ôs dam, bawo tewe tem teyi mi disr…õ.
\v 22 K…Ē m…ônc…ôŇčk…ôl dim d…Ēn belbel, m…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ilok'…ôm m…Ē f…ôp-…õ, indey…Ēn…õ w…ôter ka ater…õn…õ am, w…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ ka aŇč…õ Ňčamb…ôp …ôm k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ m…Ē.
\p 
\v 23 M…õl…õk…õ mem mendek…Ēt f…Ēr yam kiriŇč mekek…ôr…õ nda Am…Ēr, aHit, aPerisi, aKanaŇč, aHiwy k…Ē aYebus, indek…Ēm…ôl…ôk Ňča.
\v 24 Ta m…ôtontn…õn…õ canu c…ôŇčan, ta m…ôsal…õn…õ ci. Ta m…ôcy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ŇčaŇčy…Ē m…Ē, mba m…ôcl…ôs…ôr m…õr…ôŇčka maŇčan few, m…ôcw…Ēk…ôc masar motontn…õ m…Ēk…Ē Ňčacc…ômb…ôr m…Ē.
\v 25 K…Ē n…ôndek…Ē n…ôcsalin…õ MARIKI Kanu konu-…õ, endek…Ē p…ôcs…ĒŇč p…ôt…Ēt k…ôcom kam k…Ē domun dam p…ôb…Ēl…õn'am docu.
\v 26 W…ôran w…ôc…ĒŇč …Ēf…Ēdek…Ēyi at…Ēf Ňčam, w…ôran w…ôt…Ēkom …Ēf…Ēk…Ēs…Ēyi di. Indes…ĒŇč am k…ôwon doru.
\p 
\v 27 Ayek-yek Ňč'indenuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôsak Ňčey'…ôm kiriŇč, indew…õn…ôr afum ak…Ē n…ôndek…Ē ndaraŇčan m…Ē f…ôp anciyan, indek…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ ater…õn…õ anu f…ôp Ňčay…õks…ôr nu.
\v 28 Deme d'indenuŇčk…õn…õ isak dey'…ôm kiriŇč, nd…õ dendek…Ēb…õl…ôs aHiwy, aKanaŇč k…Ē aHit m…Ē.
\v 29 If…Ēdek…Ēb…õl…ôs Ňča f…Ēr yam kiriŇč k…ôren kin, ta tedes…ĒŇč…õ at…Ēf k…ôy…Ē yer-yer, s…õm y…õl…õc ya dop y…õla ny…õ yendet…Ēr…ôs …ôm m…Ē.
\v 30 P…ôpic p…ôpic p'indek…Ē icb…õl…ôs Ňča f…Ēr yam kiriŇč haŇč m…ôcla m…ôctam k…ôbaŇč at…Ēf f…ôp.
\v 31 Indek…Ēboc'am k…ôl…ônc…ôr k…ôy…õf…õ ka k…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma haŇč nde k…ôba k'aFilisti, k…ôy…õf…õ ka nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ haŇč nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka ∆źf…ôrat. Bawo indek…Ēl…õk afum aka at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē ib…õr …ôm Ňča d…ôwaca, ib…õl…ôs Ňča f…Ēr yam kiriŇč.
\v 32 Ta m…ôdek…ĒcaŇč…ôs danapa k…Ē Ňča, ta m…ôcaŇč…ôs s…Ē danapa k…Ē canu c…ôŇčan.
\v 33 Ňäaf…Ēdek…Ē nd…õ at…Ēf Ňčam, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčades…ĒŇč'am k…ôciya nn…Ē iyi m…Ē. K…Ē m…ôsak afum akak…Ē k…ônd…õ ndaram-…õ, t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč'am k…ôsali canu c…ôŇčan, t…Ēy…Ēn'am towul.¬Ľ
\c 24
\s1 Kanu k…ôsek danapa k'aka Yisrayel
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku Musa: M…ôp…õ nn…Ē MARIKI iyi m…Ē, m…ôna, Aruna, Nadab k…Ē Abihu, k…Ē abeki w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (70) aka Yisrayel, n…ôdek…Ē n…ôtontn'em p…ôb…Ēl…õ.
\v 2 Musa sona endel…Ēt…ôrn…õ MARIKI, ak…Ē Ňčaf…Ēdel…Ēt…ôrn…õ de, afum s…Ē Ňčaf…Ēdep…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn.
\v 3 K…Ē Musa ender k'oloku moloku ma MARIKI mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp aka Yisrayel, k…Ē mosom m…Ēn f…ôp. K'aka Yisrayel Ňčawos…õ dim din: ¬ęMoloku mm…õ MARIKI oloku m…Ē f…ôp, s…ôndey…Ē mi¬Ľ.
\v 4 K…Ē Musa encic…ôs moloku ma MARIKI f…ôp. Dec dendes…Ēk k'…õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ nde t…Ēr…Ē d…ônt…Ēf k'…õnc…ômb…ôr s…Ē masar w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč teta t…õc…õmc…õm…ôs ta cusuŇčka nc…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč ca Yisrayel.
\v 5 K'osom at…õmp aka Yisrayel Ňčaken…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf, Ňčaken…õ s…Ē MARIKI mura ma k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu.
\v 6 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk dac…Ē da mecir mam…Ēk…Ē k'…õmb…õr mi d…ôt…Ēb…Ēl, k'…õw…õs…ôs…ôr dac…Ē da mecir tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč.
\v 7 K'…õl…õk buk ba Danapa nd…õ ŇčanacaŇč…ôs k…Ē MARIKI m…Ē, k'…õŇčkaraŇč…õn…õ bi aka Yisrayel. K'aka Yisrayel Ňčaloku: S…ôndec…ôm…õ t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI oloku m…Ē dar…ôŇč f…ôp, s…ôndes…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē.
\v 8 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk mecir k'…õw…õs…ôs…ôr mi aka Yisrayel, k'oloku: N…ôn…ôŇčk mecir ma danapa nd…õ MARIKI esek k…Ē n…ôna aka Yisrayel m…Ē mam…õ, k…Ē mosom m…Ēn mm…õ n…ônt…ôŇčn…õ m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 9 K…Ē Musa Ňčamp…õ k'Aruna, Nadab, Abihu k…Ē abeki aŇč…õ w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (70) aka Yisrayel.
\v 10 K…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk Kanu ka Yisrayel p…ôc…ômb…ôr…ôr w…õc…ôk wa Ki tant…Ēf, p…ônayi p…ôm…Ē nt…õ aŇčlomp…ôs paka p…Ēy…Ē alom Ňča bulu m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē k…Ēm k…ôŇčs…Ēk m…Ē.
\v 11 Mba …õnatenci f…õ k…ôca k…Ēn afum ap…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel akak…Ē k…ôroŇč. K…Ē ŇčaŇčgb…ôtn…õ Kanu, k…Ē Ňčandi yeri k…Ē Ňčamun.
\s1 K…ôb…ôp…õn…õ ka Musa nde d…ôt…Ēr…Ē k…Ē Kanu
\p 
\v 12 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: M…ôp…õ nn…Ē iyi m…Ē, nn…Ē t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč m…ôde m…ôc…ôm…õ nn…Ē k…ôr…õsna: Walak…õ wa masar w'indes…ĒŇč …ôm, sariy…õ k…Ē tosom tem t'incic…ôs wi k…ôroŇč nt…õ m…ôŇčk…Ēt…ôks…õ aka Yisrayel m…Ē.
\v 13 Musa …õy…õf…õ k…Ē Yosuwe w…ômar…ôs k…Ēn, k…Ē Musa …õmp…õ t…Ēr…Ē ta Kanu k…ôroŇč.
\v 14 K'oloku abeki aka Yisrayel: ¬ęN…ôkar su nn…Ē haŇč s…ôder s…Ē s…ôb…ôp nu. N…ôm…Ēm…ôn Aruna k…Ē Hur Ňčayi nu d…õ k…ôs…ôk. Nw…õ o nw…õ tes t…õmb…ôp m…Ē, w…ôkayi p…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Ňča.¬Ľ
\v 15 K…Ē Musa …õmp…õ s…Ē d…ôt…Ēr…Ē, k…Ē k…ôp k…ôŇčgb…ôp…ôr t…Ēr…Ē.
\v 16 K…Ē n…Ēr…Ē da debeki da MARIKI deyi t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi k…ôroŇč oŇč, k…Ē k…ôp k…ôŇčgb…ôp…ôr t…Ēr…Ē haŇč mata cam…ôt-tin. Tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, MARIKI p…ôyi d…ôk…ôp k'ewe Musa.
\v 17 N…Ēr…Ē da debeki da MARIKI d…õnawur…õn…õ n…õnc aka Yisrayel d…ôf…Ēr p…ôm…Ē nt…õ n…õnc d…Ēp…ĒŇč dende k…ôcmar t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč m…Ē.
\v 18 K…Ē Musa …õmb…õr…õ k…ôp kaŇčk…Ē disr…õ, k'…õmp…õ nde t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč. K…Ē Musa …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôwon nde t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč mata w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) daŇč k…Ē pibi.
\c 25
\ms2 T…õc…ômb…ôr ta aŇčgbancan Ňčosoku
\mr 25-31
\s1 K…ôf…õk ka aka Yisrayel
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel a ŇčabaŇč…ôs k…ôf…õk kem. N…ôbaŇč k…ôpoc…õ ka nw…õ o nw…õ …ĒŇčs…Ēk ab…ôk…ôc p…õs k…ôs…ĒŇč ki m…Ē.
\v 3 K…ôf…õk nk…õ k…Ē n…ôndebaŇčs…ôr Ňča: K…õma, gbeti, k…Ēp…ôr,
\v 4 c…ôloto c…ôgb…ôt kar…õ alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňčeyim Ňčeyimb…ôr…ôr, c…ôloto nc…õ andun…õ s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler k…Ē nc…õ andun…õ c…ôfon ca wir m…Ē,
\v 5 kata ya Ňčkesiya ny…õ aŇčgb…ôt kar…õ alom Ňčeyim m…Ē, kata ya ntempeli, t…Ēk ya kasiya,
\v 6 moro momot…õn…õ, labund…õ dobotu amb…Ēnc nd…õ ande pacn…ĒŇčk…ôl moro m…Ēb…Ēy m…Ēs…Ēk…ôsn…õ, k…Ē suray s…ôbotu amb…Ēnc,
\v 7 k…Ē masar m…Ēt…Ēt mm…õ aŇčwe onik…ôs m…Ē k…Ē m…Ēt…Ēt m…Ēl…Ēma mm…õ andeb…õr duma da ef…Ēd k…Ē yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc m…Ē.
\v 8 K…ôfo k…ôsoku k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčandec…ômb…ôr'em, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ idetam k…ônd…õ Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē.
\v 9 P…ôm…Ē yay…Ēk…Ē indement…ôr …ôm m…Ē, m…ôlomp…ôs ca ya d…ôkiyi dosoku k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya di p…ôm…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 KaŇčk…ôra ka sede
\p 
\v 10 ¬ęKaŇčk…ôra ka k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya k…Ē Ňčandelomp…ôs. Ňäatubuc ki dobolu cururu m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē dac…Ē, k…Ē dowokulu da ki kururu katin k…Ē dac…Ē k…Ē dotukum da ki kururu katin k…Ē dac…Ē.
\v 11 M…ôsop kaŇčk…ôra kaŇčk…Ē k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs, tedisr…õ k…Ē todoru, pay…Ē ki k…ôb…ôr ka k…õma haŇč pan…ĒŇčk…ôr.
\v 12 Palomp…ôs c…ôsora maŇčk…ôl…õ ca k…õma nc…õ andek…Ēb…õr kaŇčk…ôra kaŇčk…Ē d…ômoŇčkubut m…Ē c…ôsora m…õr…ôŇč k…ôs…ôk kin, k…Ē c…ôk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč k…ôs…ôk ka m…õr…ôŇč k…ôŇčk…Ē.
\v 13 M…ôpat c…ôgbo m…õr…ôŇč ca t…Ēk ya kasiya m…ôsop ci k…õma.
\v 14 Pasor c…ôgbo cac…Ēk…Ē d…ôc…ôsora ca k…õma cac…Ēk…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pade pactam k…ôs…õl…õŇč kaŇčk…ôra kaŇčk…Ē pacgbaŇčn…õ m…Ē.
\v 15 K'alip k…ôsor c…ôgbo cac…Ēk…Ē d…ôc…ôsora ca kaŇčk…ôra-…õ, p…ômar f…õ s…Ē pasulu ci.
\v 16 KaŇčk…ôra kaŇčk…Ē disr…õ k…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēb…õr walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa dem k'aka Yisrayel nw…õ indes…ĒŇč …ôm m…Ē.
\p 
\v 17 Af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs k…Ē n…ôndek…Ēlomps…õ Ňči. Dobolu da Ňči dendey…Ē cururu m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē dac…Ē, k…Ē dowokulu da Ňči kururu katin k…Ē dac…Ē. Af…õŇčk ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčendey…Ēn…õ Ňč…õgb…ôp…ôr…õ kaŇčk…ôra.
\v 18 M…ôlomps…õ m…õl…õk…õ kerub\f + \fr 25:18 \fq M…õl…õk…õ kerub\ft = M…õl…õk…õ m…Ē mm…õ m…õnay…Ē y…õb…ôc ya k…ôbum mofo mosoku ma Kanu m…Ē. \f* m…õr…ôŇč k…õma k…ôt…õmp, m…ôs…õl…ôr…õn…õ mi d…ôk…ôcop k…Ē d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya k…ôroŇč.
\v 19 M…ôs…õl…ôr…õn…õ m…õl…õk…õ kerub min d…ôk…ôcop da af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya k…ôroŇč, m…õl…õk…õ kerub m…Ēk…Ē d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da Ňči k…ôroŇč. M…ôlomp…ôs m…õl…õk…õ kerub m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē af…õŇčk ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ paka pin nde d…ôk…ôcop k…Ē d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da Ňči k…ôroŇč.
\v 20 M…õl…õk…õ mam…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč mendek…Ēperi banca tak…ôroŇč, yi yokump af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya, m…õt…õf…ôr…õn…õ meti c…ôro nde af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya k…ôroŇč.
\v 21 K'alip k…ôb…õr ki disr…õ walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa dem k…Ē aka Yisrayel nw…õ indes…ĒŇč …ôm m…Ē, m…ôgb…ôp…ôr…õ kaŇčk…ôra af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē.
\v 22 D…ônda af…õŇčk ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē k…ôroŇč s…ônde s…ôcb…ôp…õn…õ, m…õl…õk…õ kerub mam…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē mm…õ meyi af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē aŇčgb…ôp…ôr kaŇčk…ôra kaŇčk…Ē k…ôroŇč m…Ē. Dif…Ē indek…Ē icsom …ôm m…õfaŇč mem f…ôp m…Ēk…Ē m…ônde m…ôcloku aka Yisrayel m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Am…õsa Ňča c…ôcom nc…õ aŇčs…ĒŇč Kanu m…Ē
\p 
\v 23 ¬ęM…ôlomps…õ am…õsa k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya. Dobolu da Ňči d…Ēy…Ē cururu m…õr…ôŇč, dowokulu da Ňči d…Ēy…Ē kururu katin, k…Ē deŇčeci da Ňči kururu katin k…Ē dac…Ē.
\v 24 M…ôsop am…õsa ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs, m…ôlomp…ôs Ňči c…ôs…ôk k…ôb…ôr ka k…õma haŇč m…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr.
\v 25 M…ôboc c…ôbam c…ôl…Ēma c…ôs…ôk cac…Ēk…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ tant…Ēf, dowokulu da ci d…Ēcy…Ē k…ôca disr…õ, m…ôn…õps…ôr ci k…õma haŇč m…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr.
\v 26 M…ôlomp…ôs c…ôsora maŇčk…ôl…õ ca k…õma, m…ôboc ci d…ômoŇčkubut k…ôsur…õn…õ ka y…õc…ôm…õn…õ maŇčk…ôl…õ ya am…õsa ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē.
\v 27 C…ôsora cac…Ēk…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ c…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ f…ôr…õm. C…ôsora cac…Ēk…Ē c'andek…Ēsor c…ôgbo nc…õ ande pacl…õk…õn…õ am…õsa ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.
\v 28 M…ôpat c…ôgbo ca k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya, m…ôsop ci k…õma, c…ôgbo cac…Ēk…Ē c'andek…Ē pactam k…ôgbaŇčn…õn…õ am…õsa ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē.
\v 29 M…ôlomps…õ Ňči ca nc…õ p…ômar m…Ē: P…ôlet, m…Ēb…Ēl, s…ôp…Ēt k…Ē mapan ny…õ andek…Ē pacb…ôc…õ yoloŇčn…õ ya moro k…Ē w…õn m…Ē, k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs k…Ē m…ôndelomps…õ yi.
\v 30 P…ômar m…ôde m…ôcc…ômb…ôr'em k…ôcom nk…õ ande pacloŇčn'em m…Ē nn…Ē am…õsa ŇčaŇč…õ k…ôroŇč t…õm o t…õm.¬Ľ
\s1 P…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp pa wara cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč
\p 
\v 31 ¬ęM…ôde m…ôlomps…õ p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp k…õma k…ôt…õmp k…ôsoku p…õs. Pas…õl…ôr…õn…õ pi k…ôy…õf…õ ka p…õc…ôm…õn…õ k…ôk…Ē t…ômboŇčk pa pi, y…Ēn…Ēn…õ ya s…ôlamp, yogbuc ya pi, k…Ē yowur…õn…õ ya y…õl…õŇčk ya t…Ēk.
\v 32 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē p…ĒŇčk…Ēyi wara cam…ôt-tin w…ĒŇčk…Ēy…õf…õ d…ôt…ômboŇčk parac…Ē m…Ē, k…ôca o k…ôca wara maas.
\v 33 K…ôra o k…ôra ka p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp k…ôy…Ē yogbuc maas k…Ē y…õl…õŇčk ya yi. It…Ē p…ôŇčk…Ēyi wara cam…ôt-tin nw…õ w…ĒŇčk…Ēy…õf…õ d…ôt…ômboŇčk pa p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp m…Ē m…Ē.
\v 34 T…ômboŇčk pa p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp p…Ēy…Ē y…Ēn…Ēn…õ ya s…ôlamp maŇčk…ôl…õ ny…õ y…ĒŇčk…Ēwur…õn…õ y…õl…õŇčk ya t…Ēk yokom m…Ē, yogbuc, k…Ē y…õl…õŇčk ya yi.
\v 35 Wara waw…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč k…ômaas nw…õ w…õŇčy…õf…õ d…ôt…ômboŇčk parac…Ē m…Ē, d…ôk…ôy…õf…õ da wara m…õr…ôŇč o m…õr…ôŇč m…õn…õ pogbuc pin peyi wi tant…Ēf.
\v 36 Pas…õl…ôr…õn…õ yogbuc k…Ē wara, pat…õmp…õ f…ôp fa yi anc…ômb…ôl Ňčin Ňča k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs.
\v 37 M…ôlomp…ôs s…ôlamp cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč s…ôk…Ē p…ômar pac…ômb…ôr y…Ēn…Ēn…õ s…ôlamp k…ôroŇč m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôcweŇčki tekiriŇč m…Ē.
\v 38 MacaŇčk k…Ē map m…õkay…õ meken s…Ē f…ôp fa mi p…ômar m…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs.
\v 39 P…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp, p…õc…ômb…ôr…õ pa pi k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr yay…Ēk…Ē, k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs kilo w…ôco maas (30) k…Ē p…ômar palomps…õ yi.
\v 40 M…ôna Musa m…ôgb…ôtn…õ belbel, m…ôsur…õn…õ y…õb…ôc ny…õ m…ôm…Ēm…ôn nn…Ē t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ
\c 26
\s1 AŇčgbip Ňčosoku
\p 
\v 1 ¬ęMusa m…ôlomps…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku c…ôpol w…ôco ca k…ôloto ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, ka alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňča bulu k'alom Ňčeyim. S…ôbeŇča sas…Ēk…Ē s…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēdun…õ ci k…ôroŇč lulu ya m…õl…õk…õ kerub. Y…õb…ôc ya w…ôc…õr…ôŇč yendeyi yay…Ēk…Ē.
\v 2 Dobolu da c…ôpol cac…Ēk…Ē f…ôp d…Ēk…Ē d…Ēy…Ē nk…õ o nk…õ cururu w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē cam…ôt-maas (28), k…Ē dowokulu da k…ôpol nk…õ o nk…õ d…Ēk…Ē d…Ēy…Ē cururu maŇčk…ôl…õ, c…ôpol f…ôp c…ôde c…ôt…ôŇčn…õn…õ potubuc.
\v 3 M…ôdek…Ē m…ôgb…õtl…õn…õ-gb…õtl…õn…õ c…ôpol k…ôcam…ôt d…õw…õnca, m…ôy…Ē s…Ē tin tayi c…ôk…Ē k…ôcam…ôt.
\v 4 M…ôwes-wes…õ dobol da k…ôloto k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…ôk…ôs…ôk s…ôbeŇča s'alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, m…ôde m…ônut yi, m…ôy…Ē s…Ē tin tayi k…ôpol ka k…ôloto ka m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 5 Dobol da c…ôloto cac…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč m…ôwes-wes…õ di s…ôbeŇča w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50), m…ônut yi, m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ yewes-wesi ya c…ôloto cac…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč f…ôp yosur…õn…õ d…õw…õnca.
\v 6 M…ôde m…ôlomp…ôs Ňčkora w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) ya k…õma ny…õ m…ôndek…Ēc…õp…ôr…õn…õ c…ôloto cac…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē, nt…õ tendes…ĒŇč…õ c…ôloto ca d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôdey…Ēn…õ kin m…Ē.
\p 
\v 7 M…ôdun…õ c…ôpol ca k…ôloto ka m…õr…ôŇč k…ôtel…ôr nk…õ w…ôco k…Ē pin c…ôfon ca wir, nc…õ andek…Ēperi d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôroŇč m…Ē.
\v 8 Dobolu da k…ôpol nk…õ o nk…õ dede d…Ēy…Ē cururu w…ôco maas (30), k…Ē dowokulu dede d…Ēy…Ē cururu maŇčk…ôl…õ. C…ôpol nc…õ w…ôco k…Ē pin (11) f…ôp c…ôde c…ôy…Ē potubuc pin payi.
\v 9 M…ôgb…õtl…õn…õ taciŇča c…ôpol k…ôcam…ôt, k…Ē c…ôpol c…ôk…Ē cam…ôt-tin s…Ē taciŇča. K…ôpol ka cam…ôt-tin, p…ômar ki k…ôy…õl…õ tekiriŇč ta aŇčgbancan.
\v 10 M…ôde m…ôlomp…ôs yewes-wesi w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) k…ôpol k…ôk…ôs…ôk ka y…õgb…õtl…õn…õ y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, m…ônut yi. K…ôpol k…ôk…ôs…ôk ka y…õgb…õtl…õn…õ ya m…õr…ôŇč s…Ē, m…ôlomp…ôs k…ôs…ôk kayi yewes-wesi w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50), m…ônut s…Ē yay…Ēk…Ē.
\v 11 M…ôlomp…ôs Ňčkora w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) ya k…Ēp…ôr ny…õ m…ôndegb…õk…ôr deyewes-wesi m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ aŇčgbancan Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňčin m…Ē.
\v 12 Dac…Ē da c…ôpol ca c…ôloto dendecern…õ, paŇč…õr…õ di d…ôkiyi dosoku tadar…ôŇč.
\v 13 Dobolu da c…ôpol ca c…ôloto decern…õ, p…ômar payer di dac…Ē k…ôs…ôk o k…ôs…ôk nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ paŇč…õr d…ôkiyi dosoku belbel m…Ē.
\v 14 M…ôlomps…õ pokump…õ pa aŇčgbancan kata ya Ňčkesiya y…Ēk…Ē aŇčgb…ôt kar…õ k…ôyim m…Ē, m…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôlomps…õ kata ya ntempeli pokump…õ pa m…õr…ôŇč.
\p 
\v 15 M…ôlomps…õ f…ôr…õm fa d…ôkiyi dosoku t…Ēk ya kasiya, nf…õ andek…Ēc…ômb…ôr m…Ē.
\v 16 P…ômar f…ôr…õm o f…ôr…õm f…ôb…Ēl cururu w…ôco k…Ē dowokulu da fi d…Ēy…Ē kururu katin k…Ē dac…Ē.
\v 17 F…ôr…õm o f…ôr…õm p…ômar f…ôy…Ē sek m…õr…ôŇč ny…õ yosol d…õw…õnca m…Ē, tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē p…ômar pay…Ē f…ôr…õm fa d…ôkiyi dosoku f…ôp.
\v 18 M…ôlomps…õ ntende k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka di nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē f…ôr…õm w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20).
\v 19 M…ôlomps…õ y…õc…ôm…õn…õ w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) ya gbeti ny…õ m…ôndek…Ēc…ômb…ôr tant…Ēf ta f…ôr…õm w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) m…Ē. Nf…õ o nf…õ f…ôy…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ m…õr…ôŇč, k…ôsur…õn…õ ka bi y…Ēk…Ē p…ômar pas…õt sek m…õr…ôŇč y…Ēk…Ē f…ôr…õm f…ôy…Ē m…Ē.
\v 20 K…ôca k…ômeriya ka d…ôkiyi dosoku nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, m…ôlomps…õ s…Ē d…ôndo f…ôr…õm w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20).
\v 21 Y…õc…ôm…õn…õ w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) ya gbeti, ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ m…õr…ôŇč yede yeyi f…ôr…õm fin tant…Ēf.
\v 22 M…ôde m…ôlomp…ôs f…ôr…õm cam…ôt-tin fa t…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ ta d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôca ka ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē.
\v 23 M…ôlomp…ôs f…ôr…õm m…õr…ôŇč taciŇča nf…õ f…ôŇčk…Ēyi d…ômoŇčkubut nde t…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ pa d…ôkiyi dosoku m…Ē.
\v 24 M…ôde m…ôy…Ē f…ôr…õm faf…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč f…ôgb…õp…õn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ tant…Ēf, m…ôkot…ôr…õn…õ fi tak…ôroŇč k…ôsora kin. Tin tayi t'andey…Ē f…ôr…õm, m…õr…ôŇč f…ôk…Ē feyi moŇčkubut mam…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē.
\v 25 It…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē f…ôr…õm cam…ôt-maas k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-tin (16) ya gbeti, f…ôr…õm o f…ôr…õm f…ôy…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ m…õr…ôŇč tant…Ēf.
\p 
\v 26 M…ôpat c…ôgbo ca k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya k…ôcam…ôt nc…õ andesump…ôr…õ f…ôr…õm f…ôp fa k…ôs…ôk kin ka d…ôkiyi dosoku m…Ē.
\v 27 C…ôgbo k…ôcam…ôt s…Ē ca f…ôr…õm fa k…ôs…ôk ka m…õr…ôŇč ka d…ôkiyi dosoku, k…Ē c…ôgbo k…ôcam…ôt s…Ē ca f…ôr…õm fa t…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ ta d…ôkiyi dosoku ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē.
\v 28 K…ôgbo k…ôrac…Ē k…ômar k…ôcep…ôr f…ôr…õm fa k…ôs…ôk kin f…ôp dac…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ f…ôr…õm f…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē haŇč k…ôb…ôp f…ôlp…ôs.
\v 29 M…ôde m…ôsop f…ôr…õm f…ôp k…õma, m…ôlomps…õ c…ôsora k…õma nc…õ andec…õp…ôr…õn…õ c…ôgbo cac…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, m…ôsop s…Ē ci k…õma.
\v 30 K…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē melip-…õ, m…ôna Musa m…ôyekti d…ôkiyi dosoku, m…ôc…ômb…ôr di dowur…õn…õ k…Ē dand…õ iment…ôr …ôm nn…Ē t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč m…Ē.
\p 
\v 31 M…ôlomps…õ k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, sa alom Ňča bulu, k…Ē sa alom Ňčeyim. Pawur…õ k…ôloto kaŇčk…Ē k…ôroŇč lulu ya m…õl…õk…õ kerub m…õr…ôŇč. Y…õb…ôc ya w…ôc…õr…ôŇč k…ôdu yendeyi yay…Ēk…Ē.
\v 32 M…ôde m…ôd…õt ki d…ômogbu maŇčk…ôl…õ ma k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya mm…õ asop k…õma k…Ē m…Ēy…Ē Ňčkora ya k…õma m…Ē, m…ôc…ômb…ôr mi d…ôy…õc…ôm…õn…õ maŇčk…ôl…õ k…ôroŇč ya gbeti.
\v 33 N…ôd…õt…ôr k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ Ňčkora tant…Ēf. K…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ kaŇčk…Ē tadar…ôŇč k'aŇčk…Ēc…ômb…ôr kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôy…Ē walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa dem k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē. N…ôd…õt k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ kaŇčk…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôyer aŇčgbip Ňčosoku k…Ē t…Ēks…Ē tosoku m…Ē.
\v 34 K…Ē m…ôlip-…õ, m…ôgb…ôp…ôr oŇč af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa dem k'aka Yisrayel nde d…ôt…Ēks…Ē tosoku.
\v 35 M…ôc…ômb…ôr am…õsa k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ todoru, aŇčgbip disr…õ ntende k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…Ē p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp pi p…õt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē am…õsa ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.
\p 
\v 36 M…ôde m…ôdun…õ kusuŇčka k'aŇčgbancan c…ôloto c…ôŇč…õr…õ ca s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, pan…ĒŇčk…ôs…ôl s…ôbeŇča sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, sa alom Ňča bulu k…Ē sa alom Ňčeyim.
\v 37 M…ôde m…ôpat…õ k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ mogbu k…ôcam…ôt ma k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya, m…ôsop mi k…õma, m…ôgb…õk…ôr Ňčkora ya k…õma mogbu mam…Ēk…Ē. M…ôs…õl…õ y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mogbu k…ôcam…ôt yay…Ēk…Ē k…Ēp…ôr.¬Ľ
\c 27
\s1 Tetek toloŇčn…õ
\p 
\v 1 ¬ęM…ôlomps…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya, dobolu da pi d…Ēy…Ē cururu k…ôcam…ôt, k…Ē dowokulu da pi s…Ē cururu k…ôcam…ôt. Tetek p…õt…ôŇčn…õn…õ c…ôs…ôk f…ôp, mba deŇčeci da pi d…Ēy…Ē cururu maas.
\v 2 M…ôlomp…ôs l…õn ya tetek nde moŇčkubut mam…Ēk…Ē mak…ôroŇč maŇčk…ôl…õ. M…ôde m…ôs…õl…ôr…õn…õ l…õn yay…Ēk…Ē k…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ y…Ēy…Ēn…õ paka pin m…Ē, m…ôsop pi k…Ēp…ôr.
\v 3 M…ôlomps…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ dap d…õb…õr…õ k…ôbof, pel, mapan, bak yosort…õ s…õm k…Ē map m…õkay…õ meken. M…ôlomps…õ yosump…ôr-sump…ôr yay…õ f…ôp k…Ēp…ôr.
\v 4 M…ôlomps…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ manta ma k…Ēp…ôr, m…ôb…õr mi c…ôsora maŇčk…ôl…õ ca k…Ēp…ôr d…ômoŇčkubut. M…ôc…ômb…ôr mi k…ôb…ôr ka tetek toloŇčn…õ tant…Ēf, deŇčeci da manta mam…Ēk…Ē m…õcb…ôp dac…Ē da tetek.
\v 5 Pac…ômb…ôr manta mam…Ēk…Ē k…ôb…ôr ka tetek toloŇčn…õ tant…Ēf, deŇčeci da manta mam…Ēk…Ē m…õcb…ôp deŇčeci dac…Ē da tetek.
\v 6 M…ôpat…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ c…ôgbo k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya, m…ôsop ci k…Ēp…ôr.
\v 7 Pasor c…ôgbo cac…Ēk…Ē d…ôc…ôsora cac…Ēk…Ē c…ôyi c…ôs…ôk ca tetek pap…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pactam k…ôkek…ôr…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ pap…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.
\v 8 Tetek toloŇčn…õ pap…Ēk…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēlomps…õ c…ôbam m…Ē, pede p…Ēy…Ē fos disr…õ. Ňäay…Ē pi p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē anament…ôr …ôm nn…Ē t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôlomp…ôs k'abaŇčka
\p 
\v 9 ¬ęM…ôlomp…ôs abaŇčka Ňča d…ôkiyi dosoku. Ntende k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, p…ômar dobolu da saŇčka d…Ēy…Ē cururu tasar tin (100), m…ôd…õt di c…ôloto ca s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler.
\v 10 Mogbu w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč ma k…ôp…ôr (20) k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi ya k…Ēp…ôr w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20), Ňčkora ya mogbu k…Ē gbat-gbata ya mi p…ômar y…Ēy…Ēn…õ ya gbeti.
\v 11 K…ôca k…ômeriya ka ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, p…ômar ki k…ôy…Ē s…Ē c…ôloto p…ôm…Ē k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē dobolu da ki d…Ēy…Ē cururu tasar tin (100), k…ôca kaŇčk…Ē k…ôy…Ē mogbu w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) ya k…Ēp…ôr. Ňäkora ya mogbu k…Ē gbat-gbata ya mi f…ôp, p…ômar palomps…õ yi gbeti.
\v 12 Dowokulu d'abaŇčka k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, c…ôloto ca saŇčka sa Ňči c…ôb…Ēl cururu w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50), mogbu ma ci w…ôco k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi w…ôco.
\p 
\v 13 Dowokulu d'abaŇčka k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, p…ômar d…Ēb…Ēl cururu w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50).
\v 14 P…ômar c…ôloto ca k…ôs…ôk kin c…ôde c…ôy…Ē dobolu da cururu w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (15), mogbu maas k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi maas.
\v 15 Pad…õt s…Ē c…ôloto cururu w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (15) c…ôl…Ēma k…ôca ka m…õr…ôŇč, mogbu maas k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi maas.
\v 16 P…ômar paŇč…õr…õ kusuŇčka ka saŇčka c…ôloto ca s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler ca cururu w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20), y…õb…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē yede y…Ēy…Ēn…õ ya w…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôdu p…ôlomps…õ ci s…ôbeŇča sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, sa alom Ňča bulu, sa alom Ňčeyim, p…ôc…ômb…ôr…õ c…ôloto c…ôŇč…õr…õ caŇčk…Ē mogbu maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi maŇčk…ôl…õ.
\v 17 Mogbu mm…õ andec…ômb…ôr…õ saŇčka m…Ē f…ôp gbat-gbata ya mi y…Ēy…Ēn…õ gbeti. Ňäkora s…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ ya gbeti, k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi y…Ēy…Ēn…õ ya k…Ēp…ôr.
\v 18 SaŇčka sas…Ēk…Ē s…ôb…Ēl cururu tasar tin (100), k…Ē dowokulu da si cururu w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50), k…Ē deŇčeci da si cururu k…ôcam…ôt. P…ômar c…ôloto cac…Ēk…Ē f…ôp c…ôy…Ēn…õ ca s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya k…Ēp…ôr.
\v 19 K…ôy…õf…õ ka yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya y…õb…ôc ya d…ôndo d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôb…ôp ka c…ôgbo c…ôd…Ēf ca saŇčka f…ôp, p…ômar palomps…õ yi f…ôp k…Ēp…ôr.¬Ľ
\s1 Moro ma s…ôlamp
\p 
\v 20 ¬ęK…Ē m…ôna Musa, m…ôsom aka Yisrayel Ňčak…õr'am moro m…Ēt…Ēt ma olif m…Ēf…Ēc, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôlamp s…ôctam k…ômar d…Ēf…Ēy o d…Ēf…Ēy m…Ē.
\v 21 Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun Ňčandek…Ēc…ômb…ôr p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu nde todoru ta k…ôloto k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôk…ôŇčk kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa dem k'aka Yisrayel m…Ē. P…ômar s…ôlamp s…ôdek…Ē s…ôcmar MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč k…ôy…õf…õ d…Ēf…Ēy haŇč b…ôtb…ôt. Sariy…õ sa t…õm o t…õm s…Ē, p…ômar aka Yisrayel Ňčade Ňčaclel…ôs si d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp.¬Ľ
\c 28
\s1 Yamos ya w…ôloŇčn…õ
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õn…õ aYisrayel dac…Ē nn…Ē m…ôyi m…Ē w…õnc …ôm Aruna, k'awut …Ēn arkun Nadab, Abihu, Elasar k…Ē Itamar. M…ôgb…õy Ňča k…Ē aka Yisrayel alp…ôs aŇč…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčay…Ēn'em aloŇčn…õ m…Ē.
\v 2 M…ôlomps…õ w…õnc …ôm Aruna yamos ya d…ôKanu, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ yede yecment…ôr d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ k…Ē delel d…Ēn m…Ē.
\v 3 M…ôlok-lok…ôr ac…õr…ôŇč f…ôp, ak…Ē ilas kifir ka d…õc…õr…ôŇč m…Ē: Ňäa Ňčandelomps…õ Aruna yamos, ny…õ endeb…õrn…õ k'ande pacs…Ēk…ôs k…Ē-…õ, a padey…Ēn…õ oŇč w…ôloŇčn…õ kem.
\v 4 Yamos ny…õ y…Ē p…ômar Ňčalomp…ôs: Yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc, duma da ef…Ēd, burumus, duma dedisr…õ, k…ôfak…ôl, k…Ē tabataba. Ňäalomps…õ w…õnc …ôm Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn yamos ya d…ôKanu nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčade Ňčacb…ôc em y…õb…ôc ya k…ôloŇčn…õ m…Ē.
\v 5 Ac…ôr…õ k…ôdu Ňčal…õk k…õma, k…ôloto ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, Ňča bulu, k…Ē Ňčeyim.¬Ľ
\s1 Ef…Ēd Ňča w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč
\p 
\v 6 ¬ęAc…õr…ôŇč Ňčadun…õ duma da ef…Ēd k…ôloto ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňča bulu k…Ē Ňčeyim k…Ē s…ôbeŇča sa k…õma.
\v 7 Palomp…ôs yeyes…õ banca m…õr…ôŇč, pas…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ yi c…ôs…ôk ca banca ya duma da ef…Ēd.
\v 8 Pas…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ s…Ē tabataba y…Ēy…Ēn…õ paka pin k…Ē duma da ef…Ēd. Tolomp…ôs ta yi towur…õn…õ: K…ôloto ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, s…ôbeŇča sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, sa alom Ňča bulu, k…Ē alom Ňčeyim k…Ē s…ôbeŇča sa k…õma.
\v 9 M…ôl…õk s…Ē walak…õ wa masar m…Ēt…Ēt ma onik…ôs m…õr…ôŇč nw…õ m…ôndecic mewe ma awut a Yakuba m…Ē.
\v 10 Pacic mewe cam…ôt-tin tasar t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…ôroŇč, k…Ē mewe m…õlp…ôs m…Ēk…Ē cam…ôt-tin s…Ē tasar ta m…õr…ôŇč t…Ēk…Ē k…ôroŇč, t…Ēk…Ē Ňčamb…õk…õn…õ m…Ē.
\v 11 Masar m…õpat mam…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč m…Ēy…Ēn…õ y…õb…ôc y…Ēt…Ēt, w…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôpat p…ôpat…ôs tamp ta masar p…ôcic…ôs mi k…ôroŇč mewe ma awut a Yisrayel, p…ôb…õr mi f…ôr…õm fa k…õma.
\v 12 M…ôde m…ôs…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ masar mam…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč yeyes…õ banca ya duma da ef…Ēd k…ôroŇč, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ t…õc…õmc…õm…ôs ta awut a Yisrayel (Yakuba). Ti disr…õ Aruna ende p…ôcd…õt…ôrn…õ mewe mam…Ēk…Ē d…ôbanca f…Ēr ya ina MARIKI kiriŇč nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ icc…õm-c…õmn…õ nu t…õm f…ôp m…Ē.
\v 13 M…ôlomps…õ f…ôr…õm faf…Ēk…Ē k…õma,
\v 14 m…ôdu megbekce m…õr…ôŇč p…ôm…Ē k…ôb…ônda yay…Ēk…Ē s…Ē k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs, ny…õ andek…Ēd…õt…ôr f…ôr…õm faf…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Yuba ya kiti ny…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč …õŇčgb…õkn…õ m…Ē
\p 
\v 15 ¬ęM…ôlomp…ôs yuba ya kiti y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc, pas…Ēt…õ yi k…ôloto ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, s…ôbeŇča sa k…õma, s…ôbeŇča sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňča bulu, alom Ňčeyim p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē alomp…ôs duma da ef…Ēd m…Ē. Y…õb…ôc ya w…ôc…õr…ôŇč yendeyi yay…Ēk…Ē.
\v 16 Panut ki k…ôm…õr…ôŇč, k…ôs…ôk o k…ôs…ôk k…ôy…Ē dobolu da k…ôca disr…õ katin.
\v 17 P…ômar m…ôc…õk k…ôloto kaŇčk…Ē k…ôroŇč masar momot…ôr-mot…ôr c…ôgba maŇčk…ôl…õ: K…ôgba k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…ôy…Ē tasar teyim, tasar p'alom Ňča c…ôbe, k…Ē tasar pa alom Ňča bulu Ňč…Ēn…ĒŇčks…ôl p…ôbuk.
\v 18 K…ôgba ka m…õr…ôŇč k…ôy…Ē masar momot…ôr-mot…ôr mm…õ: Tasar teyim ceŇč, tasar t'alom Ňča bulu k…Ē diyamaŇč.
\v 19 K…ôgba ka maas k…ôy…Ē masar mm…õ: Tasar pa alom Ňča alemb…ôra, tasar pa lom y…õla c…ôgb…õr k…Ē tasar ta alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc.
\v 20 K…ôgba ka maŇčk…ôl…õ k…ôy…Ē masar mm…õ: Tasar ta alom Ňčobuk m…õl, tasar ta lom y…õc…õmc…õm…ôr k…Ē tasar ta alom Ňčobuk. Tasar o tasar m…ôde m…ôs…õt…ôr pi d…ôf…ôr…õm fa k…õma.
\v 21 Pacic mewe ma awut a Yisrayel (Yakuba) masar mam…Ēk…Ē w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (12) k…ôroŇč p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ancic tamp m…Ē. Tasar o tasar tende k…ôcment…ôr tewe ta kusuŇčka kin nc…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (12) dac…Ē ca Yisrayel.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 22 ¬ęM…ôde m…ôlomps…õ yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc megbekce ma k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs.
\v 23 M…ôlomp…ôs curund…õ m…õr…ôŇč nc…õ m…ôŇčk…Ēb…õr moŇčkubut m…õr…ôŇč mak…ôroŇč ma yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc m…Ē.
\v 24 M…ôgb…õk…ôr megbekce mam…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč ma k…õma curund…õ c…ôk…Ē c…ôyi d…ômoŇčkubut ma yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.
\v 25 M…ôde m…ôgb…õk…ôr s…Ē c…ôs…ôk c…ôlp…ôs ca megbekce mam…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč d…ôf…ôr…õm m…õr…ôŇč nf…õ f…ôyi yeyes…õ banca ya duma da ef…Ēd m…Ē tekiriŇč.
\v 26 M…ôlomp…ôs s…Ē curund…õ m…õr…ôŇč ca k…õma nc…õ andek…Ēb…õr moŇčkubut mant…Ēf ma yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc, k…ôs…ôk kaŇčk…Ē k…ôndek…Ē k…ôcgbuŇč…õn…õ duma da ef…Ēd m…Ē.
\v 27 M…ôlomp…ôs s…Ē curund…õ m…õr…ôŇč c…ôl…Ēma ca k…õma nc…õ andek…Ēb…õr yeyes…õ banca ya duma da ef…Ēd tant…Ēf m…Ē tekiriŇč, d…ôk…ôs…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ da yi p…ôsur…õn…õ k…Ē tak…ôroŇč ta tabataba ta duma da ef…Ēd.
\v 28 K…ôb…ônda ka alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc k…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēkot…ôr…õn…õ curund…õ ca yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc k…Ē ca duma da ef…Ēd, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ yuba yedeŇčs…õ tak…ôroŇč ta tabataba pa duma da ef…Ēd, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ s…Ē yuba k…ôt…Ētam k…ôsak…õn…õ k…Ē duma da ef…Ēd m…Ē.
\v 29 Ti tendes…ĒŇč…õ Aruna k…ôb…õr…õ nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku p…ôgb…õkn…õ yuba ya kiti d…õb…ôk…ôc, ny…õ y…Ēy…Ē mewe ma cusuŇčka ca Yisrayel f…ôp m…Ē. Ti t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ina MARIKI k…ôcc…õm-c…õmn…õ nu t…õm f…ôp.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 30 ¬ęM…ôna Musa, m…ôdek…Ē m…ôb…õr nde yuba ya kiti disr…õ masar ma kiti m…õr…ôŇč ‚ÄĻ\it Yurim\it*‚Äļ k…Ē ‚ÄĻ\it Tumim\it*,‚Äļ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ meyi Aruna d…õb…ôk…ôc k'endeb…õr…õ nde MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč-…õ. Ti disr…õ Aruna ende k…ôcgb…õkn…õ yi t…õm o t…õm k'endeb…õr…õ nde MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčac…ôr…õ kiti kem m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Yamos ya aloŇčn…õ y…Ēl…Ēma
\p 
\v 31 ¬ęM…ôde m…ôlomps…õ burumus ba ef…Ēd s…ôbeŇča sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc f…ôp.
\v 32 Dede d…Ēy…Ē d…ôk…ôm…ôl domp nde dac…Ē da burumus bab…Ēk…Ē, p…ômar pagb…õnt bi haŇč pan…ĒŇčk…ôr, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ andu yamos ya akata, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta b…õwal…õ m…Ē. Y…õb…ôc ya w…ôc…õr…ôŇč k…ôdu yendeyi.
\v 33 M…ôdu burumus bab…Ēk…Ē tant…Ēf c…ôpare ca alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňča bulu k'alom Ňčeyim. M…ôb…õrs…ôr-b…õrs…ôr haŇč m…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr meŇčgbeŇčk…ôle ma k…õma lulu ya c…ôpare dac…Ē.
\v 34 TeŇčgbeŇčk…ôle pa k…õma pin k…ôpare kin, teŇčgbeŇčk…ôle pa k…õma pin k…ôpare kin y'aŇčk…Ēb…õrs…ôr…õn…õ burumus tant…Ēf haŇč pan…ĒŇčk…ôr.
\v 35 Duma dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ē Aruna ende k…ôcb…õrn…õ k'endek…Ēb…ôc'em y…õb…ôc ya w…ôloŇčn…õ-…õ. Dim da ŇčgbeŇčk…ôle dad…Ēk…Ē d'ande k…ôcne k'endeb…õr…õ nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč k…Ē k'ende k…ôcwur di-…õ, ti t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôt…Ēfi.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 36 ¬ęM…ôlomp…ôs ab…Ēp…ôr Ňča k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs nŇč…õ andecic ‚ÄĻDosoku da MARIKI‚Äļ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ancic tamp m…Ē.
\v 37 M…ôkot…ôr…õn…õ ab…Ēp…ôr ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē k…ôfak…ôl tekiriŇč k…ôb…ônda ka alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc.
\v 38 Ab…Ēp…ôr ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē aŇčkot…ôr Aruna d…ôtobu m…Ē Ňčendes…Ēk…ôs yoloŇčn…õ ya aka Yisrayel f…ôp, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ina MARIKI ide icbaŇč k…ôpoc…õ k…ôŇčan, ali Ňčacciya-ciya k…ôck…õr'em yopoc…õ yay…Ēk…Ē.
\v 39 Duma dedisr…õ k…Ē k…ôfak…ôl y…Ē m…ôndelomps…õ k…ôloto ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler. M…ôlomps…õ k…Ē s…Ē tabataba, y…õb…ôc ya w…ôc…õr…ôŇč k…ôdu yendeyi.¬Ľ
\s1 Yamos ya aloŇčn…õ al…Ēma
\p 
\v 40 ¬ęNt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta awut arkun a Aruna m…Ē, suma s…ôdisr…õ s'andes…Ēt…õ Ňča, mabamaba k…Ē c…ôfak…ôl ny…õ Ňčande Ňčacment…ôr…õ d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ k…Ē delel daŇčan m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 41 ¬ęK…Ē m…ôna Musa, m…ôn'endeb…õr w…õnc …ôm Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn yamos yay…Ēk…Ē, m…ôb…Ēy Ňča moro d…ôs…ôbomp m…ôdeŇč…ôr Ňča p…õsar…õ paŇčan. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē m…ôndek…Ē c…ômb…ôr Ňča dekiriŇč, Ňčay…Ēn…õ afum asoku, Ňčacb…ôc em oŇč y…õb…ôc ya aloŇčn…õ.
\v 42 M…ôlomps…õ Ňča c…Ēgba ca k…ôloto ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčawur k…ôs…Ēk…ôr m…Ē, c…Ēgba cac…Ēk…Ē c…ôcy…õf…õ Ňča d…ôfi haŇč nde d…ôl…ôŇčk.
\v 43 C…Ēgba cac…Ēk…Ē c…Ē Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun Ňčande Ňčacb…õrn…õ k…Ē Ňčande k…ôcb…õr…õ nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, k…Ē Ňčade k…ôcl…Ēt…ôrn…õ nde tetek toloŇčn…õ-…õ. Ti disr…õ Ňčaf…Ēdesar…õ kiciya nk…õ k…ôndedif Ňča m…Ē. Sariy…õ sa t…õm o t…õm s…Ē nn…Ē Aruna k…Ē yuruya y…Ēn Ňčayi m…Ē.¬Ľ
\c 29
\s1 K…ôd…ôs ka aloŇčn…õ
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē p…ômar m…ôna Musa m…ôk…Ē m…ôd…ôs Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn k…ôy…Ēn…õ afum asoku, Ňčacb…ôc'em Ňčay…Ēn'em aloŇčn…õ: M…ôl…õk tura k…Ē Ňčkesiya yorkun ny…õ m…õr…ôŇč y…Ēt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp,
\v 2 c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin, c…ôcom c…ôlok-lok c…ôt…Ēy…Ē lebin pap…Ēck…õ ci moro, k…Ē biskit b…Ēt…Ēy…Ē lebin pasop bi moro, m…ôlomps…õ c…ôcom cac…Ēk…Ē f…ôp k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt ka b…ôle.
\v 3 M…ôb…õr ci d…ôk…ôfala m…ôkek…ôr…õ k…ôfala kaŇčk…Ē, tura k…Ē Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč.
\p 
\v 4 M…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õn…õ Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun nde kusuŇčka ka aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu tekiriŇč, m…ôbikn…õn…õ Ňča domun.
\v 5 M…ôde m…ôl…õk yamos, m…ôb…õr Aruna yamos: Duma dedisr…õ, burumus ba duma da ef…Ēd, duma da ef…Ēd, k…Ē yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ ny…õ m…ôndek…Ēkot…ôr…õn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc k…Ē tabataba pa duma da ef…Ēd m…Ē.
\v 6 M…ôc…ôp k…Ē k…ôfak…ôl, m…ôd…õt…ôr ki tekiriŇč t…Ēb…Ēp…ôr t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ta d…ôKanu.
\v 7 M…ôl…õk moro m…Ēb…Ēy mopus…õ, m…ôloŇč…ôr k…Ē mi d…ôromp, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôd…ôs k…Ē dekiriŇč da y…õb…ôc yem ya k…ôloŇčn…õ.
\v 8 K…Ē telip-…õ, m…ôwe s…Ē awut arkun a Aruna Ňčac…ĒŇčn…õ, Ňča s…Ē m…ôb…õr Ňča suma s…ôdisr…õ saŇčan.
\v 9 K…Ē m…ôlip-…õ, m…ôgb…ônc…ôs Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun mabamaba maŇčan, m…ôc…ôp…ôs Ňča c…ôfak…ôl. Ti disr…õ m…ôd…ôs Ňča y…õb…ôc yem ya d…ôKanu t…Ēy…Ēn…õ oŇč sariy…õ sa kor k…ôŇčan doru o doru.
\p 
\v 10 M…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õn…õ tura pap…Ēk…Ē nde daŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu. Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun ŇčadeŇč…ôr pi waca d…ôromp.
\v 11 M…ôsu t…Ēb…Ēl m…ôfay wana waw…Ēk…Ē MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč ntende kusuŇčka ka aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu. Mecir ma wi m…õb…õr…õ d…ôt…Ēb…Ēl.
\v 12 M…ôgb…ôt t…õl…ôr d…ômecir ma tura pap…Ēk…Ē m…ôsop…ôt mi l…õn maŇčk…ôl…õ ya moŇčkubut ma tetek toloŇčn…õ, m…ôloŇč mecir m…õlp…ôs nde p…õc…ôm…õn…õ pa tetek tat…Ēk…Ē.
\v 13 M…ôl…õk moro m…Ēk…Ē moŇčkump yedisr…õ ya p…Ēc…Ēl pap…Ēk…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, p…ôwotwot…ôr pa mim, fi ny…õ m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē moro ma yi, m…ôk…Ē m…ôc…Ēf'em yi f…ôp nde tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč.
\v 14 M…ôc…Ēf s…õm, yedisr…õ ya aputuk k…Ē akata Ňča tura yay…Ēk…Ē d…ôn…õnc saŇčka todoru. K…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ē nk…õ k…ôŇčs…ĒŇč…õ paŇčaŇčn…õn…õ aloŇčn…õ kiciya k…ôŇčan m…Ē.
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē telip-…õ, n…ôk…õr…õ aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun ŇčadeŇč…ôr Ňči waca d…ôromp.
\v 16 M…ôsu t…Ēb…Ēl m…ôfay aŇčkesiya ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, m…ôl…õk mecir mam…Ēk…Ē m…ôw…õs…ôs…ôr c…ôs…ôk ca tetek toloŇčn…õ f…ôp haŇč m…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr.
\v 17 M…ôc…õn…ôs aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē f…ôk…ôl f…ôk…ôl, m…ôyak yedisr…õ ya Ňči k…Ē w…õc…ôk, m…ôk…Ē m…ôboc yi f…ôk…ôl ya s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē k…Ē domp k…ôroŇč.
\v 18 M…ôc…Ēf…õ MARIKI aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun f…ôp tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč. P…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēc…Ēf p…Ē, mp…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, amb…Ēnc Ňča pi Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ MARIKI ab…ôk…ôc.
\p 
\v 19 K'alip-…õ, m…ôk…õr…õ s…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňča m…õr…ôŇč Ňč…Ēk…Ē. Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun ŇčadeŇč…ôr s…Ē ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē waca d…ôromp.
\v 20 M…ôsu t…Ēb…Ēl m…ôfay aŇčkesiya ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē. M…ôl…õk mecir ma Ňči m…ôsop mi Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn l…ôŇč…ôs ya waca w…Ēt…Ēt, k…Ē t…õl…ôr t…Ēp…ĒŇč mp…õ o mp…õ pa waca waŇčan w…Ēt…Ēt, k…Ē t…õl…ôr t…Ēp…ĒŇč mp…õ o mp…õ pa w…õc…ôk waŇčan w…Ēt…Ēt. M…ôl…õk mecir m…õlp…ôs, m…ôw…õs…ôs…ôr mi c…ôs…ôk ca tetek toloŇčn…õ f…ôp haŇč m…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr.
\v 21 M…ôl…õk s…Ē mecir m…Ēk…Ē meyi tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč m…Ē k…Ē moro m…Ēb…Ēy m…ôw…õs…ôs…ôr mi Aruna k…Ē yamos y…Ēn, m…ôy…Ē s…Ē tin tayi awut …Ēn k…Ē yamos yaŇčan. K…ôl…õk d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē, Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn Ňčay…Ēn…õ oŇč aloŇčn…õ apus em.
\p 
\v 22 M…ôl…õk moro ma aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun, k…ôleŇča, moro mm…õ moŇčkump yedisr…õ ya aŇčkesiya m…Ē, p…ôwotwot…ôr pa mim, k…Ē fi m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē moro mm…õ moŇčkump yi m…Ē k…Ē al…ôŇčk Ňča k…ôc…ôk k…ôt…Ēt. AŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňč…õd…ôs…õ Ňča dekiriŇč da k…ôloŇčn…õ Ňč…Ē.
\v 23 M…ôwur…õ c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēy…Ē lebin c…ôl…Ēma d…ôk…ôfala nk…õ anc…ômb…ôr MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē: K…ôcom k…ôlok-lok kin, k…ôcom nk…õ an…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ moro ma olif m…Ē, k…Ē biskit.
\v 24 M…ôb…õr yi f…ôp Aruna d…ôwaca k…Ē awut …Ēn, m…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč yi ina MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\v 25 K…Ē telip-…õ, m…ôbaŇč…ôr Ňča yi d…ôwaca, m…ôk…Ē m…ôc…Ēf…õ yi MARIKI nde d…ôtetek poloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč. Amb…Ēnc Ňča yi Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ MARIKI ab…ôk…ôc. K…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ē, nk…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē.
\v 26 M…ôl…õk k…ômp…ôcp…ôc ka aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča m…õr…ôŇč Ňč…õd…ôs…õ Ňča Aruna dekiriŇč da k…ôloŇčn…õ, m…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč ki MARIKI k…ôca kam p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē aŇčs…ĒŇč fum paka m…Ē, s…õm ya m…ôna y…Ē yay…Ēk…Ē.
\p 
\v 27 M…ôs…Ēk…ôs k…ômp…ôcp…ôc nk…õ m…ôndes…ĒŇč MARIKI p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē aŇčs…ĒŇč fum daka m…Ē. M…ôs…ĒŇč s…Ē al…ôŇčk Ňča aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun nŇč…õ anaf…õk teta k…ôd…ôs…õ Aruna k'awut …Ēn dekiriŇč da k…ôloŇčn…õ m…Ē.
\v 28 Yopoc m…õr…ôŇč yay…Ēk…Ē ya Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn y…Ē, tendey…Ēn…õ sariy…õ sa t…õm o t…õm aka Yisrayel dac…Ē. Bawo yopoc…õ ya k…ôf…õk yay…Ēk…Ē, yoloŇčn…õ ya k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu y…Ē, ny…õ y…Ēy…Ēn…õ ya MARIKI m…Ē. Mba Aruna k'awut …Ēn Ňčande Ňčacs…Ēt…ôr yi aka Yisrayel d…ôyoloŇčn…õ yaŇčan.
\p 
\v 29 K…Ē Aruna efi-…õ, yamos y…Ēn ya d…ôKanu yay…Ēk…Ē w…ôl…Ēma aŇčs…ĒŇč yi awut …Ēn dac…Ē, w…ôkak…Ē s…Ē p…ôb…õrn…õ yi d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ amb…Ēy moro k…ôd…ôs k…Ē dekiriŇč da y…õb…ôc ya d…ôKanu m…Ē.
\v 30 W…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôkin awut …Ēn dac…Ē nw…õ anded…ôs d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da Aruna m…Ē, …õmb…õrn…õ yamos yay…Ēk…Ē mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k'endeb…õr…õ aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu disr…õ k…ôk…Ēb…ôc'em nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku-…õ.
\p 
\v 31 M…ôl…õk aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňč…õd…ôs…õ dekiriŇč da k…ôloŇčn…õ m…Ē, m…ôp…õc s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē k…ôfo k…ôsoku k…ôl…Ēma saŇčka disr…õ.
\v 32 Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun Ňčas…Ēm s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē c…ôcom c…ôk…Ē c…ôyi d…ôk…ôfala m…Ē, nde kusuŇčka ka aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.
\v 33 Ňäa gb…ôc…ôr…ôm Ňč…Ē p…ômar k…ôs…Ēm ka s…õm ya k…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka kiciya yay…Ēk…Ē k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôd…ôs dekiriŇč da k…ôloŇčn…õ kem k…Ē k…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka yi. P…ômar f…õ fum w…ôcuru p…ôs…Ēm s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē, bawo yeri yosoku y…Ē.
\v 34 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a s…õm ya yoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, c…ôcom c…ôl…Ēma c…ônc…ôm…õ haŇč b…ôtb…ôt-…õ, m…ôgbal y…õlp…ôs y…Ēk…Ē d…ôn…õnc. P…ômar f…õ pas…Ēm yi, bawo yeri yopus y…Ē.
\p 
\v 35 M…ôy…Ē Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē isom …ôm ti m…Ē f…ôp. Mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē m…ônded…ôs Ňča dekiriŇč da k…ôloŇčn…õ.
\v 36 D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč mam…Ēk…Ē disr…õ p…ômar m…ôloŇčn…õ tura pin teta k…ôtubucn…õ ka k…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka kiciya. Ti t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ m…ôs…Ēk…ôs tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk ka pi. K…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, m…ôloŇč…ôr moro tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ m…ôpus…õ pi MARIKI m…Ē.
\v 37 Mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē m…ônde m…ôctubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs tetek toloŇčn…õ teta k…ôpus…õ ka pi MARIKI. It…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ p…ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ oŇč posoku p…õs mp…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, t…Ēcs…ĒŇč…õ paka o paka pogbuŇč…õn…õ pi, ampus…õ pi MARIKI. K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ fum p…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ pi-…õ, …ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ oŇč fum nw…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôloŇčn…õ f…ôp ka d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk
\p 
\v 38 ¬ęD…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk p…ômar m…ôde m…ôcloŇčn…õ oŇč tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč ya teren tin tin.
\v 39 AŇčkesiya Ňčin b…ôtb…ôt b…Ē m…ôŇčloŇčn…õ Ňči, aŇčkesiya Ňča m…õr…ôŇč d…Ēf…Ēy d…Ē m…ôŇčloŇčn…õ Ňči.
\v 40 AŇčkesiya Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē pac…Ēf…õ Ňči MARIKI k…Ē k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt kilo k…ômaas nk…õ amp…Ēck…õ moro m…Ēt…Ēt ma olif lit…õr din k…Ē dac…Ē m…Ē, m…ôloŇč…ôr ki w…õn lit…õr din k…Ē dac…Ē teta k…ôloŇčn…õ.
\v 41 K…Ē d…Ēf…Ēy d…õmb…ôp-…õ, m…ôk…õr'em s…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňča m…õr…ôŇč m…ôdeŇč…ôr Ňči k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn k…Ē ka w…õn p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ôk…õr'em b…ôtb…ôt m…Ē. YoloŇčn…õ y…Ē, ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, amb…Ēnc Ňča yi Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc.
\p 
\v 42 TekiriŇč oŇč, d…õt…õmp o d…õt…õmp dende k…ôcloŇčn'em k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôc…Ēf p…Ēc…Ēl nde kusuŇčka ka aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč. Dif…Ē indek…Ē icb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē n…ôna a iclok-lok…ôr …ôm di.
\v 43 Dif…Ē indek…Ē icb…ôp…õn…õ k'aka Yisrayel, n…Ēr…Ē da debeki dem dende docpus di.
\v 44 Ina MARIKI in'endes…Ēpus aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ, ipus s…Ē Aruna k…Ē yuruya y…Ēn nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčade Ňčay…Ēn…õ aloŇčn…õ em.
\v 45 Indend…õ aka Yisrayel dac…Ē, iy…Ēn…õ Kanu k…ôŇčan.
\v 46 Aka Yisrayel Ňčandec…ôr…õ a in'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI Kanu k…ôŇčan, ina nw…õ inawur…õn…õ Ňča at…Ēf Ňča Misira, idend…õ Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē. In'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI, Kanu k…ôŇčan.¬Ľ
\c 30
\s1 Tetek p…Ēc…Ēf…õ MARIKI suray
\p 
\v 1 M…ôde m…ôlomp…ôs tetek p…Ēc…Ēf…õ MARIKI suray. K…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya k…Ē m…ôndelomps…õ pi.
\v 2 Dobolu da tetek pap…Ēk…Ē d…Ēy…Ē kururu katin, k…Ē dowokulu da pi kururu katin, p…ôndet…ôŇčn…õn…õ c…ôs…ôk f…ôp. DeŇčeci da pi d…Ēy…Ē cururu m…õr…ôŇč, tetek pap…Ēk…Ē k…Ē l…õn ya pi y…õt…ôp…ôr…õn…õ y…Ēy…Ēn…õ paka pin.
\v 3 M…ôsop pi k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs, k…ôl…õk am…õsa Ňča pi k…ôroŇč k…ôb…ôp ka c…ôs…ôk ca pi k…ôk…Ē haŇč l…õn ya pi. M…ôlomp…ôs pi k…ôb…ôr ka k…õma c…ôs…ôk haŇč m…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr.
\v 4 M…ôlomp…ôs c…ôsora m…õr…ôŇč ca k…õma, m…ôb…õr ci k…ôb…ôr tant…Ēf ka c…ôs…ôk m…õr…ôŇč ca tetek pap…Ēk…Ē. C…ôsora cac…Ēk…Ē c…Ē andek…Ē pacsor c…ôgbo, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pactam k…ôs…õl…õŇč pi m…Ē.
\v 5 M…ôde m…ôpat c…ôgbo ca k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya, m…ôsop ci k…õma.
\v 6 M…ôk…Ē m…ôc…ômb…ôr tetek pap…Ēk…Ē tekiriŇč ta k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôy…Ē walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa dem k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē. Af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya nŇč…õ aŇčgb…ôp…ôr kaŇčk…ôra k…ôroŇč m…Ē, dif…Ē s…ôndek…Ē s…ôcb…ôp…õn…õ.
\v 7 B…ôtb…ôt o b…ôtb…ôt Aruna p…ôdek…Ē p…ôcc…Ēf'em di suray k'ende k…ôclomp…ôs s…ôlamp-…õ.
\v 8 Aruna p…ôdek…Ē p…ôcc…Ēf suray s…ôbotu amb…Ēnc sas…Ēk…Ē k'endek…Ē p…ôcmot s…ôlamp dec d…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy-…õ. P…ômar pade pacc…Ēf suray sas…Ēk…Ē d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp donu.
\v 9 Tetek t…Ē nt…õ p…ônt…Ēmar n…ôde n…ôcc…Ēf…õ di MARIKI suray s…ôcuru m…Ē, p…ômar f…õ n…ôcloŇčn…õ di y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēc…Ēf, ta n…ôcloŇčn…õ di s…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn, af…Ēde pacloŇč…ôr di w…õn wa k…ôloŇčn…õ.
\v 10 Katin gboŇč teren disr…õ t…Ē Aruna ende p…ôctubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs kiciya l…õn ya tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč. D…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp ende p…ôctubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēks…õ tetek mecir ma p…Ēc…Ēl pa k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya katin teren o teren. Tetek tosoku p…õs p…Ē p…Ēy…Ēn…õ oŇč, mp…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē.
\s1 Dut da aŇčgbancan Ňčosoku
\p 
\v 11 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 12 K…Ē m…ôndek…Ēlip k…ôl…Ēm aka Yisrayel f…ôp-…õ, nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôf…õk…õ MARIKI gbeti k…ôway ka k…ôyi k…Ēn doru, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta docu nd…õ o nd…õ dosump…ôr Ňča t…õm ta k…ôl…Ēm m…Ē.
\v 13 Afum aŇč…õ andek…Ēl…Ēm m…Ē f…ôp, nt…õ t…Ē Ňčandek…Ēf…õk: Gbeti gb…ôleŇč k…ôram k…ôcam…ôt p…ôm…Ē potubuc pa nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku mp…õ p…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôram w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) m…Ē. Ina MARIKI andef…õk…õ gbeti bab…Ēk…Ē.
\v 14 Nw…õ o nw…õ andek…Ēl…Ēm nw…õ …Ēs…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) m…Ē, haŇč k…ôp…õ tak…ôroŇč f…ôp faŇčan Ňčaf…õk…õ MARIKI.
\v 15 W…ôka daka …Ēf…Ēla w…ôt…Ēy…Ē daka k…ôf…õk kaŇčk…Ē, f…ôp faŇčan Ňčandet…ôŇčn…õn…õ k…ôf…õk nw…õ o nw…õ endef…õk…õ MARIKI gb…õti gb…ôleŇč k…ôcam…ôt, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčawurusn…õ k…ôyi k…ôŇčan doru m…Ē.
\v 16 K…Ē m…ôlip k…ôbaŇč…ôs k…ôf…õk kaŇčk…Ē-…õ, m…ôde m…ôclomps…õ gbeti bab…Ēk…Ē mes ma aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu. Ti tende k…ôcs…ĒŇč…õ MARIKI k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ aka Yisrayel p…ôcyac Ňča teta k…ôwurus k…ôyi k…ôŇčan doru.
\s1 K…ôsamp k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õn…õ
\p 
\v 17 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 18 M…ôs…õl k…ôsamp ka k…Ēp…ôr, k…Ē p…õc…ôm…õn…õ pa ki s…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ k…Ēp…ôr, m…ôb…õr k…ôsamp kaŇčk…Ē domun nd…õ aloŇčn…õ Ňčande Ňčacs…Ēk…ôsn…õn…õ m…Ē, m…ôk…Ē m…ôc…ômb…ôr k…ôsamp kaŇčk…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ k…Ē aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ dac…Ē.
\v 19 K…ôsamp kaŇčk…Ē k…Ē Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun Ňčande Ňčack…õt domun nd…õ Ňčande Ňčacbikn…õn…õ waca k…Ē w…õc…ôk m…Ē.
\v 20 K…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu disr…õ-…õ, domun dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ē Ňčande k…ôcbik…õn…õ, ti t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčafi-…õ. Tin tayi t…Ē k…Ē Ňčande k…ôck…Ē k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôk…Ēb…ôc k…Ē k…ôc…Ēf…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ-…õ.
\v 21 W…õc…ôk k…Ē waca w…Ē p…ômar Ňčacbik…õn…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčafi m…Ē. Sariy…õ sa t…õm o t…õm s…Ē, nn…Ē Aruna k…Ē yuruya y…Ēn Ňčayi m…Ē d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp.
\s1 Moro m…Ēb…Ēy ma k…ôd…ôs ka aloŇčn…õ
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 23 M…ôna m…ôl…õk suray s…ôbotu amb…Ēnc: K…ôl…Ēl ka k…ôt…Ēk nk…õ aŇčwe mir m…Ē kilo k…ôcam…ôt, pol ya k…ôt…Ēk k…ôbif…ôli nk…õ aŇčwe sinam…Ēn m…Ē kilo m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē dac…Ē, k…Ē kilo m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē dac…Ē ka awo Ňč…Ēl…Ēma nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēmb…Ēt amb…Ēnc m…Ē,
\v 24 k…Ē k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya k…ôbif…ôli kilo k…ôcam…ôt p…ôm…Ē potubuc pa nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku, k…Ē moro ma olif lit…õr cam…ôt-tin.
\v 25 M…ôlomps…õ yi moro m…Ēb…Ēy mopus ma d…ôKanu: PagbuluŇč mi labund…õ, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ y…õb…ôc ya w…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôlomp…ôs labund…õ. Moro mopus m…Ē mm…õ ande pacb…Ēy nde d…ôKanu m…Ē.
\v 26 Moro mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē m…ônde m…ôcb…Ēy aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu k…Ē kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôy…Ē walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē,
\v 27 k…ôb…ôp ka am…õsa k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya Ňči f…ôp, p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya pi, tetek p…Ēc…Ēf…õ MARIKI suray,
\v 28 tetek toloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya pi, k…ôsamp k…Ē p…õc…ôm…õn…õ pa ki.
\v 29 M…ôpus…õ MARIKI ca cac…Ēk…Ē, yendey…Ēn…õ ca c…ôpus yosoku p…õs, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ paka mp…õ o mp…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti fum nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ ca cac…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, …ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ oŇč fum nw…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē.
\p 
\v 30 M…ôb…Ēy s…Ē Aruna moro mam…Ēk…Ē k…Ē awut …Ēn k…ôd…ôs Ňča dekiriŇč da k…ôloŇčn…õ, m…ôpus Ňča nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčacb…ôc'em oŇč m…Ē.
\v 31 M…ôloku aka Yisrayel: Moro m…Ēb…Ēy mopus ma ina MARIKI m…Ē, d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp donu.
\v 32 Ali fum …Ēf…Ēsop…õ mi d…ôris tat…Ēk…Ē kif…ôli, ali fum p…ômar f…õ s…Ē p…ôlomp…ôs moro mowur…õn…õ ma mam…õ. Moro m…Ē mm…õ amb…Ēy k…ôpus ka aloŇčn…õ aŇč…õ and…ôs dekiriŇč da y…õb…ôc ya d…ôKanu m…Ē. Moro mopus m…Ē mm…õ p…ômar aka Yisrayel Ňčalel…ôs MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē.
\v 33 Nw…õ o nw…õ olomp…ôs moro mowur…õn…õ ma mi, p…ôsop mi w…ôt…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ m…Ē, aŇčwur…õ w…ôkayi aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.
\s1 K…ôlomp…ôs ka suray
\p 
\v 34 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: M…ôl…õk ca c…ôbotu amb…Ēnc: Stakte, onik…ôs k…Ē kalban…ĒŇč, m…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôl yi k…Ē suray s…ôt…Ēt sa k…ôl…Ēl ka k…ôt…Ēk, y…õt…ôŇčn…õn…õ d…õlay.
\v 35 W…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôlomp…ôs labund…õ p…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôl suray sas…Ēk…Ē m…õr, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôs…Ēt…Ē suray s…ôt…Ēt k…Ē s…ôsoku ns…õ ampus…õ y…õb…ôc ya d…ôKanu m…Ē.
\v 36 Pabif…ôli suray s…ôl…Ēma, ns…õ andek…Ēboc nde kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôy…Ē walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē tekiriŇč ta nde aŇčgbancan disr…õ k…ôfo nk…õ s…ôndek…Ē s…ôcb…ôp…õn…õ m…Ē. Suray sosoku s…Ē ns…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē.
\v 37 P…ômar f…õ n…ôde n…ôclomp…ôs suray s…ôwur…õn…õ sa saŇčs…õ ns…õ afum ŇčaŇčsop…õ kif…ôli m…Ē, p…ômar s…ôy…Ēn…õ nu s…ôpus…õ fum nw…õ and…ôs dekiriŇč da y…õb…ôc ya MARIKI m…Ē.
\v 38 Nw…õ o nw…õ olomp…ôs suray p…ôm…Ē saŇčs…õ, teta k…ône ka si amb…Ēnc Ňčobotu m…Ē, aŇčwur…õ w…ôkayi aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.
\c 31
\s1 Alomp…ôs a aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôn…ôŇčk iwe Betsalel tewe t…Ēn, wan ka Uri, wans…Ē ka Hur, w…ôka kusuŇčka ka Yuda.
\v 3 Ilas k…Ē amera Ňča Kanu nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôc…õrŇč…õ, p…ôs…Ēk domp, p…ôc…ôr…õ y…õb…ôc f…ôp m…Ē,
\v 4 …õnc…ôr…õ k…ôp…ôr y…õb…ôc ya k…õma, ya gbeti k…Ē ya k…Ēp…ôr,
\v 5 k…ôpat ka masar momot…ôr-mot…ôr k…Ē k…ôs…õt mi d…ôf…ôr…õm, k…ôpat ka t…Ēk, k…Ē d…õc…õr…ôŇč da y…õb…ôc f…ôp.
\v 6 Is…ĒŇč k…Ē w…ômar nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ Oholiyab wan ka Ahisamak w…ôka kusuŇčka ka Dan, k'is…ĒŇč s…Ē afum al…Ēma d…õc…õr…ôŇč. Ňäa Ňč'andek…Ēb…õr…õn…õ k…ôb…ôc ka t…Ēk…Ē isom …ôm m…Ē f…ôp:
\v 7 K…ôy…õf…õ ka aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu k…ôb…ôp ka kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôy…Ē walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa da MARIKI k'aka Yisrayel m…Ē, k…ôk…Ē af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya, k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya aŇčgbancan,
\v 8 k…ôl…õk am…õsa k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya Ňči, p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp pa k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs, k…ôb…ôp ka yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya pi, tetek p…Ēc…Ēf…õ MARIKI suray,
\v 9 tetek toloŇčn…õ pa p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēc…Ēf k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya pi, k…ôsamp k…Ē p…õc…ôm…õn…õ pa ki,
\v 10 yamos ya d…ôKanu ya Aruna w…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ē yuruya y…Ēn ny…õ Ňčande k…ôcb…õrn…õ k…Ē Ňčandeb…ôc'em-…õ.
\v 11 Moro m…Ēb…Ēy k…Ē labund…õ dobotu amb…Ēnc da aŇčgbip Ňčosoku, ac…õr…ôŇč Ňčalomp…ôs yi p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē isom …ôm ti m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Simiti d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm
\p 
\v 12 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 13 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: N…ôde n…ôclel…ôs d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm dem, tendey…Ēn…õ ina k…Ē n…ôna aka Yisrayel dac…Ē t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ haŇč d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp da yuruya yonu, ti tendes…ĒŇč…õ Ňčac…ôr…õ a in'…Ēy…Ēn…õ MARIKI mm…õ m…ĒŇčs…Ēk…ôs nu, n…ôy…Ēn…õ afum aŇč…õ ampus'em m…Ē.
\v 14 N…ôde n…ôclel…ôs d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, bawo d…Ēs…Ēk dopus d…Ē nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē. Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēlel…ôs di m…Ē, andif k…Ē. Fum nw…õ o nw…õ …õmb…ôc t…õb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, aŇčwur…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.
\v 15 N…ôde n…ôcb…ôc mata cam…ôt-tin, mba simiti tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč t…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē. Fum nw…õ o nw…õ …õmb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm dad…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, andif k…Ē.
\v 16 P…ômar aka Yisrayel Ňčalel…ôs d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm. Ňäac…ôm…õ sariy…õ sa di dar…ôŇč d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ t…õcaŇčs…õ ta danapa da t…õm o t…õm.
\v 17 T…õgb…õk…ôr…õ tant…õ tendeyi oŇč ina k'aka Yisrayel dac…Ē t…õm o t…õm. Bawo mata cam…ôt-tin m…Ē MARIKI …õnab…ôc ant…Ēf k…Ē k…Ēm, tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k'…õsak y…õb…ôc, k'eŇčes…ôm.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 18 Nt…õ MARIKI elip k…ôlok-lok…ôr Musa nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi m…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč Musa walak…õ wa masar m…õr…ôŇč nw…õ wement…ôr danapa d…Ēn k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē, nw…õ MARIKI …õnacic…õ m…õl…ôr m…Ēn yati m…Ē.
\c 32
\ms2 Aka Yisrayel k…ôl…ôs…ôr k…ôŇčan danapa k…Ē Kanu
\mr 32-34
\s1 Tura ta k…õma
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčan…ôŇčk nt…õ Musa oncwon k…ôtor k…ôy…õf…õ ka nde t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč m…Ē. Awa, k'afum ŇčaŇčk…Ē ŇčaloŇčkan…õ nn…Ē Aruna eyi m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęM…ôlomps…õ su canu c…ôk…Ēt su f…Ēr kiriŇč, bawo Musa fum w…ôkaw…õ …õmp…õn…õ su Misira m…Ē, s…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ nt…õ t…Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 2 K…Ē Aruna oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôwur…õ yad…ôl…ôŇč…ôs ya k…õma ny…õ aran anu, awut anu arkun k…Ē aran, Ňčamb…õr…ôsn…õ m…Ē, n…ôk…õr'em yi.¬Ľ
\v 3 K'afum aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčawur…õ-wur…õ yad…ôl…ôŇč…ôs ya k…õma ny…õ Ňčanab…õr…ôsn…õ d…ôl…ôŇč…ôs m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč yi Aruna.
\v 4 K…Ē Aruna …õmbaŇčs…ôr Ňča yi d…ôwaca, k'…õŇčgb…õc…õ t…õr…ôŇčka ta tura towut anata. K'aka Yisrayel Ňčaloku: ¬ęKanu kam k…Ē kaŇčk…õ, Yisrayel, nk…õ k…ômp…õn'am at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 5 Nt…õ Aruna …õn…ôŇčk ti m…Ē, k'olomp…ôs tetek toloŇčn…õ tura tat…Ēk…Ē tekiriŇč. K'oŇčkul…õ: ¬ęAlna amboc…õ MARIKI k…ôsata!¬Ľ
\v 6 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k'aka Yisrayel Ňčay…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf k…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu. K…Ē Ňčand…õ, Ňčandi yeri, Ňčamun, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôwol…ôs-wol…ôs.
\p 
\v 7 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôtor kat…ôna kat…ôna, bawo afum am aŇč…õ m…ôsol…õ k…ôwur…õn…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē, Ňčanciya p…ôp…ĒŇč.
\v 8 Ňäamb…õlk…ôr k…ôgbaym…õ d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēk…Ē iment…ôr Ňča m…Ē. T…õr…ôŇčka ta tura ta af…õc t…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs, k…Ē Ňčantontn…õn…õ pi, k…Ē ŇčaloŇčn…õn…õ pi, haŇč k…Ē Ňčaloku: ‚ÄĻCanu conu c…Ē canc…õ Yisrayel nc…õ c…ôwur…õn…õ nu at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē!‚Äļ¬Ľ
\p 
\v 9 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęAwa, in…ôŇčk nt…õ afum akaŇč…õ Ňčayi m…Ē, ataŇči l…ôŇč…ôs Ňč…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ f…ôp faŇčan.
\v 10 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč m…ôc'em, k…ôt…õl'em k…Ē p…ônder nn…Ē Ňčayi m…Ē, k…ôm…ôl…ôk Ňča k'inder f…ôp faŇčan, mba m…ôna indes…ĒŇč'am k…ôy…Ē yuruya y…õlar…ôm m…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôka at…Ēf Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 11 K…Ē Musa …õl…õts…õn…õ MARIKI Kanu k…Ēn k…ôŇčaŇčn…õ, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęMARIKI, ta ake t…Ē p…ônt…õl…õn'am nda afum am-…õ, aŇč…õ m…ôwur…õn…õ Misira f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fam f…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē s…Ēk…ôt sa k…ôca kam m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 12 Tendes…ĒŇč…õ aka Misira Ňčandeloku: ¬ęK…ôy…Ē k…ôŇčan p…ôl…õc k…Ē MARIKI owur…õn…õ aka Yisrayel at…Ēf Ňča Misira, k…ôk…Ēdif k…ôŇčan nde d…ôm…Ēr…Ē, p…ôm…ôl…ôk Ňča, p…ônim Ňča ant…Ēf k…ôroŇč!¬Ľ M…ôtor…õ ab…ôk…ôc ta m…ôy…Ē ti, m…ôbup…ôr…õ k…ôy…Ē ka afum am p…ôl…õc!
\v 13 M…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ Abraham, Siyaka k…Ē Yakuba, acar am aŇč…õ m…ônaloku, m…ôcd…õr…ôm m…ônas…ôrka: ¬ęIndes…ĒŇč…õ afum am k…ôla p…ôm…Ē c…Ēs ca darenc. Indes…ĒŇč yuruya yam at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ f…ôp nŇč…õ iloku ta Ňči m…Ē, Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ oŇč k…õ k…ôŇčan doru o doru.¬Ľ
\v 14 K…Ē MARIKI ombup…ôr…õ s…Ē p…ôl…õc p…Ēk…Ē …õnac…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôy…Ē afum …Ēn m…Ē.
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē Musa ontor k…ôy…õf…õ ka t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč, p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr walak…õ nw…õ m…õr…ôŇč, pacic…ôs wi b…ôk…ôc yayi m…õr…ôŇč f…ôp.
\v 16 Walak…õ waw…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, y…õb…ôc ya Kanu y…õnayi, nk…Ēn Kanu …õnacic…ôs wi k…ôroŇč k…ôca k…Ēn.
\v 17 Nt…õ Yosuwe ene aka Yisrayel k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ m…Ē, k'oloku Musa: ¬ęSim sa k…ôwan s'iŇčne saŇčs…õ nde saŇčka disr…õ.¬Ľ
\v 18 K…Ē Musa oloku k…Ē: ¬ęAla baf…Ē sim sa k…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…ôtam ka k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ s…Ē, baf…Ē sim sa k…ôpariya k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ s…Ē ina iyi k…ône. Sim sa k…ôsata s…Ē ina iyi k…ône.¬Ľ
\v 19 Nt…õ …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ saŇčka m…Ē, k'…õn…ôŇčk t…õr…ôŇčka ta tura towut, k'…õn…ôŇčk s…Ē afum Ňčacpis…õ. Awa, k…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Musa, k'…õŇčgbal walak…õ wa masar waw…Ēk…Ē …õnat…Ēmp…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē w…ĒŇčk…Ē w…õw…õsl…õ-w…õsl…õ nde t…Ēr…Ē d…ônt…Ēf.
\v 20 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk t…õr…ôŇčka tat…Ēk…Ē Ňčanalomp…ôs m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…õr pi d…ôn…õnc. K…Ē Musa embif…ôli y…õlp…ôs y…Ēk…Ē y…õnac…ôm…õ m…Ē, k'…õl…õk yi k'…õŇčgbal d…ôromun nd…õ …õnas…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel k…ômun m…Ē.
\v 21 K…Ē Musa …õŇčkaf…ôl…õ nn…Ē Aruna eyi m…Ē, k'eyif k…Ē: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčay…Ē …ôm nt…õ m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča kiciya k…ôp…ĒŇč kaŇčk…õ m…Ē?¬Ľ
\v 22 K…Ē Aruna oloku: ¬ęTa p…ôt…õl'am, mariki mem! M…ôna yati m…ônc…ôr…õ aka Yisrayel: Ňäamb…Ēt…ôr mes m…õl…õc.
\v 23 Ňäa Ňčalok'im: ‚ÄĻM…ôlomps…õ su canu nc…õ c…ôndek…Ēt su kiriŇč m…Ē, bawo s…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ nt…õ t…Ēs…Ēt…Ē Musa nw…õ …õnawur…õn…õ su at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē.‚Äļ
\v 24 K'iloku Ňča a nw…õ o nw…õ …ĒŇčy…Ē peyesn…õn…õ pa k…õma m…Ē p…ôwur…õ pi! K…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč im yi, k'imb…õr yi d…ôn…õnc, k…Ē tura towut tant…õ towur di disr…õ.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôt…Ēr…ôs
\p 
\v 25 K…Ē Musa …õn…ôŇčk nt…õ ant…Ēs…Ētam k…ôdusum afum m…Ē, bawo Aruna …õnasak Ňča Ňčacy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ŇčafaŇč m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē t…õŇčlap…ôs Ňča nn…Ē ater…õn…õ aŇčan Ňčayi m…Ē.
\v 26 K…Ē Musa …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôc…ôm…õ d…ôkusuŇčka da saŇčka, k'oloku: ¬ęN…ôna aŇč…õ n…ôyin…õ MARIKI m…Ē, n…ôder nn…Ē iyi m…Ē!¬Ľ K'aka kusuŇčka ka Lewy f…ôp ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčam…õpn…õ Musa d…ônt…Ēf.
\v 27 K…Ē Musa oloku Ňča: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI, Kanu ka Yisrayel k…ôloku: ‚ÄĻNw…õ o nw…õ p…ôl…õk dakma d…Ēn, p…ôcop nn…Ē d…ôkusuŇčka da saŇčka haŇč d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da si, k…ôdif…ôt aw…õnc anu, anapa anu k'akom…õn…õ anu.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\v 28 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē k'aLewy Ňčalel…ôs dim da Musa, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel afum wul maas (3.000) k…ôfi.
\v 29 K…Ē Musa oloku aLewy: ¬ęK…ôy…õf…õ m…Ēk…Ē and…ôs nu n…ôy…Ēn…õ oŇč afum aŇč…õ Ňčandeyi y…õb…ôc ya MARIKI m…Ē, bawo n…ônes…ôrn…õ f…õ k…ôdif ka awut anu k…Ē aw…õnc anu aŇča. MARIKI p…ôpoc…õ nu m…Ēk…Ē p…ôt…Ēt!¬Ľ
\s1 Musa …õl…õts…õn…õ Kanu k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ ka aka Yisrayel
\p 
\v 30 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk, k…Ē Musa oloku aka Yisrayel: ¬ęN…ônciya p…ôp…ĒŇč! Nd…õk…ôl oŇč k…ôp…õ k'inder nde MARIKI eyi m…Ē. T…Ēl…Ēma ik…Ētam k…ôs…Ēt…ôr k…Ē k…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka kiciya konu.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 31 K…Ē Musa oluks…ôrn…õ nde MARIKI eyi m…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęM…ôŇčaŇčn…õ MARIKI! Afum akaŇč…õ Ňčanciya p…ôp…ĒŇč, Ňčalomp…ôs canu ca k…õma.
\v 32 M…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ Ňča kiciya k…ôŇčan, il…õts…õn'am! K…Ē m…ôy…Ē f…õ ti-…õ, m…ônim ina tewe nde buk b…Ēk…Ē m…ônacic m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 33 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęFum nw…õ enciy'em m…Ē, iŇčliŇč tewe t…Ēn buk bem disr…õ.
\v 34 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, m…ôk…Ē, m…ôsol…õ afum am m…ôkek…ôr…õ Ňča k…ôfo nk…õ iment…ôr …ôm m…Ē. M…õl…õk…õ mem mendek…Ē yi nu kiriŇč, mba d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ inder k…ôboc…õ nu kiti nde n…ôyi m…Ē, indes…ĒŇč Ňča ay…õk Ňča kiciya k…ôŇčan.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 35 K…Ē MARIKI osut aka Yisrayel, bawo Ňčanac…ôm…õ Aruna dar…ôŇč, a w…ôkak…Ē p…ôlomps…õ Ňča t…õr…ôŇčka ta tura towut.
\c 33
\s1 Kanu k…ôloku Musa k…ôl…õk d…Ēp…Ē Ňčak…Ē
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęN…ôy…õf…õ k…ôfo kaŇčk…õ, m…ôna k'aka Yisrayel aŇč…õ m…ômp…õn…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē. N…ôk…Ē nde at…Ēf Ňč…Ēk…Ē inad…õrm…õ Abraham, Siyaka, k…Ē Yakuba m…Ē, icloku: ‚ÄĻIndes…ĒŇč Ňči yuruya yam.‚Äļ
\v 2 Indesak m…õl…õk…õ meyi nu kiriŇč, indek…Ēb…õl…ôs aKanaŇč, aM…Ēr, aHit, aPerisi, aHiwy, k…Ē aYebus,
\v 3 at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē ŇčomboŇč dal…õ k‚Äôawop m…Ē. Mba if…Ēdesol…õ nu inas…ôrka, iŇčnes…õ ta idek…Ēlip nu k…ôdif…ôt, bawo afum ataŇči l…ôŇč…ôs Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ
\v 4 Nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčane moloku mebeŇč…ôsn…õn…õ mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčan…Ēn…õ mi k…ôbal, nw…õ o nw…õ …õnayesn…õ f…õ s…Ē.
\v 5 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: Afum ataŇči l…ôŇč…ôs Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ. K'isol…õ nu k…ôk…Ē t…õm tepic gb…ôc…ôr…ôm-…õ, iŇčm…ôl…ôk nu d…Ēp…Ē. N…ôwur…õ yeyesn…õn…õ yonu indem…Ēm…ôn nt…õ indey…Ē nu m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 6 Ti disr…õ, k'aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčgbek-gbeki yeyesn…õn…õ yaŇčan f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ ka t…Ēr…Ē ta Hor…õb.
\s1 AŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôps…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu
\p 
\v 7 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk aŇčgbancan k'…õnc…ômb…ôr Ňči nk…Ēns…ôrka saŇčka todoru p…ôwak k…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ Ňči. K'ewe di ¬ęAŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.¬Ľ Nw…õ o nw…õ …õncfaŇč tes nn…Ē MARIKI eyi m…Ē, m…õn…õ w…ôkayi p…ôwur saŇčka disr…õ p…ôder nde aŇčgbancan ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē.
\v 8 K…Ē Musa ende k…ôcwur k…ôk…Ē daŇčgbancan-…õ, aka Yisrayel f…ôp ŇčaŇčy…õf…õ. Ňäac…ôm…õ-c…ôm…õ cusuŇčka ca c…ôbal c…ôŇčan Ňčagb…ôtn…õ k…Ē haŇč p…ôb…õr…õ aŇčgbancan ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē disr…õ.
\v 9 K…Ē Musa elip k…ôb…õr…õ aŇčgbancan ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē disr…õ-…õ, acul Ňča k…ôp Ňčotor Ňč…õc…ôm…õ d…ôkusuŇčka da aŇčgbancan ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, MARIKI p…ôlok-loku k…Ē Musa.
\v 10 K'aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčan…ôŇčk t…Ēk…Ē k…ôp k…ôncc…ôm…õ k…ôsuŇčka ka aŇčgbancan m…Ē, Ňčay…õf…õ f…ôp faŇčan Ňčatont…ôsn…õ nw…õ o nw…õ nde kusuŇčka ka abal Ňč…Ēn.
\v 11 MARIKI p…ôlok-lok…ôr Musa Ňčat…õf…ôr…õn…õ, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ fum endelok-lok…ôr wanapa k…Ēn m…Ē. K…Ē telip-…õ, Musa p…ôlukus nde d…ôsaŇčka. Mba w…ômars…õn…õ k…Ēn w…ôt…õmp Yosuwe wan ka Nun …õncy…õf…õ f…õ aŇčgbancan ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē disr…õ.
\s1 MARIKI k…ôlok-loku k…Ēn k…Ē Musa
\p 
\v 12 K…Ē Musa oloku MARIKI: ¬ęM…ôm…Ēm…ôn, m…ôlok'im: ‚ÄĻM…ôsol…õ aka Yisrayel,‚Äļ mba m…ôment…ôr f'em fum nw…õ m…ôyi k…ôsom k…ôdemar im m…Ē. Ti disr…õ m…ôloku: ‚ÄĻInc…ôr…õ tewe tam, k'iy…õk-y…õk …ôm, k…Ē k…ômar ka k…ôb…Ēt…ôr kem k…ômb…ôp …ôm.‚Äļ
\v 13 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč il…õts…õn'am, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a m…ômar im teta k…ôb…Ēt…ôr kam-…õ, m…ôs…ĒŇč'em k…ôc…ôr…õ s…ôp…Ē sam. T…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč'em k…ôc…ôr'am, t…Ēs…ĒŇč'em s…Ē k…ômar ka k…ôb…Ēt…ôr kam k…ôsol'em. M…ôm…Ēm…ôn afum a at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ, akam Ňč…Ē!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 14 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęInas…ôrka, in'endek…Ē k…Ē m…ôna! Is…ĒŇč …ôm s…Ē p…ôforu.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē Musa oloku: ¬ęK…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a m…ôf…Ēk…Ē-…õ, ta m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôp…õ nn…Ē de.
\v 16 C…ôke c'andetam k…ôc…ôr…õ a m…ôy…õk-y…õk su ina k…Ē afum am-…õ? K…ôyi kam su dac…Ē gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…ôntam k…ôment…ôr k…ôgb…õy kosu k…Ē afum alp…ôs aka doru.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 17 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęIndey…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ôloku m…Ē. Inc…ôr…õ tewe tam, k'iy…õk-y…õk …ôm, k…Ē k…ômar ka k…ôb…Ēt…ôr kem k…ômb…ôp …ôm.¬Ľ
\v 18 K…Ē Musa oloku MARIKI: ¬ęM…ôment…ôr im n…Ēr…Ē da debeki dam, il…õts…õn'am.¬Ľ
\v 19 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęIndecep…ôr…õn'am f…Ēr kiriŇč dobotu dem amera, icbonc s…Ē tewe ta MARIKI f…Ēr yam kiriŇč. IŇčaŇčn…õn…õ nw…õ iŇčfaŇč k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ m…Ē, indey…Ēn…õ fum n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr nw…õ indefaŇč k…ôy…Ēn…õ n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 20 K…Ē MARIKI endeŇč…ôr: ¬ęM…ôf…Ēdetam k…ôn…ôŇčk im k…ôro m…ôna Musa, bawo fum …Ēf…Ētam k…ôn…ôŇčk im k…ôro w…ôkayi p…ôyi s…Ē doru.¬Ľ
\v 21 K…Ē MARIKI oloku: ¬ęK…ôfo k…Ē kaŇčk…õ ina k…ôs…ôk, m…ôc…ôm…õ tasar tant…õ k…ôroŇč.
\v 22 K…Ē n…Ēr…Ē da debeki dem dendenacep…ôr-…õ, indeb…õr …ôm abi Ňča tasar disr…õ, ikump …ôm k…ôca kem haŇč iclip k…ôcep…ôr.
\v 23 K'ilip k…ôcep…ôr-…õ, a ideliŇč k…ôca kem, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē m…ôntam k…ôn…ôŇčk im kumunt, mba af…Ētam k…ôn…ôŇčk im k…ôro.¬Ľ
\c 34
\s1 Walak…õ wofu wa sariy…õ
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: M…ôpat walak…õ m…õr…ôŇč wa masar p…ôm…Ē w…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, indecic…ôs moloku m…Ēk…Ē m…õnayi walak…õ w…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē waw…Ēk…Ē m…ônapor-poru m…Ē k…ôroŇč.
\v 2 M…ôlomp…ôsn…õ b…ôtb…ôtana. M…ôdena m…ônuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôp…õ nn…Ē t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi k…ôroŇč, m…ôk…Ē m…ôc…ôm…õ f…Ēr yem kiriŇč d…ôndo t…Ēr…Ē d…ôtelempan.
\v 3 Ali fum ta p…ôp…õ k…Ē m…ôna, ta pan…ôŇčk s…Ē fum t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč. K…ôy…õf…õ ka Ňčkesiya, cir, c…ôna ta y…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ di k…ôs…Ēm…ôt!
\v 4 K…Ē Musa …õmpat walak…õ wa masar m…õr…ôŇč p…ôm…Ē w…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē Musa …õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy k'…õmp…õ nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi k…ôroŇč p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr walak…õ wa masar waw…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē.
\v 5 K…Ē MARIKI ontor d…ôk…ôp, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôyi Musa k…ôs…ôk, k'omboncn…õ tewe t…Ēn: ¬ęMARIKI.¬Ľ
\v 6 K…Ē MARIKI encep…ôr Musa f…Ēr kiriŇč p…ôcloku: ¬ęMARIKI, MARIKI, Kanu k'iy…Ēn…õ nk…õ k…ôŇčy…Ēn…õ n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr, k…ôcŇčaŇčn…õn…õ m…Ē, Kanu nk…õ p…ônt…Ēb…õlk…ôr k…ôt…õl…õ m…Ē, Kanu nk…õ k…ôŇčsekt…ôrn…õ danapa da ki m…Ē.
\v 7 Kanu k'iy…Ēn…õ nk…õ k…ônt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôsekt…ôrn…õ danapa da fum haŇč d…õt…õmp wul win m…Ē, Kanu nk…õ k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ afum kiciya k…ôŇčan, k…ôt…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl k…ôŇčan k…Ē p…ôl…õc paŇčaŇč m…Ē. Mba k…ôf…ĒŇčaŇčn…õ kiti ka fum nw…õ …õnd…ôk…ôt m…Ē, fum nw…õ enciya m…Ē iŇčs…ĒŇč k…ôway k…ôl…õc k…Ēn yuruya y…Ēn d…õt…õmp maas, haŇč d…õt…õmp maŇčk…ôl…õ.¬Ľ
\v 8 K…Ē Musa …õmb…õlk…ôr k…ôc…ôp tobu d…ônt…Ēf k'ontontn…õ.
\v 9 K…Ē Musa oloku: ¬ęMariki, il…õts…õn'am k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a is…Ēt…Ē k…ômar ka k…ôb…Ēt…ôr f…Ēr yam kiriŇč-…õ, m…ôder Mariki m…ôsol…õ su. Afum ataŇči l…ôŇč…ôs Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ yati, mba m…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ kiciya kosu k…Ē p…ôl…õc posu, m…ôl…õk su s…ôy…Ēn…õ afum am.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôsek danapa
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęDanapa d…Ē s…ôndesek, f…Ēr ya afum am f…ôp kiriŇč, indey…Ē mes m…Ēp…ĒŇč mm…õ m…õntat…Ēyi doru dand…õ f…ôp m…Ē, k…Ē nda afum a t…Ēf y…õlp…ôs ny…õ m…Ē. Aka Yisrayel aŇč…õ Ňčandek…õl …ôm m…Ē, Ňčanden…ôŇčk y…õb…ôc ya MARIKI, t…Ēy…Ē t…Ēp…ĒŇč nt…õ indey…Ē k…Ē m…ôna m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 11 ¬ęM…ôde m…ôcy…Ē nt…õ o nt…õ iŇčk…Ēsom …ôm m…Ēk…Ē k…ôdey…Ē m…Ē. Indek…Ēb…õl…ôs f…Ēr yam kiriŇč Am…Ēr, aKanaŇč, aHit, aPerisi, aHiwy, k…Ē aYebus.
\v 12 M…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ ta n…ôdek…Ēsek danapa k…Ē afum aka t…Ēf ny…õ n…ôndek…Ēb…õr…õ m…Ē, ta Ňčadey…Ēn…õ mowul aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.
\v 13 N…ôdek…Ē n…ôcw…Ēk…ôc tetek toloŇčn…õ taŇčan, n…ôgbal masar motontn…õ maŇčan m…õc…ômb…ôr, n…ôcc…õp…ôs mogbu maŇčan motontn…õ ma d…ôcanu.
\v 14 Ta m…ôdek…Ē m…ôctontn…õn…õ canu c…ôcuru, bawo tewe t…Ēn t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ‚ÄĻMARIKI ma k…ôraca,‚Äļ Kanu nk…õ k…ôy…Ē k…ôraca m…Ē.
\v 15 Ta m…ôdek…Ēsek danapa k…Ē afum aka at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē. Bawo k…Ē teyi-…õ, k…Ē Ňčandek…Ēsali ŇčacloŇčn…õ canu c…ôŇčan-…õ, ŇčaŇčw'am k…ôk…Ēt…ôŇčn…õ ti, k…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ē oŇč-…õ, m…ôf…Ētam k…ôyi ta m…ôndi yeri yay…Ēk…Ē ŇčaŇčk…ĒloŇčn…õn…õ canu c…ôŇčan m…Ē-…õ.
\v 16 K…Ē n…ôfac…õ awut anu arkun awut aŇčan aran-…õ, awut aran akak…Ē Ňčandeb…õrs…õ Ňča k…ôsali k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ k…ôŇčan ka canu c…ôcuru.
\v 17 Ta m…ôdek…Ēlomp…ôs canu ca f…õc de.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 18 ¬ęM…ôdek…Ē m…ôcboc k…ôsata ka c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēy…Ē lebin: Mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ma Ňčof Ňča Abib, m…ôdek…Ē m…ôcs…Ēm c…ôcom nc…õ c…ônt…Ēy…Ē lebin m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ isom …ôm ti m…Ē, bawo Ňčof Ňča Abib, ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē disr…õ Ňč…Ē m…ônay…õf…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 19 ¬ęPokom p…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē porkun pa y…Ēc…Ēl f…ôp pemi p…Ē, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ pokom porkun mp…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yonu yende yockom m…Ē, k…ôl…õk wana, wir haŇč aŇčkesiya.
\v 20 M…ôndek…Ē m…ôcwurus s…Ēfale s…ôwut ns…õ andek…Ēkom s…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti ambiyofo, k…Ē m…ônt…Ēwurus si-…õ, m…ôtepi si kilim. M…ôdek…Ē m…ôcwurus awut am arkun ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē aŇč…õ andek…Ē packom'am m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p ¬ęAf…Ēde pack…Ē nde k…ôfo kem k…ôsoku waca w…Ēs…Ēk…ôr.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 21 ¬ęM…ôndek…Ē m…ôcb…ôc mata cam…ôt-tin, m…ôlel…ôs tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm m…Ē. Ali p…ôy…Ēn…õ a t…õm tebifti k…Ē t…õt…õl t…Ē m…ôlel…ôs pi.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 22 ¬ęM…ôdek…Ē m…ôcboc k…ôsata ka Mataka Moluks…ôr, t…õm nt…õ m…ôndek…Ēcop k…ôt…õl m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôsata ka Y…õt…õl t…õm nt…õ m…ôndet…õl d…ôc…ôb…Ēf teren d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr m…Ē.
\v 23 K…ôren o k…ôren, k…ômaas k…Ē aka Yisrayel arkun p…ômar Ňčader Ňčament…ôrn…õ f…Ēr ya W…ôb…õ MARIKI Kanu ka aka Yisrayel kiriŇč.
\v 24 Bawo indek…ĒbaŇč…ôr afum al…Ēma t…Ēf yaŇčan ib…õr…õn…õ yonu nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ yonu y…õb…õk m…Ē, ali fum …Ēf…Ēdek…Ētubucn…õ k…ôbaŇč…ôr n…ôna t…Ēf yonu t…õm tant…õ maas ta teren disr…õ, nt…õ m…ônde k…ôck…Ē d…ôk…ôment…ôrn…õ MARIKI Kanu konu f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 25 ¬ęM…ôf…Ēde m…ôck…õr'em p…Ēc…Ēl poloŇčn…õ k…Ē paka p…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin, p…ômar f…õ m…ôm…õŇčk s…õm ya k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs ka K…ôcep…ôr ka m…õl…õk…õ medif k…ôy…õf…õ d…Ēf…Ēy haŇč d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk b…ôtb…ôt.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 26 ¬ęM…ôdek…Ē m…ôck…õr…õ nde k…ôl…Ē ka MARIKI Kanu kam yokom y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ya ant…Ēf Ňčam. Ta m…ôdek…Ē m…ôcp…õc…õ ambiyofo m…õs…õ ma k…õr…õ ka Ňči.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 27 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôcic moloku mam…õ, bawo moloku mam…õ m'indesek…õ danapa k…Ē m…ôna k'aka Yisrayel.¬Ľ
\v 28 K…Ē Musa Ňčayi k…Ē MARIKI mata w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ pibi k…Ē daŇč. Endi f…õ peri, omun f…õ domun. K'encic…ôs walak…õ nw…õ k…ôroŇč moloku ma sariy…õ sa danapa, m…õt…ôk…ôs w…ôco.
\s1 K…ôlukus ka Musa nde d…ôsaŇčka
\p 
\v 29 K…Ē Musa ontor k…ôy…õf…õ ka t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi k…ôroŇč p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr walak…õ m…õr…ôŇč nw…õ wement…ôr danapa d…Ēn k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē. Musa …õnac…ôr…õ f…õ a k…ôlok-loku k…Ēn k…Ē Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôro k…ômot.
\v 30 Aruna k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…ôp ŇčaŇčgb…ôtn…õ Musa, nt…õ k…ôro k…Ēn k…ôncmot m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčanes…õ k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē.
\v 31 K…Ē Musa ewe Ňča. K…Ē Aruna k'akiriŇč a k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčander nn…Ē nk…Ēn Musa eyi m…Ē, k'olok-lok…ôr Ňča.
\v 32 Nt…õ elip m…Ē, k…Ē aka Yisrayel alp…ôs aŇč…õ Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē oŇč, k'oloku Ňča moloku m…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi k…ôdeloku aka Yisrayel m…Ē.
\v 33 Nt…õ Musa elip k…ôlok-loku Ňča m…Ē, k'…õl…õk k…ôfak…ôl k'oŇčkumpn…õ k…ôro.
\v 34 Nt…õ Musa endeb…õr…õ nde k…ôfo k…ôsoku k…ôk…Ēlok-loku k…Ē MARIKI m…Ē, k'eliŇčn…õ k…ôfak…ôl d…ôk…ôro. K'owur k…ôy…õf…õ ka d…ôndo k…ôfo k…ôsoku disr…õ-…õ, p…ôloku aka Yisrayel t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI osom k…Ē k…ôdeloku Ňča m…Ē.
\v 35 Aka Yisrayel Ňčancm…Ēm…ôn k…ôro ka Musa nt…õ k…ôcmot m…Ē. K'elip k…ôlok-lok…ôr Ňča, p…ôkumpn…õ s…Ē k…ôro m…õn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ …ĒŇčk…Ē s…Ē nde k…ôfo k…ôsoku disr…õ k…ôk…Ēlok-loku k…Ē MARIKI m…Ē.
\c 35
\ms2 K…ôc…ômb…ôr ka aŇčgbancan Ňčosoku
\mr 35-40
\s1 Simiti d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē Musa oloŇčka aka Yisrayel f…ôp, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI osom a pacy…Ē:
\v 2 Mata cam…ôt-tin pab…ôc, mba tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, simiti, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm d…Ē nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē. Fum nw…õ o nw…õ …õmb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, andif k…Ē.
\v 3 P…ômar f…õ n…ômot n…õnc d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm simiti nde w…Ēl…Ē wonu.¬Ľ
\s1 AYisrayel ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ k…ôf…õk k…ôŇčan
\p 
\v 4 K…Ē Musa oloku k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI osom:
\v 5 ‚ÄĻN…ôl…õk d…ôy…Ēs…Ēt…Ē yonu n…ôf…õk…õ MARIKI. W…ôrkun nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēs…Ēk ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…Ēt…Ēt, p…ôk…õr…õ MARIKI k…ôf…õk: K…ôy…õf…õ k…õma, gbeti, k…Ēp…ôr,
\v 6 c…ôloto c…ôgb…ôt kar…õ alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňčeyim, Ňčeyimb…ôr…ôr s…Ē, c…ôloto nc…õ andun…õ s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler k…Ē c…ôfon ca wir m…Ē,
\v 7 kata ya Ňčkesiya yorkun ny…õ aŇčgb…ôt kar…õ alom Ňčeyim m…Ē, kata ya ntempeli, t…Ēk ya kasiya,
\v 8 k…Ē moro momot…õn…õ, labund…õ dobotu amb…Ēnc nd…õ ande pacgbuluŇč moro m…Ēb…Ēy, k…Ē suray s…ôbotu amb…Ēnc,
\v 9 k…Ē masar m…Ēt…Ēt mm…õ aŇčwe onik…ôs m…Ē, k…Ē m…Ēt…Ēt m…Ēl…Ēma mm…õ andeb…õr duma da ef…Ēd k…Ē yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc m…Ē.
\p 
\v 10 Ac…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ Ňčayi nu dac…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, Ňčader Ňčalomp…ôs ca c…ôk…Ē MARIKI osom nu k…ôlomp…ôs m…Ē f…ôp:
\v 11 D…ôkiyi dosoku, aŇčgbancan f…ôp k…Ē pokump…õ pa Ňči, Ňčkora ya Ňči, f…ôr…õm fa Ňči, mogbu ma Ňči, gbat-gbata ya Ňči k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya Ňči,
\v 12 kaŇčk…ôra ka d…ôKanu k…Ē c…ôgbo ca ki k…Ē af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya, k…Ē k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ,
\v 13 am…õsa k…Ē c…ôgbo ca Ňči, yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya Ňči f…ôp k…Ē c…ôcom nc…õ aloŇčn…õn…õ Kanu m…Ē,
\v 14 p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya pi, s…ôlamp k…Ē moro momot…õn…õ,
\v 15 tetek mp…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI suray m…Ē, k…Ē c…ôgbo ca pi, moro m…Ēb…Ēy, suray s…ôbotu amb…Ēnc, k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ k…ôŇčk…Ē and…õt aŇčgbancan Ňčosoku d…ôkusuŇčka m…Ē,
\v 16 tetek toloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf y…Ēc…Ēl k…Ē manta ma k…Ēp…ôr ya pi, c…ôgbo ca pi k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya pi f…ôp, k…ôsamp k…ôb…õr…õ domun d…Ēs…Ēk…ôsn…õn…õ, k…Ē p…õc…ôm…õn…õ pa ki,
\v 17 c…ôloto ca saŇčka, mogbu ma ci k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi, k…Ē k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ ka nde kusuŇčka ka saŇčka,
\v 18 c…ôgbo c…ôd…Ēf ca d…ôkiyi dosoku, ca saŇčka, k…Ē b…ônda y…Ēk…Ē p…ômar m…Ē,
\v 19 yamos yodu y…Ēk…Ē p…ômar pab…õrn…õ a pab…ôc y…õb…ôc nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku m…Ē, k…Ē yamos ya d…ôKanu ny…õ Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn Ňčandek…Ē Ňčacb…õrn…õ a Ňčacb…ôc…õ Kanu m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\p 
\v 20 K…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ k'aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčay…õf…õ f…Ēr ya Musa kiriŇč.
\v 21 Afum aŇč…õ Ňčanates…õ b…ôk…ôc m…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ MARIKI k…ôf…õk k…ôŇčan teta y…õb…ôc ya aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, k…Ē k…ôlomp…ôs ka yamos ya d…ôKanu.
\v 22 K'arkun k…Ē aran Ňčander. Afum aŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ē b…ôk…ôc yosoku p…õs m…Ē ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ yeyesn…õn…õ ya k…õma yad…ôl…ôŇč…ôs, kurund…õ, y…õgb…õkn…õ, c…ôsora k…Ē yeyesn…õn…õ f…ôp ny…õ alomps…õ k…õma m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčander Ňčas…ĒŇč yi MARIKI k…ôloŇčn…õ.
\p 
\v 23 AŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ē c…ôloto ca alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc m…Ē, alom Ňčeyim, c…ôloto ca s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, ca c…ôfon ca wir, kata ya Ňčkesiya yorkun ny…õ aŇčgb…ôt d…ôp…ôyim, k…Ē kata ya ntempeli m…Ē ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ yi f…ôp.
\v 24 AŇč…õ Ňčanam…õŇčk…ôrn…õ k…ôs…ôk k…ôf…õk ka gbeti k…Ē k…Ēp…ôr m…Ē, ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ yi MARIKI. AŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ē t…Ēk ya kasiya m…Ē, ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ yi teta y…õb…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē.
\v 25 K'aran ac…õr…ôŇč Ňčandun…õ c…ôloto ca suwa waca waŇčan, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ nc…õ Ňčanadu m…Ē, c…ôloto ca alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňčeyim, alom Ňča bulu k…Ē c…ôloto ca s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler.
\v 26 Aran ac…õr…ôŇč al…Ēma aŇč…õ Ňčanates…õ b…ôk…ôc m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčandun…õ c…ôloto c…ôtel…ôr c…ôfon ca cir.
\v 27 K'akiriŇč aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ masar ma onik…ôs k…Ē masar m…Ēt…Ēt m…Ēl…Ēma mm…õ p…ômar pab…õr…ôs duma da ef…Ēd k…Ē yuba ny…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč …õŇčgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc m…Ē,
\v 28 k…Ē suray s…ôbotu amb…Ēnc, k…Ē moro momot…õn…õ d…ôs…ôlamp, moro m…Ēb…Ēy k…Ē suray ns…õ anc…Ēf m…Ē.
\p 
\v 29 Arkun k…Ē aran aŇč…õ o aŇč…õ Ňčanates…õ b…ôk…ôc k…ôf…õk…õ y…õb…ôc ny…õ MARIKI …õnasom Musa m…Ē, f…ôp Ňčanak…õr…õ MARIKI k…ôpoc…õ k…ôŇčan b…ôk…ôc yosoku p…õs.
\s1 Betsalel k…Ē Oholiyab Ňčasump…ôr y…õb…ôc
\p 
\v 30 K…Ē Musa oloku aka Yisrayel: N…ôm…Ēm…ôn, MARIKI ewe Betsalel tewe t…Ēn, wan ka Uri wans…Ē ka Hur w…ôka kusuŇčka ka Yuda,
\v 31 k'…õlas k…Ē amera Ňča Kanu nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôc…õrŇč…õ, p…ôs…Ēk domp, p…ôc…ôr…õ y…õb…ôc f…ôp m…Ē.
\v 32 ∆źnc…ôr…õ k…ôp…ôr y…õb…ôc ya k…õma, ya gbeti, k…Ē ya k…Ēp…ôr,
\v 33 k…ôpat ka masar momot…ôr-mot…ôr, k…Ē k…ôs…õt mi d…ôf…ôr…õm, k…ôpat ka t…Ēk, k…Ē d…õc…õr…ôŇč da y…õb…ôc f…ôp, k…Ē k…ôp…ôr ka yi.
\v 34 K…Ē Kanu k…ômpoc…õ Betsalel p…ôt…Ēt nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôtam k…ôt…ôks…õ afum al…Ēma d…õc…õr…ôŇč dad…Ēk…Ē f…ôp m…Ē, k…Ē k…ômpoc…õ s…Ē Oholiyab wan ka Ahisamak w…ôka kusuŇčka ka Dan p…ôt…Ēt pap…Ēk…Ē.
\v 35 MARIKI …õnalas Ňča d…õc…õr…ôŇč Ňčactam k…ôb…ôc ka y…õb…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, k…ôy…õf…õ ka k…ôpat, k…ôn…õk…ôs, k…ôc…õm, k…ôdu c…ôloto ca alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňčeyim, c…ôloto c…ôf…ôf…ôr k…Ē c…ôloto c…ôtel…ôr, k…Ē k…ôp…ôr ka y…õb…ôc f…ôp.
\c 36
\p 
\v 1 K…ôy…õf…õ ka Betsalel k…ôk…Ē ka Oholiyab k…ôb…ôp ka ac…õr…ôŇč alp…ôs ak…Ē MARIKI …õnas…ĒŇč d…õc…õr…ôŇč k…Ē dosoku s…ôbomp nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčac…ôr…õ y…õb…ôc ya nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku Ňčasump…ôr y…õb…ôc Ňčasur…õn…õ yi p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti m…Ē.
\p 
\v 2 K…Ē Musa ewe Betsalel, Oholiyab k…Ē ac…õr…ôŇč ak…Ē MARIKI …õnab…õr dosoku s…ôbomp m…Ē, aŇč…õ b…ôk…ôc yaŇčan y…õnasump…ôr k…ôb…ôc y…õb…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.
\v 3 K…Ē Ňčas…Ēt…ôr Musa ca c…ôk…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanaf…õk teta k…ôlomp…ôs k…Ē y…õb…ôc ya aŇčgbip Ňčosoku m…Ē. B…ôtb…ôt o b…ôtb…ôt anck…õr…õ Musa y…õf…õk tuŇč, b…ôk…ôc yosoku p…õs.
\v 4 Awa afum ac…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanasump…ôr y…õb…ôc f…ôp ya aŇčgbip Ňčosoku m…Ē, Ňčanc…ômb…ôr…ôs nw…õ o nw…õ y…õb…ôc y…Ēk…Ē …õnayi m…Ē.
\v 5 K…Ē Ňčander Ňčaloku Musa: Afum Ňčayi k…ôcep…ôr…ôr k…ôk…õr…õ ka y…õf…õk teta y…õb…ôc y…Ēk…Ē MARIKI osom k…ôlomp…ôs m…Ē.
\v 6 K…Ē Musa osom pad…ôŇčk saŇčka disr…õ f…ôp: Ali fum, p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôrkun p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôran, ta p…ôt…õn s…Ē p…õf…õk…õ aŇčgbip Ňčosoku! K'ayams…ôr oŇč afum k…ônaŇčkan…õ k…ôk…õr…õ ka y…õf…õk y…õc…ômb…ôr…õ ya aŇčgbip Ňčosoku.
\v 7 Y…õf…õk ny…õ anabaŇč…ôs m…Ē y…õnct…ôŇčn…õ haŇč yecep…ôr…ôr teta y…õb…ôc ny…õ p…ônamar k…ôb…ôc m…Ē.
\s1 AŇčgbip Ňčosoku
\p 
\v 8 Afum ac…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ Ňčancb…ôc m…Ē f…ôp, Ňčalomps…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku c…ôpol w…ôco ca s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňča bulu, k'alom Ňčeyim, padu ci k…ôroŇč lulu ya m…õl…õk…õ kerub, y…õb…ôc ya ac…õr…ôŇč y…õnayi.
\v 9 Dobolu da c…ôpol cac…Ēk…Ē f…ôp d…Ēy…Ē nk…õ o nk…õ cururu w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē cam…ôt-maas (28) k…Ē dowokulu da k…ôpol nk…õ o nk…õ d…Ēy…Ē cururu maŇčk…ôl…õ, c…ôpol f…ôp c…ônat…ôŇčn…õn…õ potubuc.
\v 10 K'…õŇčgb…õtl…õn…õ-gb…õtl…õn…õ c…ôpol k…ôcam…ôt kin kin, k'…õŇčgb…õtl…õn…õ-gb…õtl…õn…õ s…Ē c…ôk…Ē k…ôcam…ôt.
\v 11 K…Ē Ňčawes-wes…õ dobol da k…ôloto k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…ôk…ôs…ôk s…ôbeŇča s'alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, k…Ē Ňčanut yi, k…Ē Ňčay…Ē s…Ē tin tayi k…ôpol ka k…ôloto ka m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 12 Dobol da c…ôloto cac…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, k'ewes-wes…õ di s…ôbeŇča w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50), k'onut yi, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ yewes-wesi ya c…ôloto cac…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč f…ôp k…ôsur…õn…õ yin yin.
\v 13 K'olomp…ôs Ňčkora w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) ya k…õma ny…õ …õnac…õp…ôr…õn…õn…õ c…ôloto cac…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ c…ôloto ca d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôy…Ēn…õ kin.
\p 
\v 14 Nt…õ elip m…Ē, k'olomps…õ c…ôpol ca k…ôloto k…ôtel…ôr w…ôco k…Ē pin c…ôfon ca wir, nc…õ …õnalomps…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku m…Ē, k'emperi ci d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôroŇč.
\v 15 K…ôpol nk…õ o nk…õ k…ônay…Ē dobolu da cururu w…ôco maas (30), k…Ē dowokulu d…Ēy…Ē cururu maŇčk…ôl…õ. C…ôpol nc…õ w…ôco k…Ē pin (11) c…ônat…ôŇčn…õn…õ potubuc.
\v 16 K'…õŇčgb…õtl…õn…õ taciŇča c…ôpol nc…õ k…ôcam…ôt, k'…Ēy…Ē s…Ē tin tayi c…ôk…Ē cam…ôt-tin.
\v 17 K'olomp…ôs yewes-wesi w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) k…ôpol k…ôk…ôs…ôk ka y…õgb…õtl…õn…õ y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, k'onut yi. K…ôpol k…ôk…ôs…ôk ka y…õgb…õtl…õn…õ ya m…õr…ôŇč y…Ēk…Ē k'olomp…ôs yewes-wesi w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50), k'onut s…Ē yay…Ēk…Ē.
\v 18 K'olomp…ôs Ňčkora w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) ya k…Ēp…ôr, k'…õŇčgb…õk…ôr…õn…õ yi k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ aŇčgbancan k…ôy…Ēn…õ Ňčin.
\v 19 K'olomps…õ pokump…õ pa aŇčgbancan p…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē kata ya Ňčkesiya yorkun ny…õ anagb…ôt kar…õ k…ôyim m…Ē, k'oŇčkump…õ tam…õr…ôŇč kata ya ntempeli.
\p 
\v 20 K'olomps…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku t…Ēk ya kasiya f…ôr…õm k'…õnc…ômb…ôr fi.
\v 21 Dobolu da f…ôr…õm o f…ôr…õm d…õnay…Ē cururu w…ôco k…Ē dowokulu da fi kururu katin k…Ē dac…Ē.
\v 22 F…ôr…õm o f…ôr…õm f…ônay…Ē sek m…õr…ôŇč ny…õ y…õnasol m…Ē, tat…Ēk…Ē t'…õnay…Ē s…Ē f…ôr…õm fa d…ôkiyi dosoku f…ôp.
\v 23 K'olomp…ôs f…ôr…õm w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) fa k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka nde dec d…õmp…õ da d…ôkiyi dosoku m…Ē.
\v 24 K'olomp…ôs y…õc…ôm…õn…õ w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) ya gbeti ny…õ …õnac…ômb…ôr tant…Ēf ta f…ôr…õm w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20). F…ôr…õm o f…ôr…õm f…ônay…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ m…õr…ôŇč, k…ôsur…õn…õ ka bi ny…õ antam k…ôs…õt sek m…õr…ôŇč y…Ēk…Ē f…ôr…õm f…ôy…Ē m…Ē.
\v 25 K'olomp…ôs s…Ē f…ôr…õm w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) fa k…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec d…õmp…õ da d…ôkiyi dosoku m…Ē,
\v 26 k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) ya gbeti, ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ m…õr…ôŇč y…õnayi f…ôr…õm fin tant…Ēf.
\v 27 K'olomp…ôs f…ôr…õm cam…ôt-tin fa t…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ ta d…ôkiyi dosoku, k…ôca ka ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē,
\v 28 k'olomp…ôs f…ôr…õm m…õr…ôŇč taciŇča fa moŇčkubut ma t…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ pa d…ôkiyi dosoku.
\v 29 K'…õŇčgb…õp…õn…õ f…ôr…õm faf…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč k…ôy…õf…õ tant…Ēf k'oŇčkot…ôrn…õ fi tak…ôroŇč k…ôsora kin. K'…Ēy…Ē tin tayi f…ôr…õm nf…õ m…õr…ôŇč, nf…õ f…ônayi moŇčkubut yay…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē.
\v 30 F…ôr…õm cam…ôt-maas f…ônayi, k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-tin (16) ya gbeti, ti t…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē f…ôr…õm o f…ôr…õm f…ônay…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ m…õr…ôŇč tant…Ēf.
\p 
\v 31 K'…õmpat c…ôgbo ca k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya k…ôcam…ôt nc…õ c…ônasump…ôr f…ôr…õm f…ôp fa k…ôs…ôk kin ka d…ôkiyi dosoku m…Ē.
\v 32 C…ôgbo k…ôcam…ôt ca f…ôr…õm fa k…ôs…ôk ka m…õr…ôŇč ka d…ôkiyi dosoku, k…Ē c…ôgbo k…ôcam…ôt s…Ē c…ôsump…ôr…õ f…ôr…õm fa t…Ēgb…Ēk…õn…õ ta d…ôkiyi dosoku, ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē.
\v 33 K'olomp…ôs k…ôgbo k…ôrac…Ē nk…õ k…ônacep…ôr f…ôr…õm fa k…ôs…ôk kin f…ôp dac…Ē m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ f…ôr…õm f…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē haŇč k…ôb…ôp f…ôlp…ôs.
\v 34 K'osop f…ôr…õm f…ôp k…õma, k'olomp…ôs c…ôsora ca k…õma nde p…ônamar c…ôgbo c…ôcep…ôr m…Ē, k'osop s…Ē ci k…õma.
\p 
\v 35 K'olomps…õ k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, sa alom Ňča bulu k…Ē sa alom Ňčeyim. K'ondu k…ôloto kaŇčk…Ē k…ôroŇč m…õl…õk…õ kerub, y…õb…ôc ya w…ôc…õr…ôŇč k…ôdu y…õnayi yay…Ēk…Ē.
\v 36 K'…õmpat…õ ki mogbu maŇčk…ôl…õ ma k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya, k'osop mi k…õma. Mogbu mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē anab…õr Ňčkora ya k…õma. K'olomps…õ mogbu mam…Ēk…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ maŇčk…ôl…õ ya gbeti.
\p 
\v 37 D…ôkusuŇčka d'aŇčgbancan, k'ondun…õ k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, k'…Ēn…ĒŇčks…ôl si s…ôbeŇča sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, sa alom Ňča bulu k…Ē sa alom Ňčeyim.
\v 38 K'olomps…õ k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ mogbu k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē Ňčkora, k'osop y…õn…õk…ôs ya mogbu tak…ôroŇč k…Ē gbat-gbata ya mi k…õma. Y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi k…ôcam…ôt, k…Ēp…ôr k…ônayi.
\c 37
\s1 KaŇčk…ôra ka sede sa danapa
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē Betsalel olomps…õ kaŇčk…ôra ka sede sa danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya. KaŇčk…ôra kaŇčk…Ē k…ônab…Ēl cururu m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē dac…Ē, k…Ē dowokulu da ki d…õnay…Ē kururu katin k…Ē dac…Ē.
\v 2 K…Ē Betsalel osop kaŇčk…ôra kaŇčk…Ē tedisr…õ k…Ē todoru k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs, k'olomp…ôs k…ôb…ôr ka k…õma haŇč k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôr.
\v 3 K'olomp…ôs c…ôsora maŇčk…ôl…õ ca k…õma nc…õ …õnab…õr moŇčkubut ma kaŇčk…ôra kaŇčk…Ē m…Ē, k…ôs…ôk k…ôt…Ēt c…ôsora m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē k…ôs…ôk k…ômeriya c…ôsora m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 4 K'…õmpat c…ôgbo m…õr…ôŇč ca k…ôt…Ēk k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka kasiya, k'osop ci k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs.
\v 5 K'osor c…ôgbo cac…Ēk…Ē c…ôsora c…ôc…ôs…ôk nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pactam ki k…ôs…õl…õŇč m…Ē.
\p 
\v 6 K…Ē Ňčalomps…õ af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs, dobolu da Ňči d…õnay…Ē cururu m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē dac…Ē k…Ē dowokulu da Ňči d…Ēy…Ē kururu katin k…Ē dac…Ē.
\v 7 K'olomps…õ m…õl…õk…õ kerub m…õr…ôŇč k…õma k…ôt…õmp, k'…õs…õl…ôr…õn…õ mi d…ôk…ôcop k…Ē d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya k…ôroŇč.
\v 8 M…ôs…õl…ôr…õn…õ m…õl…õk…õ kerub min d…ôk…ôcop da af…õŇčk k…ôroŇč, m…õl…õk…õ kerub m…õr…ôŇč m…Ēk…Ē d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da Ňči k…ôroŇč. K'olomp…ôs m…õl…õk…õ kerub m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya, k…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ paka pin nde d…ôk…ôcop k…Ē d…ôk…ôl…ôps…ôr da Ňči k…ôroŇč.
\v 9 M…õl…õk…õ kerub mam…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč meperi banca tak…ôroŇč, yi yokump af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya, m…õnat…õf…ôr…õn…õ meti c…ôro Ňči k…ôroŇč.
\s1 Am…õsa Ňča c…ôcom nc…õ aŇčs…ĒŇč Kanu m…Ē
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē Betsalel olomps…õ am…õsa k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya. Dobolu da am…õsa ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē d…õnay…Ē cururu m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē dowokulu da Ňči d…õnay…Ē kururu katin, k…Ē deŇčeci da Ňči kururu katin k…Ē dac…Ē.
\v 11 K'osop Ňči k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs, k'olomp…ôs Ňči k…ôb…ôr ka k…õma haŇč k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôr.
\v 12 K…Ē Betsalel olomps…õ c…ôs…ôk cac…Ēk…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ f…ôr…õm nf…õ dowokulu da fi d…õnct…ôŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē dowokulu da k…ôca disr…õ m…Ē, k'…õmb…õr ki k…ôb…ôr ka k…õma haŇč k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôr.
\v 13 K'olomp…ôs s…Ē c…ôsora maŇčk…ôl…õ ca k…õma nc…õ …õnab…õr moŇčkubut m'am…õsa k…ôsur…õn…õ ka y…õc…ôm…õn…õ maŇčk…ôl…õ ya Ňči m…Ē.
\v 14 C…ôsora cac…Ēk…Ē c…ônal…Ēt…ôrn…õ f…ôr…õm, dif…Ē ancsor c…ôgbo nc…õ anctam k…ôl…õk Ňči m…Ē.
\v 15 K'olomp…ôs c…ôgbo ca k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya k'osop ci k…õma, c…ôgbo cac…Ēk…Ē c'ancl…õk…õ am…õsa ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē.
\v 16 K'olomps…õ yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya d…õm…õsa k…ôy…õf…õ p…ôlet, m…Ēb…Ēl, s…ôp…Ēt k…Ē mapan ny…õ ancb…ôc…õ teta yoloŇčn…õn…õ ya moro k…Ē ya w…õn m…Ē, k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs k'…õnalomps…õ yi.
\s1 P…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp pa wara cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč
\p 
\v 17 K…Ē Betsalel olomps…õ p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp k…õma k…ôt…õmp k…ôsoku p…õs, k'…õs…õl…ôr…õn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ p…õc…ôm…õn…õ, k…ôk…Ē t…ômboŇčk pa pi, y…Ēn…Ēn…õ ya s…ôlamp, yogbuc ya pi, k…Ē yowur…õn…õ ya y…õl…õŇčk ya t…Ēk.
\v 18 Wara cam…ôt-tin w…õncy…õf…õ d…ôt…ômboŇčk parac…Ē, k…ôca o k…ôca wara maas.
\v 19 K…ôra o k…ôra k…ônay…Ē y…Ēn…Ēn…õ ya s…ôlamp maas ny…õ y…õnawur…õn…õ y…õl…õŇčk ya t…Ēk yokom m…Ē, k…ônay…Ē s…Ē pogbuc k…Ē p…õl…õŇčk. It…Ē p…ônayi wara cam…ôt-tin nw…õ w…õnay…õf…õ d…ôp…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp m…Ē.
\v 20 T…ômboŇčk pa p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp p…õnay…Ē y…Ēn…Ēn…õ ya s…ôlamp maŇčk…ôl…õ ny…õ y…õnawur…õn…õ k…Ē y…õl…õŇčk ya t…Ēk yokom m…Ē, yogbuc k…Ē y…õl…õŇčk ya yi.
\v 21 Wara waw…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč m…õr…ôŇč k…ômaas nw…õ w…õncy…õf…õ d…ôt…ômboŇčk parac…Ē m…Ē, d…ôk…ôy…õf…õ da wara m…õr…ôŇč o m…õr…ôŇč, pogbuc pin pin pencyi wi tant…Ēf.
\v 22 Yogbuc k…Ē wara waw…Ēk…Ē f…ôp anas…õl…ôr…õn…õ yi, f…ôp fa yi f…ôy…Ēn…õ anc…ômb…ôl Ňčin Ňča k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs k…ôt…õmp.
\v 23 K'olomp…ôs s…ôlamp cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, macaŇčk k…Ē map m…õkay…õ meken. K'olomps…õ f…ôp fa mi k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs.
\v 24 K…õma k…ôsoku p…õs kilo w…ôco maas (30) k'…õnalomps…õ p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya pi.
\s1 Tetek p…Ēc…Ēf…õ pa suray
\p 
\v 25 K…Ē Betsalel olomps…õ tetek p…Ēc…Ēf…õ MARIKI suray k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya. Dobolu da tetek pap…Ēk…Ē d…õnay…Ē kururu katin, k…Ē dowokulu da pi kururu katin, p…ônat…ôŇčn…õ c…ôs…ôk f…ôp, k…Ē deŇčeci da pi cururu m…õr…ôŇč. Tetek k…Ē l…õn ya pi y…õt…ôp…ôr…õn…õ anas…õl…ôr…õn…õ y…Ēy…Ēn…õ paka pin.
\v 26 K'osop pi k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs k…ôl…õk am…õsa Ňča pi k…ôroŇč k…ôb…ôp ka c…ôs…ôk ca pi k…ôk…Ē haŇč l…õn ya pi. K'olomp…ôs pi k…ôb…ôr ka k…õma c…ôs…ôk haŇč k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôr.
\v 27 K'olomp…ôs c…ôsora m…õr…ôŇč ca k…õma nc…õ anab…õr ci k…ôb…ôr tant…Ēf ta c…ôs…ôk m…õr…ôŇč ca tetek pap…Ēk…Ē. C…ôsora cac…Ēk…Ē c…Ē andek…Ē pacsor c…ôgbo, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pactam k…ôl…õk ka pi m…Ē.
\v 28 K'…õmpat c…ôgbo ca k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya k'osop ci k…õma.
\p 
\v 29 K…Ē Betsalel olomp…ôs moro m…Ēb…Ēy mopus…õ, k'olomps…õn…õ s…Ē suray s…ôsoku p…õs ns…õ s…ômb…Ēt amb…Ēnc m…Ē, y…õb…ôc ya w…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôlomp…ôs labund…õ y…õnayi.
\c 38
\s1 Tetek poloŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē k…ôsamp k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õn…õ
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē Betsalel olomps…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ Kanu p…Ēc…Ēl pac…Ēf k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya, dobolu da pi d…õnab…ôp cururu k…ôcam…ôt, k…Ē dowokulu da pi cururu k…ôcam…ôt. C…ôs…ôk ca pi c…ônt…ôŇčn…õn…õ, mba deŇčeci da pi d…õnay…Ē cururu maas.\f + \fr 38:1 \ft Kururu kin k…ônt…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē m…õt…ôr min dac…Ē.\f*
\v 2 K'olomp…ôs l…õn ya tetek nde moŇčkubut mak…ôroŇč maŇčk…ôl…õ, ny…õ anas…õl…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē pi m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ pi k…ôy…Ēn…õ paka pin, k'osop pi k…Ēp…ôr.
\v 3 K'olomps…õ yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya tetek toloŇčn…õ f…ôp, k…ôl…õk ka dap, pel, mapan, bak yosort…õ s…õm k…Ē map m…õkay…õ meken. K'olomps…õ yosump…ôr-sump…ôr yay…õ f…ôp k…Ēp…ôr.
\v 4 K'olomp…ôs manta ma k…Ēp…ôr, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr mi k…ôb…ôr ka tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ tant…Ēf haŇč dac…Ē. K'…õs…õl c…ôsora maŇčk…ôl…õ ca k…Ēp…ôr nc…õ …õnab…õr d…ômoŇčkubut ma manta, teta k…ôsor ka c…ôgbo m…Ē.
\v 5 K'olomp…ôs c…ôsora maŇčk…ôl…õ nc…õ …õnab…õr moŇčkubut maŇčk…ôl…õ ma manta ma k…Ēp…ôr mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pactam k…ôsor ka c…ôgbo m…Ē.
\v 6 K'…õmpat c…ôgbo ca k…ôt…Ēk ka kasiya, k'osop ci k…Ēp…ôr.
\v 7 K'osor c…ôgbo cac…Ēk…Ē d…ôc…ôsora cac…Ēk…Ē c…ônayi c…ôs…ôk ca tetek toloŇčn…õ m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pactam k…ôl…õk tetek pap…Ēk…Ē m…Ē. ∆źnalomps…õ pi c…ôbam, k…Ē p…Ēy…Ē fos disr…õ.
\p 
\v 8 K'…õs…õl…õ k…ôsamp ka k…Ēp…ôr, k…Ē p…õc…ôm…õn…õ pa ki s…Ē p…ônay…Ēn…õ k…Ēp…ôr. K'alomps…õ yi m…õm ny…õ aran aŇč…õ Ňčanayi y…õb…ôc nde kusuŇčka ka aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē.
\s1 C…ôloto ca saŇčka
\p 
\v 9 K'olomp…ôs abaŇčka. K'…õnc…ômb…ôr…õ saŇčka k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē c…ôloto ca s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler. Dobolu da c…ôloto cac…Ēk…Ē d…õnab…ôp cururu tasar tin (100).
\v 10 Mogbu ma yi w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) k…Ēp…ôr k…ônayi. Ňäkora ya mogbu k…Ē gbat-gbata ya mi y…Ēy…Ēn…õ gbeti.
\v 11 K…ôca k…ômeriya ka ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, c…ôloto c…ônab…Ēl cururu tasar tin (100), mogbu w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya yi w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) ya k…Ēp…ôr, Ňčkora ya mogbu k…Ē gbat-gbata ya mi f…ôp gbeti b…õnayi.
\p 
\v 12 K…ôca nk…õ dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, c…ôloto c…ônab…Ēl cururu w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) mogbu ma ci w…ôco k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi w…ôco, Ňčkora ya mogbu k…Ē gbat-gbata ya mi f…ôp gbeti b…õnayi.
\v 13 K…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, dobolu d'abaŇčka d…õnay…Ē cururu w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50).
\v 14 K…Ē k…ôs…ôk kin k…ôy…Ē c…ôloto nc…õ c…ônab…Ēl cururu w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (15) m…Ē, mogbu maas k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi maas.
\v 15 K…ôca ka m…õr…ôŇč, d…ôkusuŇčka da saŇčka k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…Ē k…ômeriya, dobolu da c…ôloto d…õnay…Ē cururu w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (15), mogbu maas k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi maas.
\v 16 C…ôloto nc…õ anan…õp…ôr saŇčka m…Ē f…ôp, c…ôloto ca s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler s…ônayi.
\v 17 Y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mogbu f…ôp, ya k…Ēp…ôr y…õnayi, Ňčkora ya mogbu k…Ē gbat-gbata f…ôp ya gbeti y…õnayi, y…õn…õks…õ ya mogbu f…ôp anasop yi gbeti, k…Ē mogbu ma saŇčka f…ôp anakot…ôr…õn…õ mi k…Ē gbat-gbata ya gbeti.
\p 
\v 18 K'ondun…õ c…ôloto nc…õ anaŇč…õr…õ kusuŇčka ka saŇčka m…Ē. K'olomps…õ ci s…ôbeŇča sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, s…ôbeŇča alom Ňča bulu, sa alom Ňčeyim, s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, y…õb…ôc ya w…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôdu y…õnayi. C…ôloto c…ôŇč…õr…õ c…ônab…Ēl cururu w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) k…Ē deŇčeci da ci d…õnay…Ē cururu k…ôcam…ôt, p…ôm…Ē dowokulu da c…ôloto ca saŇčka.
\v 19 Anad…õt…ôr yi mogbu maŇčk…ôl…õ mm…õ m…õnac…ôm…õn…õ y…õc…ôm…õn…õ maŇčk…ôl…õ ya k…Ēp…ôr m…Ē, Ňčkora k…Ē gbat-gbata ya gbeti y…õnayi, k…Ē y…õn…õks…õ ya mogbu s…Ē, anasop yi gbeti.
\v 20 C…ôgbo c…ôd…Ēf ca d…ôkiyi dosoku k…Ē abaŇčka Ňča saŇčka f…ôp, ca k…Ēp…ôr c…ônayi.
\s1 D…õlay da k…õma, gbeti k…Ē k…Ēp…ôr nk…õ anab…ôc…õ m…Ē
\p 
\v 21 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē daka da f…õc nd…õ anab…õrs…õ k…ôlomp…ôs ka d…ôkiyi dosoku nd…õ walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē. P…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnasom Ňča ti m…Ē, aLewy Ňčanal…Ēm yi, Itamar p…ôyi ti kiriŇč wan w…ôrkun w…ôka w…ôloŇčn…õ Aruna.
\v 22 K…Ē Betsalel wan ka Uri, wans…Ē ka Hur, w…ôka kusuŇčka ka Yuda, …õmb…ôc t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 23 Oholiyab, wan ka Ahisamak, w…ôka kusuŇčka ka Dan …õnamar k…Ē, w…ôkak…Ē …õncpat, w…ôc…õr…ôŇč nw…õ oncdu c…ôloto ca alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňča bulu, k…Ē alom Ňčeyim, k…Ē c…ôloto ca s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler.
\p 
\v 24 K…õma nk…õ k…ônab…õr…õ k…ôlomp…ôs ka aŇčgbip Ňčosoku m…Ē f…ôp k…ônab…ôp kilo masar cam…ôt-maas w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (877), potubuc…õ pa aŇčgbip Ňčosoku p'anatubc…õ ki.
\v 25 Gbeti mb…õ aka k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel Ňčanaf…õk m…Ē f…ôp, b…õnak…Ē kilo wul maas w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-maas (3.018), potubuc…õ pa aŇčgbip Ňčosoku p'anatubc…õ ki.
\v 26 K'ayer k…ôf…õk kaŇčk…Ē-…õ, antam k…ôloku a arkun wul masar cam…ôt-tin k…Ē maas, masar k…ôcam…ôt w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (603.550) aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) haŇč k…ôp…õ k…ôroŇč m…Ē, nw…õ o nw…õ …õnaf…õk p…ôsam gbeti k…ôcam…ôt potubuc…õ pa p…ôsam p'aŇčgbip Ňčosoku.
\v 27 K…Ē Ňčalomps…õ gbeti wul maas (3.000) y…õc…ôm…õn…õ tasar tin (100) ya f…ôr…õm ya aŇčgbip Ňčosoku k…Ē ya k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ tedisr…õ ti t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč p…õc…ôm…õn…õ o p…õc…ôm…õn…õ analomps…õ pi gbeti kilo w…ôco maas (30).
\v 28 K'alomps…õ gbeti b…õlp…ôs mb…õ kilo w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (17) k…Ē k…ôram masar cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (750) Ňčkora ya mogbu, k'aŇčsop s…Ē ncal…ôran k…Ē gbat-gbata ny…õ anakot…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē mogbu m…Ē.
\v 29 K…Ēp…ôr nk…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčanatubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč MARIKI m…Ē k…ônab…ôp kilo wul m…õr…ôŇč, tasar tin w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ (2.124).
\v 30 K…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs ki y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya d…ôkusuŇčka da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, tetek toloŇčn…õ pa k…Ēp…ôr k…Ē manta ma k…Ēp…ôr m…Ēk…Ē anan…õp pi m…Ē, k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya tetek f…ôp,
\v 31 k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya saŇčka k…Ē ya d…ôkusuŇčka da saŇčka, k…Ē c…ôgbo c…ôd…Ēf ca d…ôkiyi dosoku k…Ē ca saŇčka f…ôp.
\c 39
\s1 Yamos ya w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč
\p 
\v 1 S…ôbeŇča sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňča bulu, k…Ē alom Ňčeyim s…Ē Ňčanalomps…õ yamos ya d…ôKanu ny…õ p…ômar pab…õrn…õ a pab…ôc y…õb…ôc nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku m…Ē. K'alomps…õ s…Ē Aruna yamos ya d…ôKanu p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\p 
\v 2 K'olomps…õ duma da ef…Ēd k…ôloto ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, sa k…õma, sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňča bulu, k…Ē alom Ňčeyim.
\v 3 K…Ē Ňčamperi b…Ēp…ôr ya k…õma ny…õ Ňčanagbint-gbinti k…Ē Ňčan…õk…ôs yi m…õgb…õr m…õf…õt m…õf…õt mm…õ Ňčancb…õrs…ôr c…ôloto c…ôf…ôf…ôr ca s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňča bulu, k…Ē alom Ňčeyim, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ y…õb…ôc ya ac…õr…ôŇč k…ôdu.
\v 4 K'amb…õr duma da ef…Ēd yeyes…õ banca m…õr…ôŇč ny…õ anas…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ yi c…ôs…ôk ca banca ya duma da ef…Ēd m…Ē.
\v 5 Tabataba mp…õ p…õnan…ĒŇčk…ôr duma da ef…Ēd ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē. Anas…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ pi, k…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ paka pin k…Ē duma da ef…Ēd: Tolomp…ôs ta yi t…õnawur…õn…õ: k…ôloto ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, sa k…õma, sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňča bulu, k…Ē alom Ňčeyim p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\v 6 K…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs walak…õ wa masar m…Ēt…Ēt ma onik…ôs k…Ē Ňčamb…õrs…ôr mi f…ôr…õm fa k…õma disr…õ. K…Ē Ňčancic…ôs mewe ma awut a Yisrayel, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ ancic tamp m…Ē.
\v 7 K'…Ēs…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ masar mam…Ēk…Ē yeyes…õ banca ya duma da ef…Ēd k…ôroŇč, k…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs ka mewe ma awut a Yisrayel (Yakuba), p…ôm…Ē nt…õ MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\s1 Yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc
\p 
\v 8 K'ondun…õ yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc k…ôloto ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, pan…ĒŇčk…ôl s…ôbeŇča sa k…õma, sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňča bulu k…Ē alom Ňčeyim, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē analomp…ôs duma da ef…Ēd m…Ē. Y…õb…ôc ya w…ôc…õr…ôŇč k…ôdu y…õnayi.
\v 9 Yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē ananut yi k…ôm…õr…ôŇč, y…õt…ôŇčn…õn…õ c…ôs…ôk f…ôp dobolu da c…ôs…ôk ca yi d…õnay…Ē k…ôca disr…õ katin.
\v 10 K…Ē Ňčand…õt…ôr ki masar momot…ôr-mot…ôr c…ôgba maŇčk…ôl…õ: K…ôgba k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…ônay…Ē tasar teyim, tasar t'alom Ňča c…ôbe, k…Ē tasar pa alom Ňčobuk m…õl.
\v 11 K…ôgba ka m…õr…ôŇč k…ônay…Ē tasar teyim ceŇč, tasar t'alom Ňča bulu k…Ē diyamaŇč.
\v 12 K…ôgba ka maas k…ônay…Ē Tasar pa alom Ňča alemb…ôra, tasar pa lom y…õla c…ôgb…õr k…Ē tasar pa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc.
\v 13 K…ôgba ka maŇčk…ôl…õ k…ônay…Ē tasar pa alom Ňčobuk m…õl, tasar pa lom y…õc…õmc…õm…ôr k…Ē tasar pa alom Ňčobuk. Tasar o tasar anas…õt…ôr pi d…ôf…ôr…õm fa k…õma.
\v 14 Tasar o tasar anacic pi tewe ta wan w…ôkin w…ôka Yisrayel (Yakuba), p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ancic tamp m…Ē. Ti tencment…ôr mewe ma cusuŇčka nc…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (12) ca Yisrayel.
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē Ňčalomps…õ yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē megbekce ma k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs.
\v 16 K…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs f…ôr…õm m…õr…ôŇč fa k…õma, k…Ē curund…õ m…õr…ôŇč ca k…õma nc…õ anab…õr moŇčkubut m…õr…ôŇč ma yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc mak…ôroŇč m…Ē.
\v 17 K'aŇčgb…õk…ôr megbekce mam…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč ma k…õma curund…õ c…ôk…Ē c…ôyi d…ômoŇčkubut ma yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē.
\v 18 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē ŇčaŇčgb…õk…ôr c…ôs…ôk c…ôlp…ôs ca megbekce mam…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč d…ôf…ôr…õm m…õr…ôŇč nf…õ f…ônayi yeyes…õ banca ya duma da ef…Ēd m…Ē tekiriŇč.
\v 19 K…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs s…Ē curund…õ m…õr…ôŇč ca k…õma k…Ē Ňčamb…õr ci moŇčkubut ma yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē tant…Ēf, k…ôs…ôk nk…õ k…ôncgbuŇč…õn…õ duma da ef…Ēd m…Ē.
\v 20 K…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs s…Ē curund…õ m…õr…ôŇč c…ôl…Ēma ca k…õma nc…õ Ňčanab…õr yeyes…õ banca ya duma da ef…Ēd tant…Ēf m…Ē, tekiriŇč, d…ôk…ôs…Ēt…ôr…õn…õ da yi nde p…ôsur…õn…õ k…Ē tak…ôroŇč ta tabataba ta duma da ef…Ēd m…Ē.
\v 21 K…Ē ŇčaŇčkot…ôr…õn…õ curund…õ ca yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc k…Ē ca duma da ef…Ēd k…ôb…ônda ka alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ yuba y…õgb…õkn…õ d…õb…ôk…ôc k…ôdeŇčs…õ tak…ôroŇč ta tabataba pa duma da ef…Ēd, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ s…Ē yuba k…ôt…Ētam k…ôsak…õn…õ k…Ē duma da ef…Ēd, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\s1 Yamos yosoku y…Ēl…Ēma
\p 
\v 22 K'ondun…õ burumus ba ef…Ēd s…ôbeŇča sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc f…ôp, y…õb…ôc ya w…ôc…õr…ôŇč k…ôdu y…õnayi.
\v 23 D…ôk…ôm…ôl domp da duma dad…Ēk…Ē dac…Ē d…õnayi, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ andun…õ yamos akata m…Ē. Anagb…õnt di kilim haŇč pan…ĒŇčk…ôr nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta d…õwal…õ m…Ē.
\v 24 K…Ē Ňčandu bi tant…Ēf haŇč k…Ē Ňčan…ĒŇčk…ôr c…ôpare ca alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, alom Ňča bulu, alom Ňčeyim k…Ē s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler.
\v 25 K…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs meŇčgbeŇčk…ôle ma k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs, k…Ē Ňčamb…õrs…ôr-b…õrs…ôr yi burumus tant…Ēf haŇč k…Ē Ňčan…ĒŇčk…ôr lulu ya c…ôpare dac…Ē.
\v 26 TeŇčgbeŇčk…ôle pin k…ôpare kin, teŇčgbeŇčk…ôle pin k…ôpare kin k'amb…õrs…ôr yi burumus haŇč k'an…ĒŇčk…ôr, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôk…Ēb…ôc'em p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\p 
\v 27 K'ac…õr…ôŇč k…ôdu Ňčas…Ēt…õ s…Ē Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn duma dedisr…õ da k…ôloto ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler.
\v 28 C…ôfak…ôl, m…ômbo k…Ē c…Ēgba f…ôp fa yi f…ônay…Ēn…õ k…ôloto ka kent…ôler.
\v 29 K'ac…õr…ôŇč Ňčandun…õ mabamaba k…ôloto ka s…ôbeŇča sa kent…ôler, Ňčan…ĒŇčk…ôs…ôl s…ôbeŇča sa alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, sa alom Ňča bulu, k…Ē sa alom Ňčeyim, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\v 30 K…Ē Ňčalomps…õ ab…Ēp…ôr Ňča d…ôKanu k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs, k'ancic Ňči k…ôroŇč ¬ęDosoku da MARIKI¬Ľ p…ôm…Ē nt…õ ancic tamp m…Ē.
\v 31 K…Ē ŇčaŇčkot…ôr…õn…õ t…õb…ônda ta alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc k…ôfak…ôl tak…ôroŇč, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\s1 Y…õb…ôc yelip, k'aŇčk…õr…õ yi Musa
\p 
\v 32 K…Ē y…õb…ôc ya d…ôkiyi dosoku, y'aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu yelip oŇč. Aka Yisrayel Ňčanasur…õn…õ k…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa m…Ē.
\v 33 K'aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ Musa d…ôk…ôyi dosoku: AŇčgbancan k…Ē ca ya Ňči: Ňčkora ya Ňči, f…ôr…õm fa Ňči, gbat-gbata ya Ňči, mogbu ma Ňči k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya Ňči,
\v 34 kata ya Ňčkesiya yorkun ny…õ aŇčgb…ôt alom Ňčeyim, pokump…õ pa kata ya ntempeli, k…Ē k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ,
\v 35 kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa da MARIKI, k…Ē c…ôgbo ca ki k…Ē af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya,
\v 36 am…õsa k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya Ňči f…ôp, k…Ē c…ôcom nc…õ aloŇčn…õn…õ Kanu m…Ē,
\v 37 p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp pa k…õma k…ôsoku p…õs k…Ē s…ôlamp sa pi, yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya pi f…ôp k…Ē moro momot…õn…õ ma pi,
\v 38 tetek toloŇčn…õ pa k…õma, moro m…Ēb…Ēy, suray s…ôbotu amb…Ēnc, k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ ka d…ôkusuŇčka da aŇčgbancan,
\v 39 tetek toloŇčn…õ pa k…Ēp…ôr k…Ē manta ma k…Ēp…ôr, k…Ē c…ôgbo ca pi k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya pi, k…ôsamp k…ôb…õr…õ domun d…Ēs…Ēk…ôsn…õn…õ k…Ē p…õc…ôm…õn…õ pa ki,
\v 40 c…ôloto ca saŇčka k…Ē mogbu ma ci, k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi, k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ d…ôkusuŇčka da saŇčka, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ b…ônda k…Ē c…ôgbo c…ôd…Ēf ca yi, yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ny…õ p…ônamar pab…ôc…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku m…Ē f…ôp, aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē f…ôp,
\v 41 yamos yodu y…Ēk…Ē p…ômar pab…õrn…õ a pab…ôc y…õb…ôc nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku m…Ē, k…Ē yamos ya d…ôKanu ny…õ Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn Ňčandek…Ē Ňčacb…õrn…õ a Ňčacb…ôc…õ Kanu m…Ē.
\v 42 Aka Yisrayel Ňčanab…ôc y…õb…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\v 43 Nt…õ Musa …õn…ôŇčk a Ňčasur…õn…õ k…ôb…ôc y…õb…ôc f…ôp y…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…ôb…ôc m…Ē, k'ontolan…õ aka Yisrayel p…ôt…Ēt.
\c 40
\s1 K…ôsom ka k…ôc…ômb…ôr k'aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē k…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka Ňči teta y…õb…ôc ya d…ôKanu
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęTataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ta Ňčof Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, m…ôc…ômb…ôr d…ôkiyi dosoku, aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.
\v 3 M…ôb…õrs…õ di kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôy…Ē walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa dem k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē, m…ôk…ôŇčk…õ kaŇčk…ôra kaŇčk…Ē k…ôloto ta afum Ňčacn…ôŇčk ki.
\v 4 M…ôk…õr…õ am…õsa m…ôc…ômb…ôr Ňči k…ôroŇč yosump…ôr-sump…ôr t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar m…Ē. M…ôk…õr…õ p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp m…ôc…ômb…ôr, m…ôd…õt pi s…ôlamp.
\v 5 M…ôk…Ē m…ôc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ pa k…õma mp…õ ande pacc…Ēf suray ns…õ s…ômb…Ēt amb…Ēnc m…Ē, tekiriŇč ta kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa da MARIKI m…Ē. K…Ē telip-…õ, m…ôd…õt k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ nde kusuŇčka ka d…ôkiyi dosoku.
\v 6 M…ôc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēc…Ēf nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da d…ôkiyi dosoku, nd…õ d…Ēy…Ēn…õ aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.
\v 7 M…ôc…ômb…ôr k…ôsamp aŇčgbip k…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ dac…Ē, palas ki domun.
\v 8 M…ôc…ômb…ôr saŇčka haŇč m…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr, m…ôd…õt k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ d…ôkusuŇčka da si.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 9 ¬ęM…ôl…õk moro m…Ēb…Ēy m…ôsop mi d…ôkiyi dosoku k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya di f…ôp. M…ôpus di k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya di nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ca cac…Ēk…Ē f…ôp nde d…ôkiyi dosoku k…Ē disr…õ y…Ēy…Ēn…õ yopus f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč.
\v 10 M…ôb…Ēy tetek toloŇčn…õ mp…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI y…Ēc…Ēl m…Ē, k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya pi, m…ôpus…õ MARIKI tetek toloŇčn…õ, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ pi oŇč k…ôy…Ēn…õ posoku p…õs f…Ēr yem kiriŇč.
\v 11 M…ôb…Ēy k…ôsamp k…Ē p…õc…ôm…õn…õ pa ki, m…ôpus…õ yi s…Ē MARIKI.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 12 ¬ęM…ôc…ĒŇč…õn…õ Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun nde kusuŇčka ka aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, m…ôbik…õ Ňča domun.
\v 13 M…ôb…õr Aruna yamos y…Ēn ya d…ôKanu, m…ôb…Ēy k…Ē moro ma d…ôKanu, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē m…ôs…Ēk…ôs k…Ē p…ôb…ôc'em oŇč y…õb…ôc ya w…ôloŇčn…õ.
\v 14 M…ôc…ĒŇč…õn…õ s…Ē awut …Ēn m…ôb…õr…ôs Ňča duma dedisr…õ daŇčan.
\v 15 M…ôb…Ēy Ňča moro ma d…ôKanu p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ômb…Ēy mi kas k…ôŇčan m…Ē. Ňäa s…Ē Ňčade Ňčab…ôc'em p…ôm…Ē aloŇčn…õ. K…ôb…Ēy ka moro ma d…ôKanu kaŇčk…Ē k…ôndes…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr y…õb…ôc ya k…ôloŇčn…õ kem doru o doru.¬Ľ
\v 16 K…Ē Musa …Ēy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.
\s1 Musa osom k…ôc…ômb…ôr ka aŇčgbancan
\p 
\v 17 Tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ta Ňčof Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Ňča teren ta m…õr…ôŇč, k'anc…ômb…ôr d…ôkiyi dosoku.
\p 
\v 18 K…Ē Musa …õnc…ômb…ôr d…ôkiyi dosoku k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya di, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr f…ôr…õm, k'emperi c…ôgbo, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr mogbu.
\v 19 Nt…õ elip m…Ē, k'emperi k…ôloto k…ôkump…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku, k'oluks…ôrn…õ k'…õŇčgb…ôp…ôr k…ôloto ka m…õr…ôŇč tak…ôroŇč, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē.
\p 
\v 20 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel w…Ēk…Ē anacic…ôs m…Ē, k'…õmb…õr kaŇčk…ôra disr…õ, k'osor c…ôgbo c…ôl…õk…õ ca kaŇčk…ôra kaŇčk…Ē, k'…õl…õk af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya k'…õŇčgb…ôp…ôr ki tak…ôroŇč.
\v 21 K'…õl…õk kaŇčk…ôra k'eŇčkek…ôr…õ ki nde d…ôkiyi dosoku disr…õ. K'…õnd…õt k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ nk…õ k…ôyi tekiriŇč ta kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē Musa …õnc…ômb…ôr am…õsa aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu disr…õ, ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya ka d…ôkiyi dosoku.
\v 23 K'…õnc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr c…ôcom f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē nk…Ēn MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\p 
\v 24 K'…õnc…ômb…ôr p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu disr…õ, p…õt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē am…õsa, ntende k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka d…ôkiyi dosoku.
\v 25 K'…õnc…ômb…ôr s…ôlamp MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē nk…Ēn MARIKI …õnasom ti nk…Ēn Musa m…Ē.
\p 
\v 26 K…Ē Musa …õnc…ômb…ôr tetek pa k…õma nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ disr…õ k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ tekiriŇč.
\v 27 K'…Ēnc…Ēf suray s…ôbotu amb…Ēnc, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē.
\p 
\v 28 K'…õnd…õt k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ nde kusuŇčka da d…ôkiyi dosoku.
\v 29 K…Ē Musa …õnc…ômb…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēc…Ēf…õ MARIKI nde kusuŇčka ka d…ôkiyi dosoku, nd…õ d…Ēy…Ēn…õ aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē, k'oloŇčn…õ di p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēc…Ēf, k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti nk…Ēn Musa m…Ē.
\p 
\v 30 K…Ē Musa …õnc…ômb…ôr k…ôsamp aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ dac…Ē, k'amb…õr ki domun d…Ēs…Ēk…ôsn…õn…õ.
\v 31 K…ôl…õk nk…Ēn Musa k…ôb…ôp ka Aruna haŇč awut …Ēn arkun k…Ē Ňčambik…õn…õ waca k…Ē w…õc…ôk teta k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ.
\v 32 K…Ē Ňčande k…ôcb…õr…õ aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu disr…õ Ňčack…Ē k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ-…õ, m…õn…õ Ňčambik…õn…õ teta k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\p 
\v 33 K…Ē Musa …õnc…ômb…ôr saŇčka k'…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôr d…ôkiyi dosoku k…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ, k'…õnd…õt k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ nde kusuŇčka ka saŇčka. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē Musa …õnal…ôp…ôs y…õb…ôc ny…õ MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē m…Ē.
\s1 N…Ēr…Ē da debeki da MARIKI d…õlas aŇčgbancan
\p 
\v 34 Nt…õ y…õb…ôc ny…õ yelip m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôp k…ônder k…ôgb…ôp…ôrn…õ aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, k…Ē n…Ēr…Ē da debeki da MARIKI dender d…õlas d…ôkiyi dosoku.
\v 35 T…õnas…ĒŇč…õ ta Musa …õntam k…ôb…õr…õ daŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ-…õ, bawo k…ôp k…ônayi Ňči k…ôroŇč k…Ē n…Ēr…Ē da debeki da MARIKI d…õnalas d…ôkiyi dosoku.
\p 
\v 36 T…õm nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčaccep…õ-cep…õ m…Ē, Ňčacy…õf…õ f…õ k…ôl…õk d…Ēp…Ē m…õn…õ k…ôp k…ônuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôroŇč.
\v 37 K…Ē k…ôp k…ônt…Ēy…õf…õ-…õ, aka Yisrayel Ňčaf…Ēcep…õ haŇč d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ k…ôŇčy…õf…õ m…Ē.
\v 38 D…Ēs…Ēk disr…õ, k…ôp ka MARIKI k…ôncyi d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôroŇč, k…Ē p…ômbiy…õ-…õ n…õnc dencyi s…Ē d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôroŇč, tat…Ēk…Ē t…õnayi f…Ēr ya aka Yisrayel f…ôp kiriŇč, t…õm nt…õ Ňčanayi k…ôcep…õ-cep…õ k…ôŇčan disr…õ f…ôp m…Ē.
